999864737.name: Big Bag of Bucks
999864737.description: A big bag of money is always useful for funding an adventure or bribing your way out of a tricky situation.

209290837.name: Big Hero 6 Baymax
209290837.description: Get Baymax as your sidekick and bring him home today with Big Hero 6 on Digital HD & Disney Movies Anywhere, and Blu-ray™ Feb 24!

189910805.name: Snow Storm Cloud
189910805.description: Clicking on a humanoid of any kind (yep, works on NPCs) will cause a cloud to rush from your hand to your target. It will hover above them, spin and occasionally drop snowflakes.

1760406591.name: Glorious Sword
1760406591.description: A sword of unfathomable power, laid buried in the sands of time till now.

220288991.name: Fake Egg Spawner
220288991.description: Troll your fellow players and friends by spawning fake eggs in game!

11999279.name: XLS Mark II Pulse Laser Pistol
11999279.description: The XLS Mark II Pulse Laser Pistol is standard issue in the intergalactic police corps.

433922317.name: Summer Camp Arm Floaties
433922317.description: Equip and you will be wearing a floatie on each of your arms. When standing idle in water, your character gently paddles his arms back and forth while floats up to the surface.

21294489.name: Jade Katana of the Darkest Forest
21294489.description: "The career of a sage is of two kinds: He is either honored by all in the world, Like a flower waving its head, Or else he disappears into the silent forest." - Lao Tzu

257807712.name: Heather the Dragon Rider
257807712.description: As tough as they come and sly as a fox. You couldn’t ask for a better companion than her…but can you really trust her motives?  Comes with the turf, I guess.

725802546.name: Gamora’s Sword
725802546.description: Want super speed like Gamora? Take this sword with you and you shall be fast!

95354259.name: Forbidden Box
95354259.description: You know that box your gramps told you never to open?  Now you know why!  The Forbidden Box will summon several violent beasts, which will hunt down any player, friend or foe, who lays eyes on it or falls within its area of effect. You can spawn up to four monsters at a time, each of which is capable of dealing 10 points of damage per second.

209980135.name: Frozen Fury of the Bloxian Order's Smoke Bomb
209980135.description: Part of the Frozen Fury of the Bloxian Order package.

2803771415.name: Royal Guard of Horus' Lotus Staff
2803771415.description: Duty. Honor. Loyalty to the Pharaoh and Horus above all others. Part of the Royal Guard of Horus Bundle.

939145471.name: Super Speedy Pink Potion
939145471.description:
It's the right mix of chemicals and the right shade to make a statement. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

129471121.name: Trololo Cape of Invisibility
129471121.description: Now you see me - now you don't!  Turns yourself invisible and reappear as if out of thin air!

1929592959.name: Treacherous Throwing Knives
1929592959.description: Dagger, dagger, dagger! Made for throwing only, click to launch three daggers at your foes.

86692539.name: RGC 2012 Gladius
86692539.description: Modeled after Julius Caesar's Gladius - awarded to users who purchased a ticket to RGC 2012 by July 2nd.

1230839551.name: Ferdinand
1230839551.description: Ferdinand has arrived, bounding into action and ready for any adventure that comes your way!

261826406.name: Cro-Minion Club
261826406.description: The Minions have been serving the most despicable masters throughout time. This weapon was state of the art for evildoers…40,000 years ago.

29100543.name: Water Balloon
29100543.description: Kick off summer right - with a water balloon fight!

61459706.name: Staff of Shifting Polarity
61459706.description: When you use the Staff of Shifting Polarity, all near by players are pulled to the nearest object.  This force is unstoppable!

75906930.name: Lobster
75906930.description: Win this by playing "Welcome to Stoogeville" and being the MVS (Most Valuable Stooge)!  Be sure to catch the Three Stooges Movie - in theaters April 13th.  Check out the game here - http://www.roblox.com/Welcome-to-Stoogeville-place?id=74885275  Tag - 3 Stooges, Moe, Curly, Larry

12187319.name: Sword of the Highlander
12187319.description:
And there's fire in the glen, fire in the glen /
But no fire in the eyes of our Highland men

103359953.name: Shadow Sword
103359953.description: Equipping the Shadow Sword shrouds your character in darkness. You immediately transform into a warrior wearing a jet-black suit and begin emitting a cloud of dark fog. While your appearance unnerves and disorients your opponents, each sword strike does 35 points of damage and pressing space twice teleports you forward.

2221408043.name: 7723 Companion
2221408043.description: Don’t let robots scare you, 7723 is found to be quite a charm. Tune into Netflix’s Next Gen on September 7 to find out more!

2413687523.name: Dread Elder Warlock's Wand
2413687523.description: It takes a will of iron to control, and a will of steel to resist its power. Part of the Dread Elder Warlock package.

292970740.name: From the Vault: Dozens of Dinosaurs
292970740.description: From the vault of interns past, ROBLOX brings you - dozens of dinosaurs! Sharksie's pack of dinos spawns 14 plushie dinos for you to enjoy.

257816690.name: Beast Boy
257816690.description: Dog person? Cat person? Well, with Beast Boy you get both…and every other creature in the known universe. Including a crime fighting Teen Titan.

160198363.name: Dynamically Lit Sword
160198363.description: Darkness strikes in the light!  Swing your glowing sword at your foes to do 25 damage per hit.

18479357.name: Boomerang
18479357.description: Enjoy a nice peaceful game of catch... with yourself or a friend!

221181437.name: Red Sparkle Time Claymore
221181437.description: Slash fiercely at your enemies with vengeance, dealing some massive damage; between 15 to 35 points.  Click and hold for 3 seconds to summon a red ring of enchantment that shoots rubies up around you and does 12.5 points of damage to anyone they hit.

78665204.name: Adalinda's Anlance
78665204.description: Charge the Anlance for ultimate speed and power.

202083069.name: REKTangle Board
202083069.description: All I ever want to do is skate. With this REKTangle board that is no problem!

81847365.name: Potato Cannon
81847365.description: Cloudy with a chance of raw potatoes? Hurl potatoes through the sky to stun your foes!

1981809272.name: Blobby Companion
1981809272.description: Blobby is always jiggling for a good time!  You can often find an unexpected thing or two inside his gelatin body.

97161295.name: Gear Cloner
97161295.description: This device will clone your gear so that you can share it with a teammate or friend.

1513260464.name: Pot O’ Gold Sword
1513260464.description: Defend your treasure with this mighty sword, leaving a rainbow trail in your wake.

68848741.name: Spectral Sword of Illusions
68848741.description: "Rainbows are visions, but only illusions / And Rainbows have nothing to hide"

321582427.name: Lightning Horn of the Heavens
321582427.description: Click to summon massive lightning from the heavens.  Anyone close to a strike will be knocked to the ground and blown away from it, doing an additional 20 damage. Anyone directly hit will take 100 damage!

1363020083.name: Black Panther - Claws
1363020083.description: The power of the gauntlets will get you further, faster for the Innovation Event! Be sure to see Marvel Studio’s Black Panther in theaters February 16!

382837983.name: Opened Basket of Ultimate Troll
382837983.description: Inside this basket is a troll top hat. Don't feed the trolls. Inside you find... Troll Top Hat.

161219921.name: All American Roped
161219921.description: This Roped was made in America!  Zip around ROBLOX in your patriotic roped. Available for a limited time only!

70476435.name: Dragon's Breath Potion
70476435.description: Yeah this does exactly what you think it does. Drink it and you can shoot flames at anything and everything!

21440056.name: Protest Sign: Pro Fake Mustache
21440056.description: It's a reasonable position, I think.

136213778.name: Legendary Ice Club
136213778.description: This Ice Club is part of the Legendary Yeti package.

18776718.name: Golden Katana of the Unflinching Dawn
18776718.description: "Victory is reserved for those who are willing to pay it's price." - Sun Tzu

102705402.name: Super Freeze Cannon
102705402.description: Shoots frozen balls of doom out at a rate of 1 per second.  The balls will slow your enemies and also do 10 damage per hit. Every so often, you'll get the coolest cannonball of all time, it will freeze your enemy for up to 4 seconds.

257811449.name: Neon Bloxster
257811449.description: Neon colored reskin of the Bloxster 2XH. Emits neon-blue like exhaust smoke instead of grey. Holding the shift key allows you to do a wheelie like move. The 'X' key toggles the head light in front of the vehicle.

10468915.name: ROBLOX Classic Brigand's Sword
10468915.description: Stand and deliver! Does moderate damage and has a special Lunge attack (double click) that increases reach and damage. This is the first gear item ever published.

1245309147.name: Frostooth the Frozen Treasure Chest
1245309147.description: Freeze your foes who would try and steal your treasure!

172298750.name: Dragonheart Sword & Shield
172298750.description: The boldest of the bold, fight with the greedy heart of a dragon.  Swing and lunge at your enemies or press 'Q' to block damage.

101078326.name: Candy Cane Launcher
101078326.description: Need some holiday cheer? Say hello to my little friend! Rapid fire launch candy canes at anyone who stands in your way.  Does 5 damage per hit.

103358098.name: Tom's Beans
103358098.description: Inspired by an advertisement for Apocalypse Rising, a popular ROBLOX survival game, this tin of beans slowly refills 80% of your health. Plus, it gives you a special face decal when chowing down.

244081145.name: DarkAge Naginata
244081145.description: Fight with the strength and power of the DarkAge Ninjas.

173755801.name: Diamond Blade Sword
173755801.description: What cuts like diamond? Nothing. Swing this super powerful sword over your head.  As it sparkles around you, the sword does powerful damage to your foe. If you manage to blox them, they will turn into a diamond as they fall apart.

2435999675.name: Elder Wand
2435999675.description: One of the first hallows created as a bounty. Be sure to watch Fantastic Beasts: The Crimes of Grindelwald on 11.16!

220288951.name: Attack Snake Staff
220288951.description: Click to summon a bunch of snakes around you which slither toward whatever location you desire.

61459592.name: Ne'Kotikoz Incarnate
61459592.description: Trade places with your intergalactic friend (or perhaps fiend?) and shoot fireballs at your enemies.

111518891.name: Orinthian Bow
111518891.description: Get this with the Orinthian Soldier Package - http://www.roblox.com/item.aspx?seoname=Orinthian-Soldier&id=111514918

1119904760.name: Ernesto De La Cruz’s Guitar
1119904760.description: The legendary musician's famous guitar - it still plays like the first day it was strung! Play it with pride and use it to seize your moment, sponsored by Disney's/Pixar's Coco.

159229806.name: Rainbow Periastron Omega
159229806.description: The sword men use to fight angry magical unicorns... in space.

602146440.name: Pizza Sword
602146440.description: Sometimes you cut the pizza, sometimes the pizza cuts you.

430066424.name: Bunch of Balloons
430066424.description: Fill the sky with balloons! Click to release them; they'll float up up and away! Please do not do this in real life- it's not environmentally friendly.

15397778.name: First Aid Kit
15397778.description: It was hard, but you graduated college with a 4.2 GPA and got into a decent med school. Then you slogged through 4 more years of memorizing random facts. THEN you slaved away through 4 years of residency. THEN you got drafted by the army and make $45,000 a year. NOW you run around like mad, flinging medkits at your team mates just trying not to get shot. Yes. Law school was the right choice. You owned yourself.

42321801.name: Hot Chocolate
42321801.description: Warms you up on a snowy day!

172246820.name: Paint Grenade
172246820.description: Pull the pin and throw the paint!

114687223.name: Cinco de Mayo Piñata
114687223.description: Celebrate with this festive piñata!  Drops 1 of 10 surprise items!

84417104.name: Helper Cannon
84417104.description: Even in his demise, still helpful.

1708355542.name: Racing Tractor
1708355542.description: He traded tilling fields for chasing thrills!

24659699.name: Magic Dragon
24659699.description: Little Jackie Paper grew up to be an arsonist. Sad but true.

13478015.name: Skele-tar
13478015.description:
Columbus he set sail to find out if the world was round /
He kept on sailing west until he ran aground /
He thought he'd found the Indies, but he found the U.S.A. /
I know some navigators who can still do that today

53130887.name: RobloTim's RobloHunk Potion
53130887.description: Want to be the next superstar in town? Then this potion is for you! Brewed by our very own RobloTim, this potion make you into a solid weight lifting champion. Huge muscles, strong arms and giving + 100% health and movement speed! Once transformed you can use other gear to fight or show off!

532254782.name: Sword of the Eternal Abyss
532254782.description: Click to slash and double click to lunge. Each hit will do 20-26 points of damage. Hit the 'Q' key to activate this item's special attack.

19703046.name: Christmas Tree Ornament
19703046.description: Shoot these at a Christmas tree to decorate it!

313536525.name: Snoopy Companion
313536525.description: Congratulations you found Snoopy!  Be sure to catch  the Peanuts Movie THE PEANUTS MOVIE in theaters November 6th!

512451831.name: Golden Soccer Trophy
512451831.description: Congratulations on completing the Twitch Challenge brought to you by EA Sports FIFA 17! A true testament to your abilities!

109583771.name: Leprechaun Lucky Sword and Shield
109583771.description: Does a small amount of damage for most strikes.  Occasionally, you'll get lucky and do massive damage!

48596305.name: Confusoray 672
48596305.description: Aim this ray at your enemies and confuse them!  They won't know which way is up...or left or right or down for that matter!

54694311.name: Ruby Encrusted Sword of the Mighty
54694311.description: The Mighty lost his sword many years ago in fierce battle. It is said that he who wields the sword will summon his return and the destruction of all coffee shops.  Yeah - it's a weird legend.

56561593.name: Potion of the Fiery Fists
56561593.description: This magical elixir lets you run quickly to catch up with your opponent. Once you've got him - it's on!

85150452.name: Blue Raspberry Slurpee - A 7-Eleven Exclusive
85150452.description: Cool off with this delicious 7-Eleven Slurpee!  Get a free virtual Slurpee when you redeem a 7-Eleven card in July.

2845988123.name: Pirate Mop
2845988123.description:
Ahoy, mateys! Let’s mop the latrines and swab the deck! Not in that order. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

277955605.name: Throwing Knife Pen
277955605.description: You look like you're about to sign this contract to give away the coveted magical super weapon, but no! You are a secret agent who has a knife disguised as a pen!  Click to remove the cap and then slash all the foes. Click and hold to charge the force of the throw when you release the knife from your hand. A hit will do 40 damage.  The secret weapon is safe... for now.

93136746.name: Telamonster: the Chaos Edge
93136746.description: “The lions sing and the hills take flight. The moon by day, and the sun by night. Blind woman, deaf man, jackdaw fool. Let the Lord of Chaos rule.”

121385193.name: Rubber Chicken Launcher
121385193.description: Launch rubber chickens at your foes to do damage and then transform them into chickens!

325758098.name: Bigfoot Boarder's Board
325758098.description: Part of the Bigfoot Boarder package.

160189629.name: DarkAge Bo Staff
160189629.description: Slash at your foes with a bo staff to do 15 damage.  Show off your extreme prowess by hitting the 'Q' key to activate the special attack - summon a line of deadly purple flames that will flow in any direction you face.

80576967.name: Spray Paint
80576967.description: Spray paint your favorite decals all over the place!

846792499.name: Blue Laser Scythe
846792499.description: The future is blue. Slash this powerful laser scythe to do 30 damage per hit. Click and hold to do some animated swinging to unleash a laser projectile .

193772607.name: Korblox Hunter's Bow
193772607.description: Click and hold to pull the arrow and charge it up to do maximum damage. Part of the Korblox Hunter Package.

14864611.name: Compass
14864611.description: Never get lost in a cave or maze again with this handy compass. Always points due north. A must for tomb raiders everywhere.

635616686.name: Bloxdor's Ray Gun
635616686.description: Speak softly and carry a big ray gun. Fire neon red laser projectiles which instantly vaporize your enemies! Very powerful so it has a pretty long reload. Part of the Bloxdor Champion of the Stars package.

92142829.name: Rayvenge Sword
92142829.description: Get your revenge with the Rayvenge!  This sword makes short work of eliminating your enemies -the first attack removes your opponents limbs and does 27 damage with each subsequent hit doing 9 damage.

21420014.name: Scatterblaster
21420014.description: Think of it as a one-handed shotgun from the future. Good against masses of enemies, especially in tight corridors.

1990272438.name: Wyldfang the Brave Companion
1990272438.description: Now you're a two man wolf-pack.

46362414.name: Ice Potion
46362414.description: It's a slippery slope with this potion.  Even if it's not a slope!

431045523.name: Captain Party Pirate's Attack Parrot
431045523.description: Summon a parrot by your side; he'll fly around nearby and swoop down attacking any nearby foes! Click on enemies for him to attack as well.

483308034.name: Overseer Warlord's Sword
483308034.description: The mighty can take what they want. This mythical blade flames green and does 17 damage per slash.  Double click to dash attack. The mighty magic of this blade protects you from your foes and reduces damage by 20%.

230516405.name: Rainbow Basket of Solitary Omega
230516405.description: Like the cheese, he stands alone.

183346956.name: Halloween Ray Gun
183346956.description: Shoot festive orange green and purple lasers at other players to do 15 damage.

184757948.name: Misfortune's Guardian Blade
184757948.description: Part of the Misfortune's Guardian's package.

184757813.name: Divine Guardian's Sword
184757813.description: Part of the Divine Guardian Package

78005009.name: Blackhole Ray Gun
78005009.description: So you want to defeat your enemies?  Everyone does.  But then you want to take it a step further?  Then you need the Blackhole Ray Gun.  Creates a blackhole and sucks your foes remains into it!

64647631.name: Brain Trap
64647631.description: It's like the Parent Trap, only gross. And with less Lindsay Lohan.

42201538.name: BCX2000 Snowreaper Bazooka
42201538.description: Who's up for a snowball fight?

31839260.name: 8-Bit Throwing Barrel
31839260.description: They'll never get the princess now! MUAHAHAHAHA

99254164.name: billylones' ROBLOX Tablet
99254164.description: Winner: billylones. ROBLOX will be in touch to redeem this prize. Void if sold, traded, or deleted.

163352376.name: Personal UFO
163352376.description: Drive your own personal UFO with up to 8 passengers! Use 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D' or arrow keys to control the direction and 'Q' to raise the UFO, 'E' to lower it. Click and hold to suck up players beneath you into the ship and press 'T' while they are in the beam to teleport players into an open seat on your UFO. Use ' L' to control your sweet UFO lights.

72318993.name: Box Of Chocolates
72318993.description: Life is like a box of chocolates - you never know what you're gonna get.  I'm hoping for super speed.

561842836.name: Everfrost Wizard Staff
561842836.description: Click to summon a massive wall of ice; made of different blocks of ice.

790968791.name: Jack Sparrow’s Compass
790968791.description:
Use the compass of Captain Jack Sparrow to guide you and be sure to see Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Men Tell No Tales in theaters on May 26th!

**Grand Prize will be awarded on May 31st after completion of Event**

65969758.name: Native Bow and Arrow
65969758.description: Fire one arrow or maybe five!

67319385.name: Holidaysplosion
67319385.description: Ever walk into someone's house and think, "Gosh, it's like Christmas just exploded in here!" Now it did.

35366215.name: Roboarm
35366215.description: Your arm will have a blast when wearing the Roboarm. Roboarm blasts off and grabs whatever gear item you aim it at!

241512134.name: Mythic Sword of the Earth
241512134.description: Protect Mother Earth with this mighty sword. Slash away at your enemies and leave behind a quaking trail of earth. 15 - 22 damage per swing. While the sword is equipped, the wielder leaves a trail of broken, quaking earth that causes anyone that steps on it to trip and fall.

1088051790.name: Skele-chucks
1088051790.description: Some people break bones, some people break bones with other bones.

87361508.name: Chimera
87361508.description: This chimera attacks on command – performing one of three attacks – shooting fireballs, shooting poison, or biting. It does some serious damage with 30-60 damage dealt per attack.

38861951.name: Green Epic Sauce
38861951.description: Feeling HOT HOT HOT!  Ouch it's so hot!

471751406.name: Summer Games - Soccer Ball
471751406.description: Life is simple: eat, sleep, play soccer.

147937415.name: Mardi Gras Necklace Shooter
147937415.description: I like to call this my party blaster. Shoot festive items at people and get them to join the party!

139581823.name: Dark Avenger's Sword & Shield
139581823.description: Part of the Dark Avenger Package.

27902388.name: BC Skateboard
27902388.description: Builders Club members know how to ride in style. The blue and orange is on the attack!

82707568.name: Rockin' Axe
82707568.description: Not all guitars are axes, but this guitar most certainly qualifies.

88885539.name: Airstrike
88885539.description: Your foes don't stand a chance when you call your pilot friends for reinforcements!  Use this to call a jet fighter that launches missiles at any area you designate.

1183007628.name: BB-9E
1183007628.description: A mysterious droid in the service of the First Order that surely has a trick or two when it comes to stopping its enemies.

56561579.name: Dark Spellbook of the Forgotten
56561579.description: Learn to cast one of the following spells - The Orb of Onica, The Spikes of Speicla or The Freeze of Fontican.

2605966484.name: Breath of Ice
2605966484.description: Swallow the frost and spit out ice at your foes!

128162713.name: Emerald Knights of the Seventh Sanctum Staff
128162713.description: Use the magical power of Emeralds to immobilize and shock your target!

1145358304.name: Turkey Friend
1145358304.description: Now you have a turkey friend to share all the holiday fun with! Please don’t eat it though. Or feed it any turkey – that’d be weird.

2010630652.name: Virtual Book - Bad Guys
2010630652.description: Read the chapter to see who defeats Dr. Rupert Marmalade!

19704172.name: Snowball Cannon
19704172.description: What happens when you take the idea of having a snowball fight and you use that idea as the basis for a new over-the-top eXtreme sport?! BAM! Snowball Cannon!

302063713.name: Dark Skeleton Scythe
302063713.description: Click to slash, dealing 15 damage. Occasionally, you will spin while slashing, dealing 22 damage. Part of the Dark Skeleton package!

2713323785.name: Power Gloves
2713323785.description: Some people like to talk big and flex, others prefer to settle it in the square. Want to ring the bell? Ding, ding.

306971449.name: Mr. Bones- Skeleton Dog
306971449.description: A very intelligent skeleton dog, which fetches a bone when you toss it. Click somewhere on the map nearby to throw the bone there. He'll fetch it and return loyally to your side!

18210455.name: Four-In-A-Row
18210455.description: Play a quick game of Four-In-A-Row with a nearby player! (Get close to another player and click on them to start a game - they need to accept your challenge for the game to start)

306971294.name: Bat Scythe
306971294.description: Your bat friends will protect you as you defeat your foes with this sweet bat scythe. Hit the 'Q' key to activate the special attack!  When you do - blood-red flames shoot up and out like a fountain, raining upon nearby enemies and dealing around 20 damage each!

193743245.name: Winter Wolf Warrior's Mace
193743245.description: Part of the winter wolf warrior package.  Click to whack your enemy on the head, dealing randomly between 15 and 20 damage.

134111541.name: Dragon Hunter Spear
134111541.description: Part of the Dragon Hunter Package.

2568113462.name: Dragonheart Bow
2568113462.description: Crafted from dragon bones, strung with a unicorn's hair, it is a weapon of untold power...

11999235.name: Spec Alpha Biograft Energy Sword
11999235.description: This sword biografts to your character amps your jumping capabilities. Double click and jump at the same time to superjump. Also, if you get close to anyone, you will positively wreck them. Yes, the future is a dangerous place.

157205818.name: Metal Cog Shuriken
157205818.description: Use your collection of cogs as dangerous shuriken! Each hit does 25 damage.

163348575.name: Classic Plane
163348575.description: You'll go plane crazy for this awesome plane. Jump in and fly around ROBLOXIA.

179369914.name: Halloween Tank
179369914.description: Shoot exploding pumpkins at your foes.

208659734.name: Super Spy Laser Blaster
208659734.description: Left click to unleash a beam of energy that is dynamically lit along its length.  Deals 45 damage per second while the beam is on the target.

83021197.name: RC Tank
83021197.description: This remote control tank comes equipped with real explosives!  Drive around and blow things up.  Your foes will never see you coming!

55301897.name: Baseball Bat
55301897.description: Take me out to the ballgame!

1119905177.name: Coco - Family Portrait
1119905177.description: A reminder of times long past, but memories not forgotten. The most precious prize of all is family so cherish this portrait as if it were your own.

43245080.name: 2011 New Year's Fireworks
43245080.description: Have fun, but always remember to be safe on new years eve!

314534854.name: Lucy’s Psychiatry Booth
314534854.description: Snap out of it! Be sure to catch THE PEANUTS MOVIE in theaters November 6!

71422327.name: Hammer of Eternal Frost
71422327.description: The frost is neverending.  Your life sadly is not.

39258389.name: Anger Management Phone Book
39258389.description: RAAAAAWWWWWWWWWWRRRRRRR!  Phone book makes me so angry!

215448210.name: Mystical Griffin
215448210.description: This mystical creature will fly around you - waiting for your next command.  Click on a target and the griffin will fly to it and attack- doing 35 points of damage.

987005222.name: Nerf Zombie Strike Dreadbolt
987005222.description: The newest and boldest is here! Got archery skills? Let’s see how great your aim is. This is Advertising.

537436448.name: Moana’s Paddle
537436448.description: Bring Moana’s Paddle on your own adventures and use it to ward off evil! Be sure to see Disney’s Moana, in theatres November 23 in 3D!

71037101.name: Dagger of Shattered Dimensions
71037101.description: At first stab, it appears to be an ordinary dagger. But one quick press of the 'Q' key proves it to be something quite different.  Something that shatters dimensions.  Particularly the dimension of time.

743692715.name: iLift Three
743692715.description:
Throwing your weight around this way separates the barbells from the dumbbells. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

319655993.name: Beat Up Super Jank Boombox
319655993.description: This used to play the hits... now we're lucky if it plays anything at all.

2548992615.name: Sea Dragon
2548992615.description: A mighty oceanic steed, perfect for riding in on to save the day! And be sure to see Aquaman, in theaters December 21!

92142841.name: Artemis Bow
92142841.description: The Artemis Bow features two attack modes--you can charge a concentrated death shot that does up to 100 damage, or shoot in rapid fire mode for more arrows that deal 12 damage each.But that's not all - you can also use it to fly! When you jump, the Artemis Bow will grow wings and allow you to take flight.

96669682.name: Danger Dagger
96669682.description: This dagger is perfect for close range combat, this dagger lets you run and strike faster than normal.

61916132.name: ROBLOXIAN Healing Orb
61916132.description: Heal yourself with this glowing green orb.  No need to heal right now?  Drop healing orbs around a game and pick them up as needed. Why green?  Everyone knows that green is the color of healing...duh.

163488515.name: The 7D’s Grumpy
163488515.description: Create your own The 7D game with Disney XD’s Grumpy! Take Grumpy into the game for a surprise & watch The 7D on Monday 7/7 @10A on Disney XD!

98411436.name: Rapid Launch Blaster
98411436.description: I don't fire laser guns often, but when I do, I want to do it rapidly.

35683911.name: Wall Walker
35683911.description: I wish I could summon my own personal anywhere elevator in real life... Uphill is my least favorite direction

108158379.name: Ivory Periastron
108158379.description: The sword men use to fight hippos covered in poisonous snakes... in space.

60888308.name: DarkAge Ninjas: Combat Potion
60888308.description:
The DarkAge Ninjas are masters of hand to hand combat that none but the fiercest of warriors can handle. 

Drink this potion to increase your vitality to two fold, and to learn to spin kick, flash kick and charge kick in the face, decimating anyone who tries to fight you.

221173959.name: Red Panda
221173959.description: Your panda pal will follow you around and attack anyone you click on!  Does 22 damage per hit!

78730532.name: Body Swap Potion
78730532.description: Ever wanted to see what it was like to live as someone else?  Wonder no more!

2190019650.name: Spy All Terrain Vehicle
2190019650.description: Every spy needs a car that’s a boat, and a boat that’s a car.

180518956.name: Halloween Monster Potion
180518956.description: Drink this potion to turn into a random monster.  Who knows what terrifying creature you will be next - ghost, vampire, werewolf, or maybe even a... clown.

1001649855.name: Giant Magnet
1001649855.description: People just seem drawn to me, maybe it's my natural magnetism! Click to pull enemies within 30 studs closer with this powerful magnet.

16726984.name: Pirate's Flintlock
16726984.description: The reason why pirates wear swords is that the firearms of the day where not particularly accurate or effective. You will find that this flintlock excels at mid-range combat, but is quite useless for picking off foes at long range.

101106464.name: Battle Bottle
101106464.description: This bottle is half full...of explosives.

81847570.name: Military Axe
81847570.description: Axe me no more questions, I'll kill no more your spies.

29532089.name: Keith's Vengeance Launcher
29532089.description: Keith has been leaving these angry-looking jars of peanut butter around the office, so we made this gun in his honor. It lobs sticky peanut butter at people, which slows their walkspeed down to a crawl. Then you can move in and get the vengeance you deserve.

183355817.name: Speedy Shoes
183355817.description: Wear these shoes to increase your walk speed to 24. Hit 'Shift' to use your super speed boost!

88146497.name: Clown Bomb
88146497.description: Your enemies will explode with laughter.  Okay maybe they'll just laugh a lot.

295461517.name: Viridian Katana
295461517.description: Sometimes it is easy being green.  Easy to slash through foes, easy to win the battle, easy to win the war.

99130630.name: TheAmazeman's ROBLOX Tablet
99130630.description: Winner: TheAmazeman. ROBLOX will be in touch to redeem this prize. Void if sold, traded, or deleted.

95354288.name: Luger Pistol
95354288.description: The WW2 Luger is an old school war relic that lets you target different limbs for different affects. Shoot a player in the leg, and they'll walk a quarter slower. Shoot them in the arm, and they'll drop their weapon. Body shots do 20 hit points of damage.

2230347432.name: Dog Man Book 5
2230347432.description: Dog Man faces his most formidable foes yet! Get ready for non-stop action and laughs with our heroic hound as he join forces with an unlikely ally

185422295.name: Bloxster 2XZ
185422295.description: 25% faster than the Bloxster 2XH. You fancy!

114690870.name: Dual Plungers
114690870.description: Click and hold to become a plunger firing machine!

12187431.name: Sand Tempest Scimitar
12187431.description: In the lost desert kingdoms, three things are eternal: fire, sand, and steel.

315617026.name: Dual Monster Axes
315617026.description: Sling these at your foes to do some major damage! You'll do 12 to 17 damage when you slash you foes and 25 points on double slash!

163351579.name: Killer Bee Launcher
163351579.description: Bees?!?  Yes, bees!  Shoot a swarm of killer bees at your foes.  Each shot releases five groups of six bees that will charge at any foes within 25 studs of you.

15470222.name: Gridiron Guitar
15470222.description: A unique guitar that says "No!" to good taste.

57229337.name: Instamatic Tent
57229337.description: Tent - activate!  Bam - you've got a tent.  No messing around with poles and stakes for you!

330296114.name: Christmas Tree Launcher
330296114.description: Launch miniature Christmas trees, and watch as they instantly become full size!

2163551089.name: Bluesteel Crossbow
2163551089.description: A heavy crossbow with a mighty shot.

433923430.name: BFG Butterfly Net
433923430.description: Watch the enchanting butterflies fly around the net as you try to capture your dreams.

206798405.name: Laser Lava Launcher
206798405.description: This powerful gun unleashes deadly beams of lava directly at your opponent. Click and hold to charge the beam.  The longer you charge, the more damage it deals!

52938493.name: Admiral's Cutlass - A Walmart Exclusive!
52938493.description: Get this for free when you redeem a Walmart gamecard in June 2011!  It is said that the admiral rose quickly throught the ranks because of his superior swordsmanship.  But perhaps it was the sword itself?

257829534.name: Heather's Axe
257829534.description: This weapon has a checkered past in Heather’s hands. Friend or foe, often it’s hard to tell. Not as hard is hitting folk with this axe, though!

1340206957.name: Black Hole Sword
1340206957.description: Slash your foes into a despair so dark that even light cannot escape it.

343586214.name: Rainbow Laser Blaster
343586214.description: Click and hold rapidly fire neon lasers in all the colors of the rainbow.  Each laser does 12 damage on hit.

178400986.name: Star Wars Rebels Chopper
178400986.description: Chopper is a grumpy but loyal droid who is always up for fighting Stormtroopers and the Empire! Get Chopper as your sidekick now and watch Star Wars Rebels Oct 13 at 9P/8c!

11956382.name: Police Baton
11956382.description: Every breath you take / Every move you make / Every bond you break / Every step you take / I'll be watching you.

2535464538.name: Tiger Strike Shuriken
2535464538.description: Quick like a tiger, the six-pointed shuriken will sink its teeth into you before you see it coming. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy! Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

450566409.name: Summer Hang Glider
450566409.description: Soaring through the sky all summer long!

298085284.name: Personal Rocketship
298085284.description: It's like a personal pizza but with no pepperoni and it costs five billion dollars.

1645056094.name: Bad Seed
1645056094.description: This snapdragon snaps back! Click to drop and your plant will take a bite out of anyone close enough to stop and smell the roses.

96501454.name: Lightning Bolt Sword- A Gamestop Exclusive
96501454.description: Your foes will have more than a sword to contend with when you wield this weapon.

10727852.name: Witches Brew
10727852.description: Do the Brew! Shipped direct from the Haunted Hill soda company. Warning: may cause freakish deformities. Warning: may contain actual witches.

97712291.name: hicup789's ROBLOX Tablet
97712291.description: Winner: hicup789. ROBLOX will be in touch to redeem this prize. Void if sold, traded, or deleted.

501753915.name: ): Red Grind Original Flyer Skateboard
501753915.description:
A tool for kickflips, ollies, and grinds? Or a straight up work of art? Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

77443491.name: Sword of Darkness
77443491.description: Dare to reach out your hand into the darkness, to pull another hand into the dark from the light.

928794651.name: Sword of the Waves
928794651.description: If the ocean waves, it's polite to wave back. Click to slash, keep clicking to unleash a watery torrent at your foes.

257838919.name: Heather’s Boots
257838919.description: We stole Heather’s boots. Then, we blamed her dragon and said she ate them. The perfect plan! And now you get boots! (You’re welcome.)

99033296.name: brayden99's ROBLOX Tablet
99033296.description: Winner: brayden99. ROBLOX will be in touch to redeem this prize. Void if sold, traded, or deleted.

218631128.name: Green Laser Scythe
218631128.description: Slash this powerful laser scythe to do 30 damage per hit.  Click and hold to do some sweet animated swinging that will unleash a laser projectile that does damage to anything in its path.

635636907.name: Galactic Soldier's Raygun
635636907.description: Once you're in his sights, he never misses. Rapid fire round laser projectiles; dealing 15 damage per hit. After a while, a short reload kicks in. Part of the Galactic Soldier's package.

152187198.name: Red Rock Star Guitar
152187198.description: "If it's illegal to rock and roll, throw me in jail!" Keep rock alive with the 'Z', 'X', 'C', 'V', and 'B' keys.

1241586595.name: Laser Sword and Shield
1241586595.description: Protect the present with the weapon of the future, lasers!

78665196.name: Katana of the Ninth Moon
78665196.description: Slash until the sun goes down...and then keep going!

170902990.name: Mad Morning Star
170902990.description: Not quite the good morning I was hoping for... Click to swing the mace and do mad damage to your foe.

610133129.name: Fire Breathing Friend
610133129.description: Better be careful what you say around this guy, unless you want to end up extra crispy.

113299620.name: Snake Sniper
113299620.description: Shoot snakes from a snake. Your foes will never see it coming... okay they might.  You are shooting a snake from a snake after all.

190094313.name: Rocket Powered Skis
190094313.description: Click to equip these skis.  Hold shift to use their rocket powered ski boost! Once it recharges at least half way, you can use the speed boost again.

313532207.name: Destinations View-Master
313532207.description: Have you been everywhere, man? Well with this, now you can! Use it to transport yourself from one spot in the game to another. The future is now!

28492363.name: RobloTim's Chavez Burrito
28492363.description: In the same way that RobloTim loves to eat a burrito from Chavez restaurant, you love to help new users! Your place has been voted pretty gosh darn helpful!

230185510.name: Opened Astral Basket from the Lofty Isles
230185510.description: How do we get there? Fly, of course! Inside you find... Astral Isle Wings of Infinite Height.

302281291.name: Tarantula Pet
302281291.description: Click to summon a giant tarantula! A loyal friend, he'll follow you around until you command him to attack your enemy! Then, he'll chase after the enemy, shooting cobwebs at him. Once a web successfully strikes your foe, 25 damage is dealt and a large spiderweb wraps around his head, blinding him and slowing him down for 8 seconds. Now that your enemy is pretty much defenseless, this is when the tarantula goes in for the kill. Charging at your enemy, dealing 15 damage per hit.

36042821.name: Monster Mash Dance Potion
36042821.description: You'll be a graveyard smash with this thrilling dance potion.

57983650.name: Sapphire Blaster
57983650.description: Get the sapphire blaster for free when you redeem a ROBLOX Card from Walmart in August (2011).

261447208.name: ROBLOXworld Contest Trophy
261447208.description: This trophy was awarded to the top 150 finalists in the ROBLOXworld Smooth Terrain Contest on July 6th, 2015. Congratulations to all the winners!

583159170.name: Orbital Violin: Deep Freeze
583159170.description: Play a violin that summons other flaming violins to smite your foes!

20577851.name: Blue Katana of One Thousand Tears
20577851.description: So, often in the course / Of life's few fleeting years, / A single pleasure costs / The soul a thousand tears.

116040770.name: Flashlight
116040770.description: The light follows your mouse around the level to illuminate what lays hidden.

2413755690.name: Petrifying Pumpkin Scythe
2413755690.description: You can't reason with a headless man. Part of the Petrifying Pumpkin package.

133315268.name: 2013 Trick or Treat Bag
133315268.description: Trick or treat. Choice is yours. Makes your character 35% faster. Is allowed in Halloween 2013 game to run faster and collect BLOXikins!

189910262.name: Robloxsai Bike
189910262.description: Now you can bike like Robloxsai!  Control your bike using 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D', or the arrow keys.

317592936.name: Pirate Throwing Axes
317592936.description: Yer foes don't stand a chance when you got yer trusty pirate axes.  Click to throw two hatchets at your foes. Each hatchet does 28 damage. If you're really lucky and both hit, that's a combined 56 total damage!

147143821.name: Orinthian Axe
147143821.description: Swing it at your foes to do Orinthian level damage, or use the special attack to throw a trail of signature Orinthian blue deathbricks.

359179463.name: Year of the Monkey Lantern
359179463.description: Celebrate the year of the monkey with this awesome lantern.  The spirit of monkey will protect you!

313532084.name: Wildlife View-Master
313532084.description: Lions and Tigers and Bears, OH MY! Oh wait, those are just virtual projections. False alarm everyone! False alarm.

67747860.name: 2012 Night Rocket
67747860.description: Start 2012 right, light up the night!

2436000243.name: Newt’s Magical Case
2436000243.description: What sort of magic can you find? Aboard the hunt on Roblox to find out. Be sure to watch Fantastic Beasts: The Crimes of Grindelwald on 11.16!

163353363.name: Breakfast Gun
163353363.description: The ultimate in food fight technology!  Hit someone four times to make a waffle face - egg eyes, bacon smile, waffle face.

65979823.name: Magical Turkey Wand
65979823.description: Turn your enemies into the turkeys that they are!

1103011681.name: Nightmare Dragon Slayer
1103011681.description: This mighty blade is full of restless spirits that slowly escape the blade. Click to deal your foes 16 to 22 points of damage. If you successfully blox your foe, they become a skeleton!

2274759555.name: Dollar Sign Skateboard
2274759555.description: Shreddin’ dolla dolla bills, y’all. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy! Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

69947379.name: Illuminating Spear of Revengeance
69947379.description: There are people who will tell you that revengeance is not a thing, but those are people have never felt the way you do.... or they own dictionaries. Revengeance is yours with this spear that both stabs and charges up for a super powerful attack.

68603151.name: All-Seeing Sentry
68603151.description: These sentries see your enemies so you don't have to!

75556791.name: Duelling Glove
75556791.description: Good sir, I challenge you to a duel!  A slapping duel!

110204666.name: Galaxy Zack: Hello, Nebulon!
110204666.description: Read the first chapter of Hello, Nebulon!, the latest book from the Galaxy Zack series.  This book is available in stores on April 2nd, 2013.

536288166.name: Silver Monkey
536288166.description: Conquer the shrine of the Silver Monkey and use it to run faster.

170896461.name: Beef Wellington Launcher
170896461.description: Burgers are for the common folk, but beef wellington is next level delicious. In fact, they are so delicious that your foes will eat them until it's painful and does damage.

55192815.name: 4th of July Rocket
55192815.description: It's amazing what modern Robloxian pyrotechnics can do!

515688182.name: Nerf Zombie Potion
515688182.description: This is advertising. By the pricking of my thumbs, take this potion and speed up your run.

3600621618.name: RDC 2019 2nd Runner Up Trophy:
3600621618.description: You absolutely rocked the Game Jam at RDC 2019. Congrats on placing in the top 3! We can’t wait to see where your game goes next.

2803762878.name: Aztec Warrior Macuahuitl
2803762878.description: A heavy club with obsidian blades along the side, it really gets your point across. Part of the Aztec Warrior Bundle.

1678349400.name: Radical Purple Keytar
1678349400.description: Is this keytar totally radical? No duh! Just click to slam out a sick jam like a totally righteous dude.

125859385.name: Big Apple Launcher
125859385.description: Launch explosive apples at your foes.  In the city, you must fight to survive!

53623248.name: Builderman's Hammer of Shimmering Light
53623248.description:
Better to light one small candle  
than to curse the darkness.

161216321.name: Homemade Wings
161216321.description: Click to equip- double jump to take flight! You'll soar over ROBLOX with your own homemade wings. Birds got nothin' on you, son!

147143863.name: Darkest Arts Sword
147143863.description: A dark magic possesses this sword. Use it as a sword or use its dark magic to destroy the artifacts of others.

128210518.name: Ace Ranger Axe
128210518.description: Part of the Ace Ranger package.

122278276.name: iLift
122278276.description: Next time someone asks - "Do you even lift?"  You can let them know exactly how much you lift... with a bar bell to the belly.

74904387.name: Lucky Clover
74904387.description: "I'm lookin' over a four leaf clover" at a rainbow.  What's at the other side of the rainbow?  Only one way to find out!

98411325.name: Spec Omega Biograft Energy Sword
98411325.description: Black energy is the heaviest kind of energy.  The sword does some serious damage.

2569022418.name: Twin Space Pistols
2569022418.description: Twice the laser, twice as bright.

987032734.name: Super Spy Drone
987032734.description: In the future everything will be delivered by drone. The future is now. Use the remote control to fly, 'Q' and 'E' to more up or down.

2620452349.name: Jingle Bell Launcher
2620452349.description: Make sure your enemies know the REAL holiday spirit with this launcher!

24785057.name: Marshmallow Chirp
24785057.description: Delicious marshmallow chirps are made from sweet marshmallow with a shiny sugar coating.  They're only here one time a year!

319656339.name: Cuddly Cat
319656339.description: Attack doge has nothing on him! This trusty cat will follow you around and chase away your foes!

10510024.name: Board With a Nail in It
10510024.description: Did they? That board with a nail in it may have defeated us. But the humans won't stop there. They'll make bigger boards and bigger nails, and soon, they will make a board with a nail so big, it will destroy them all!

128160832.name: PE Whistle
128160832.description: Use this PE Whistle to start a vicious game of dodgeball - a game where you have all the balls! Point at an opponent and they will be the target of a bunch of dodgeballs. Each hit does 34 damage.

91360104.name: Stop Hitting Yourself
91360104.description: Your enemies won't be able to stop themselves....from beating themselves up!  Does 10 damage per second.

176087556.name: Leopard Print Balloon
176087556.description: Use this stylish leopard print balloon to jump and float around.

335132838.name: Navy Convertible
335132838.description: Get out of my game, and into my car! To drive use 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D', or the arrow keys. Hit 'X' to toggle headlights and 'H' to honk.

170903868.name: Taco Launcher
170903868.description: It's raining tacos! Not really- more like you're shooting tacos. Fire tacos at your friends and foes. If hit they will take 20 damage as they eat the taco.  Occasionally there is a very spicy taco that will turn the eater bright red!

107458429.name: Throwing Spork
107458429.description: For the suburban ninja in all of us.  Throw these sporks at opponents for a laugh.

2907613658.name: Incendiary Expert Goblin - Bomb
2907613658.description: And boom goes the dynamite. Part of the Incendiary Expert Goblin bundle.

2103276507.name: 8-Bit Restoration Fairy
2103276507.description: Everybody gets one, so use it wisely and listen! This faithful fairy follows you and slowly heals you.

99206970.name: The Merry Avenger Bow
99206970.description: It's a sure shot everytime.  With this jolly bow, your foes don't stand a chance!  This item is exclusively available to users who redeem a card from Gamestop or EB Games in December!

26673760.name: Mariachi Guitar
26673760.description: This is music made for dancing!

149222558.name: Five Kingdoms: Sky Raiders
149222558.description: Adventure awaits in the Five Kingdoms—come and claim it in this start to a new series from the #1 New York Times bestselling author of the Fablehaven and Beyonders series.

162857391.name: Endless Summer Fireworks
162857391.description: Just one click and you're in for a huge fireworks display!  This firework will reload every 5 seconds so the fun never has to stop!.

66896542.name: Annoying Elf: Ostrichsized
66896542.description: He's jolly, but if you click him too often, he might rage! Number one of four - collect them all!

2470982537.name: Imaginary Companion
2470982537.description: When imaginary friends start to become real, when they rattle windows and chains, begin to menace and terrify…Run, for that is no friend.

163348758.name: Victrola
163348758.description: Play that old timey song and create a sonic blast - blowing people back and doing 20 damage.

185422055.name: Inglaciator -6000
185422055.description: Why -6000?  Because it launches an icy sphere of doom that is -6000 degrees.  Click and hold to charge up your icy projectile and release to launch it. When your ice hits - it will create an icy ball that grows over time. Anyone hit by the ice will take 30 damage.  Your foes' chances of survival? Absolute zero.

181245172.name: Monster Radar
181245172.description: Use this item in Hallow's Eve to know which monsters are in the level.  This item only works in Hallow's Eve. Play the game here - http://www.roblox.com/Hallows-Eve-2014-The-Witching-Hour-Returns-place?id=180331551

444457864.name: Sea Sorcerer Staff
444457864.description: Part of the sea sorcerer package!  Shoot bursts of water at your enemies, anybody caught in its path will be dealt 25 to 40 damage

28275809.name: Scythe
28275809.description:
The Scythe has a huge variety of moves.  

 'q' key = swipe left
'e' key = swipe right
click once = normal strike
double click = double strike
"fgh" = spin attack of great doom

119101595.name: Trolladad
119101595.description: You thought trollamon was tough - wait 'til you meet his dad!  Trolladad will summon Trollamon and the two will attack your foes with endless supplies of fried chicken!

157205782.name: Steam Engine
157205782.description: Guide this fancy steam engine towards your foes with the 'W', 'A', 'S', and 'D' keys.  When you get close enough right click to throw dangerous train shrapnel at them! Hit the 'X' key for an explosive surprise.

233520157.name: Grey Bunny Accoutrement
233520157.description: Run fast and jump high like a bunny!

834681176.name: Red LAZER Sword
834681176.description:
Sword meets future laser tech. Just like we always dreamed. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

158069071.name: Rainbow Katana
158069071.description: To be victorious you must fight with all the colors of the wind.  Double click to charge the katana to do double damage.

280661926.name: Mystical Staff of Cyan Lightning Magic
280661926.description: Shoot lightning at your foes with the click of a button. This staff has 4 special attacks in addition to sending lightning speeding towards your foes.  Hit 'x'  to spin with lightning surging around you. Anyone you touch will be knocked back and dealt 10 damage.  Hit the 'q' key to shoot lightning in a straight line in front of you, dealing 40 damage to anyone in its path!  If you're in danger, hit the 'e' key to create a force field of lightning strikes around you forming a circle, keeping your enemies at bay.   Hit the 'z' key to forcefully cast a lightning bolt at your closest enemy (max distance is 45 studs away).

380210977.name: Leprachaun Potion
380210977.description: The leprechaun potion makes you half your normal size and 2x faster!

116040828.name: ROBLOX World Tour Hot Air Balloon
116040828.description: This thing will take you on a world tour of ROBLOX in 80 days or less!  Not really, but it will fly you and a buddy around the level and make you look awesome in your avatar thumbnail.  Our first personal transport vehicle for two!

51347716.name: Noble RedCliff Eagle
51347716.description: To aid in the grand war against the Korbloxian Zombies, the faithful companion of the Knights of RedCliff follows its Master to the battlefield. With the strength of the Zombies ever increasing, the Eagle of RedCliff's help is definitely necessary for any and every Knight.

81330766.name: Time Watch
81330766.description: What time is it?  You decide!

542755101.name: 8-Bit Blaster
542755101.description: Pew pew pew! Shoot neon red lasers at enemies making a pew pew noise!

26777502.name: Mother's Day Card
26777502.description: Tell your mom how you feel about her with the thoughtful mad lib this card produces!

357837444.name: Initiate of Glorious Flight Magic Staff
357837444.description: This super stylish wizard staff shoots neon purple lightning! Click and hold to shoot continuous beams of lightning at for enemies. Part of the Initiate of Glorious Flight package!

156467855.name: Korblox Bone Mace
156467855.description: Each swing of this powerful Korblox mace deals 15 damage. KO 3 players and transform yourself into a Korblox character with a super fast walk speed and extra damage capabilities.

67494312.name: Annoying Elf: ReeseMcBlox
67494312.description: A jolly friend that gives you more speed,  but also gives your enemies more strength.

563288952.name: Rocket Boots
563288952.description: Why walk anywhere when you can rocket there? Equip and the boots appear on each of your feet. Enables you to jump much higher and run a little faster!

2548993638.name: Aquaman's Trident
2548993638.description: A symbol of power and royalty, possession of this is proof of your status as a hero! Also, be sure to see Aquaman, in theaters December 21!

95484098.name: Werewolf Claws
95484098.description: Lunge, slash and dash at your opponents.  At night - become faster and stronger just like the rest of your pack!  These werewolf claws came out of the Gift of Clawed Combat on October 19th. 2012.

36784258.name: Zombie Friend Fred
36784258.description: Friends don't let friends eat brains...so maybe Fred isn't exactly your friend...

150366351.name: Spring Launcher
150366351.description: This fancy spring launcher launches springs that will bounce toward your foes. You'll knock them down in no time at all! Occasionally the spring launcher will launch some deadly flowers.

125013830.name: Scroll of Sevenless
125013830.description: "'That is the weave we must use when fighting Forsaken, Narishma,' al'Thor said, his quiet voice cutting straight through Cadsuane's. 'If we kill them with anything else, they can be reborn. It is a dangerous tool, but still just a tool. Like any other.'"

41855400.name: Christmas Cookie
41855400.description: "Christmas cookies/ oh they're in my belly / Christmas cookies /nothing has ever been so smelly / in a good way"

30847779.name: Magic Ninja
30847779.description: The magic ninja will camouflage you to look like whatever you throw it at.

212641536.name: Golden Super Fly Boombox
212641536.description: Nothin' but the hits.  Play the hottest jams on ROBLOX all over town.

1117745433.name: Giant Kaiju Arms
1117745433.description: Equip this gear to get monster-like arms. Clicking makes you punch, so you're ready for any fight.

188854357.name: Raig Snowman Claws
188854357.description: Doubles your walk speed and does 15 damage per slash. Part of the Raig Snowman's Package.

629893424.name: Bombastic Sword
629893424.description: Your foes will definitely see it coming, but you're so fast it doesn't matter!

18481407.name: Bronze Kopesh
18481407.description: Standard issue for the ancient Egyptian infantry.

89390459.name: Furno's Aquajet Pack and Plasma Gun
89390459.description: Furno's Aquajet Pack and Plasma Gun make it easy for him to fry any villain that gets in his way - especially Jawblade. Now you can fry your enemies too! Play the Lego®Hero Factory game on ROBLOX and win this prize!  http://www.roblox.com/LEGO-Hero-Factory-Breakout-place?id=32373412

160189476.name: DarkAge Nunchuks
160189476.description: Swing these bad boys around by clicking and deal 15 damage.  Dare to double click?  The nunchuks will split in two and do double damage. When equipped, you hold the nunchuks out in front of you in both hands.

1560600467.name: Combat Mop
1560600467.description: I came here to clean house.

50454041.name: Magic Carrot
50454041.description: This carrot packs a major rabbit punch!

243788010.name: Bombo's Survival Raig Table
243788010.description: When Bombo gets mad, he gets really mad, explosively mad!

139577997.name: Festive Sentry
139577997.description: Perfect for when those pesky elves try to sneak up on you!

179625551.name: Haunted Pizza
179625551.description: Take a bite out of this spooky haunted pizza and become a ghost!  You'll get ghost super speed after eating this pizza!

319106687.name: The Dinoboard
319106687.description: Ride into the Bloxgiving festivities in style on this awesome board. Not only good for transport but also for showing off how cool dinosaurs are!

186867693.name: Larry’s Night Guard Flashlight
186867693.description: The Museum comes alive at night! Use Larry’s flashlight to guide your way to the next level and into theaters to see Night at the Museum: Secret of the Tomb on December 19th!

1360078533.name: Red Hover Roped
1360078533.description: We dared to ask, "Could a roped hover?" Now we dare to dream, "What if it were red?"

1469849512.name: Red Carpet Hoverboard
1469849512.description: Now you can hover in style!

23306097.name: Ocean Samurai
23306097.description: The rolling ocean encounters no resistance.

27245855.name: Green Gremlins Paintball Gun
27245855.description: Go green with this awesome paintball gun!

17680660.name: Bat Knight Bat Sword
17680660.description: You would think that you wouldn't need to use the word "Bat" so many times to name a sword.

236442380.name: Gear Recycler
236442380.description: Everything old is new again! Put a gear item in, get a gear item of similar type out!

123234626.name: Stinky Skunk
123234626.description: This stinky guy will knock your foes to the ground!

84012460.name: Fluffy Unicorn
84012460.description: I thought unicorns were more ... fluffy.

88885481.name: Military Dress Sword
88885481.description: Sword of honor, sword of might, strike the right foe tonight.  This sword slashes and lunges.  For a special attack press 'W' twice before striking.

152823669.name: Common Egg Compass 2014
152823669.description: This gear item will only work in the official ROBLOX 2014 Egg Hunt- which is only open for a few more hours.  This item will direct you to the nearest common egg in a level.

109364052.name: Skarra, the Dragonkeeper's Red Sword & Shield
109364052.description: Skarra's trusty sword and shield will keep your enemies on the run! Only available for purchase on an iOS device.

189910707.name: Snowplow
189910707.description: Click on a player to chase them with your snowplow and push them away from you.

201756020.name: Violin Crossbow
201756020.description: Your music is dangerous!  Click and hold to draw and arrow.  Release the mouse to launch your arrow with great force! Each hit does between 20-30 points of damage to your foes.

3381451677.name: Flayed Rats
3381451677.description: These rats are up to something...but what? Stranger Things 3 premieres July 4 only on Netflix.

610133821.name: Flying Dragon
610133821.description: Soar above Robloxia on your beautiful dragon!

245617341.name: TombQuest Book 1
245617341.description: Mummies are waking. New York is overrun with scorpions. And five Death Walkers have broken free. It’s up to one boy to stop them before it’s too late!

2103274863.name: 8-Bit Sword and Shield
2103274863.description: It can be dangerous if you go it alone, you'd better take this.

126710875.name: Ultra-Flat Spray Paint
126710875.description:
Need the side of your building painted with some urban wildside
stylings? This is your paint. Granted to BLOXcon NYC 2013 attendees
who spent $40 or more at the Merchandise store.

226205948.name: Golden Sword of Spring Growth
226205948.description: Spring is here and gold is best. Best your foes by slashing them or by spawning a deadly field of protective poisonous flowers.  Click to slash and do 30-35 damage per hit. Press 'Q' to  spawn a deadly field of white, blue, gold, and violet flowers around you, preventing your enemies from coming up to you. Anyone that attempts to enter the field of flowers will be massively damaged every second they're in it.

1748600996.name: The Unicorn Mace
1748600996.description: This mace is known for dolling out punishment and a great way to fight fire with fire. Now hold tight, it ain’t over till it’s over.

492854717.name: Slime Potion
492854717.description: Obtain this potion for some special power, sponsored by Nickelodeon Kids’ Choice Awards.

22787248.name: Watermelon
22787248.description: I think this should be renamed nomtermelon because it's so delicious.  So far no one agrees with me.

1241585055.name: Elf Launcher
1241585055.description: This is a sure way to get on the naughty list. Fire elf dolls at your foes with this festive launcher.

95354268.name: Trollamom
95354268.description: Trollamom is sure to scare your foes with her deadly "mom glare".  You know the look, one that only moms can give where it feels like they're shooting lasers out of their eyes? Well this mom actually shoots lasers.  But that's not all! After her deadly glare, Trollamom summons Trollamon, who will throw pieces of fried chicken at your enemies. Aren't moms great?

143517948.name: Mr. Peabody & Sherman's WABAC Machine
143517948.description: Use Mr. Peabody’s WABAC Machine to travel back in time & space to wherever you left it. Be sure to catch Mr. Peabody & Sherman in theaters March 7!

15176169.name: Caltrops
15176169.description: An endless supply of spikey little traps that you can use to cover your path.

334620353.name: Nunchucks
334620353.description: A Kung Fu master’s first weapon of choice is their fists. Second is nunchuks. Now get your own today and go see Kung Fu Panda 3 in theatres 1.29.16

114687251.name: Angry Attack Squirrel
114687251.description: This fuzzy little guy attacks at your command!  He'll follow you around and attack anyone you click, doing ten damage per second.

106701564.name: Wizards of the Astral Isles: Rat Plague Summoner
106701564.description: Summon a horde of infected rats to chase your enemies.  One bite and they're toast!

129471170.name: Vanishing Ninja Star
129471170.description: "Your foes won't even know what hit 'em. They won't even see it coming." - Stickmasterluke

73232786.name: Flaming Dragon Slayer Bo Staff
73232786.description: Made from the talons of previously slayed dragons.  How he slayed the first one, I'll never know!

104642700.name: Gear suppressor 777
104642700.description: This will make your enemies speechless. 10 seconds of no tool usage should be plenty of time for you to finish them off.

2470984833.name: Pumpkin Trick or Treat Pail
2470984833.description: No costume is complete without something for storing the night’s haul of candy in!

62350867.name: Outrageous Sword
62350867.description: Fear will turn your enemies hearts to ice.  The sword will turn all of them to gold.

110337910.name: Eggdar - Egg Hunt 2013
110337910.description: This item will only work in the official ROBLOX Egg Hunt 2013 level for the duration of this year's egg hunt.  This item lets you know which eggs are currently in a level.  Use it to find out if a server has rare eggs.

88885524.name: Stun Grenade
88885524.description: The stun grenade causes temporary paralysis to all those in the blast radius, and does 20 damage points to surrounding enemies.

73829202.name: RoMaze
73829202.description: It's romazing.  Unfortunately no one can be told what the RoMaze is. You have to experience it for yourself.

287425246.name: DarkAge Ninja Bow
287425246.description: Click and hold to charge the arrow, the longer you charge, the more powerful the arrow gets. Max damage is between 15 and 55, depending on the charge. Hit 'Q' key to activate the special DarkAge Ninja attack for the ages! This attack rains arrows from the sky around your target.

2470915740.name: Haunted Armor Sword
2470915740.description: One touch and all the power is yours, along with all its drawbacks...Part of the Haunted Armor Bundle.

156467990.name: Overseer Short Sword
156467990.description: Ready to do some serious damage? Hit 'Q' to summon 5 Overseer minions to do your bidding for up to two minutes.

174752186.name: The Sword of Shai
174752186.description: Your destiny awaits!  This sword has five different attacks, each does a varying amount of damage- anywhere from 6-12 points per hit.  One's fate is often not clear - so it's fitting that this sword of fate will will obscure the vision of your foes with a sand storm when they get within 20 studs of you.

579868200.name: Dog Man Unleashed Virtual Book
579868200.description: Dog Man - the crime-biting canine who is part dog, part man, and ALL HERO – is BACK! Read the book to learn more!

1694661592.name: Rockin’ Red Walking Stick
1694661592.description: It's not a cane, its too fancy for that.  Part of the Rockin’ Red Suit package.

162979250.name: Bloxcon Hall of Fame 2014
162979250.description: All you do is win!  This trophy is awarded to winners of ROBLOX's 2014 Hall of Fame. Bask in the glory of being one of the community's top builders!

116040807.name: ROBLOX World Tour Lightning Guitar
116040807.description: ROBLOX is kicking off our world tour and it's gunna be loud!  This slammin' lighting guitar will send lightning at anyone nearby is you can play the notes just right.

135949859.name: Walking with Dinosaurs Speed Egg
135949859.description: This item was awarded to all users who took the Walking with Dinosaurs quiz in the ROBLOX Battle Game. Be sure to catch Walking with Dinosaurs, in theaters December 20th!

21440340.name: Gear of the Week: Paper Airplane
21440340.description: Tip: launch this plane from a high vantage point to get the longest flight possible! Gear of the week, ending on 2/5/2010.

85879456.name: Retribution Ray
85879456.description: The forces of retribution are always listening. They never sleep.

163323379.name: Turbo's Speed Shell
163323379.description: Do you dream of going fast? Grab Turbo's Speed Shell for instant acceleration!

323477973.name: Andromeda Explorer Power Punch
323477973.description: Part of the Andromeda Explorer package! These rocket fists fly forward and slam into your foes.

148017553.name: Mars Mission 1 Blaster
148017553.description: Part of the Mars Mission 1 Package.   http://www.roblox.com/Mars-Mission-1-item?id=144511523

101078559.name: Icy Arctic Fowl
101078559.description: He may be fowl, but he's your friend.  Shoots painful iceblasts that do 25 damage to anyone near you.  Don't get too close to the Phoenix though, he'll melt your frozen friend.

168142394.name: Dual Bacon Daggers
168142394.description: Bacon goes with everything! Even daggers.  Click to swing one of your daggers at your foe and do 15 damage. Double click to do a special bacon attack which does 20 damage.  Wear the bacon crown while using these daggers to do an additional 15 damage.

13477940.name: Rock It Guitar
13477940.description: We're going to party like it's 19999!

97161241.name: Super Stomp Boots
97161241.description: Click a target and BAM - you've jumped there.  If the object is another player, they will take quite a bit of damage from the strike of  your lead Super Stomp Boots.

323192649.name: Tone's Water Polo Ball
323192649.description: Hit it with your player while swimming to have it bounce into the air and away from you. Makes different sounds depending on whether its hit by a player/hit the ground/splashes against water. After two minutes, it pops! No worries, every 30 seconds you can release another into play.

94333296.name: Nightfall Elixir
94333296.description: It's that time of the day when the sun goes down.

563287969.name: Deep Space Raygun
563287969.description: The astronauts recovered this gun from a crater on an uninhabited planet. Was it lost? Or left there on purpose? Click to fire a rectangular projectile, sparks fly trailing behind as it soars through the sky toward its target.

105351748.name: Kittypult
105351748.description: Fire fierce, angry, scratching cats at other players.  Warning - do not try this in real life.

332747438.name: Festive Dual Plungers
332747438.description: Rapidly fire your very own holiday decorated dual plungers!  Each plunger does 14 damage!

334523653.name: Voyagers
334523653.description: Humankind faces the threat of extinction and we need YOUR help to keep the world from going dark. Join the Voyagers now to receive your assignment.

40493658.name: Blueberry Pie
40493658.description: "Apple, peaches, blueberry pie...you we're young and so was I"... wait.  That song isn't about blueberry pie.  It's pumpkin pie...but blueberry pie is so much more delicious!  Why would you write a song about an inferior pie?  Whatever...I'm over it.

406101128.name: Cocoa Guitar
406101128.description: This is advertising. But it is also a really awesome Guitar! Musical and delicious - musilicious, if you will. Let it guide you to the Cocoa Rain!

157205831.name: Steampunk Jetpack
157205831.description: Steam is the power of the future! Use this steampunk jetpack to glide around ROBLOX with ease.

12902404.name: Bundle of TNT
12902404.description: Industrially, TNT is synthesized in a three-step process. First, toluene is nitrated with a mixture of sulfuric and nitric acid to produce mono-nitrotoluene or MNT. The MNT is separated and then renitrated to dinitrotoluene or DNT. In the final step, the DNT is nitrated to trinitrotoluene or TNT using an anhydrous mixture of nitric acid and oleum. Nitric acid is consumed by the manufacturing process, but the diluted sulfuric acid can be reconcentrated and reused. Subsequent to nitration, TNT is stabilized by a process called sulphitation, where the crude TNT is treated with aqueous sodium sulfite solution in order to remove less stable isomers of TNT and other undesired reaction products. The rinse water from sulphitation is known as red water and is a significant pollutant and waste product of TNT manufacture.

55194474.name: Dragonfire Sword
55194474.description: Get this for free when you redeem a game card from Walmart in July 2011!  Forged by the skin of a dragon and the fire of another dragon, The Dragonfire Sword of the Magma Realm is unparallelled in strength.

57983532.name: Volleyball
57983532.description: Get ready for the longest volleyball rally of all time!

342869414.name: BLOXY 2015
342869414.description: This award was given out to the winners of the 3rd Annual BLOXY Awards, honoring the best game creators, builders, artists, and video makers on ROBLOX.

1504917437.name: Blimp Trophy
1504917437.description: Jump higher with the Blimp Trophy as you complete the Nickelodeon Kids’ Choice Awards missions. Catch the show Saturday, March 24 at 8/7c

139586244.name: Cloud 9 Snowboard
139586244.description: You’re the fastest snowboarder around!  You can win this snowboard by playing the Cloud 9 Snowboarding game on ROBLOX – http://www.roblox.com/Cloud-9-Snowboarding-Game-place?id=140438051. The new Disney Channel Original Movie Cloud 9 premieres Friday JaNEWary 17 at 8P.

29959897.name: The Grand Finale
29959897.description: In a ROBLOX fireworks show, this one always goes last.  Because it's clearly the best.

117498775.name: Beehive
117498775.description: Drop the beehive to summon killer bees. The bees do 4 damage on impact and there are 15 clusters doing a total of 60 damage per second.

176087466.name: Zebra Laser Gun
176087466.description: Rapidly fire both a black and white laser to do 5 damage to anyone you hit.  In addition to doing damage, you'll also turn your opponent black and white (depending on which laser he is hit with).

1149573271.name: Marching Drum
1149573271.description: Rhythm is everywhere! Click to let out a radical drum roll, and build tension.

93528414.name: TMNT Skateboard
93528414.description: TMNT Skateboard: Grab a skateboard to ride through the streets of ROBLOX, TMNT style!

15970544.name: Harbinger of Fimbulwinter
15970544.description: Arm yourself in preparation for the Battle for Midgard! Mete out icy punishment with this heavy iron hammer. In the arms of a true Ice God, this weapon becomes especially potent.

146047247.name: Rose Launcher
146047247.description: Talk about a war of roses!  Launch roses, and your foes will surely feel the thorns.

151291980.name: Raig Chair
151291980.description: It's time for your foes to take a seat.... as they get hit by this chair!

48847374.name: Positronic Arm Cannon
48847374.description: From the research labs of scientifically advanced Robloxia comes this attachable cannon to blasts your opponents with not 1, not 2 but 3 fully charged rotating positron charges

101078953.name: RedBLOX
101078953.description: Getting ready to blox all night?  Me too.  Get some extra speed with RedBLOX.

2221406451.name: Momo Companion
2221406451.description: Go on and explore the wonderful neon world with your best pal, Momo and be sure to watch Netflix’s New Movie Next Gen on Friday, September 7.

1144845319.name: Neon Star Fighter Blaster
1144845319.description: Click to blast though the enemies of peace in the galaxy. Part of the Neon Star Fighter package.

2758794374.name: The 6th Annual Bloxy Award
2758794374.description: A prestigious prize granted to winners of the Bloxy Awards, our yearly ceremony honoring the best and brightest of Roblox!

356212933.name: Steampunk Steam Gun
356212933.description: Shoot burning hot steam at your enemies! Click and hold to release steam in the direction of your cursor. The more steam that hits your foes, the more damage you'll do!

27312415.name: Red Foam Finger
27312415.description: Gooooooooooo speed racer! Gooooooooooo speed racer! Gooooooooooo speed racer! Gooooooooooo!

424700938.name: BFG Gobblefunk Dictionary
424700938.description: Gobblefunk is the language of Giant Country. Can you decipher the words in this magical book?

51757158.name: Korblox: Tripmine
51757158.description: These ghastly mines were invented by the Korbloxians to trap anyone and everyone brave enough to ever venture out into the wilds.

42845896.name: Frost Potion
42845896.description: Brr..... it's cold in here.  There must be some frost potion in the atmosphere!

273969902.name: Artichoke Morning Star
273969902.description: "You don't win friends with salad"... or artichokes! Click and hold to spin your deadly artichoke!  Let go to release it and bash any enemies in front of you. This does 20 - 25 per hit.

99797403.name: Make It Rain
99797403.description: Making it rain has never been so easy!  Throw money around like it ain't no thang.  People near you when you make it rain will follow you around to pick money up.

147143848.name: Flaming Mace
147143848.description: Strike your enemies and then light them on fire for extra damage!  Double click for a special fire attack!

271017537.name: Squid Launcher
271017537.description: Launch everyone's favorite squid, Mr.Tentacles at your enemies to obscure their screens in ink while doing 15 damage per hit. The squid will wrap its tentacles around your enemies head and shoot ink in their face!

718234275.name: Dread Dark Wizard Staff
718234275.description: Mighty is the hand that holds this dark power. Click to launch deadly reddish orbs at your enemies; dealing 20 damage each! You can fire up to 6 at a time before being hit with a short cooldown. Part of the Dread Dark Wizard package.

1915020448.name: The Wasp
1915020448.description: It’s time to team-up with The Wasp! And be sure to see Marvel Studios’ Ant-Man & the Wasp, in theaters July 6!

181245219.name: Rapid Candy Launcher
181245219.description: Use this item in Hallow's Eve to rapidly fire candy at those treacherous monsters!  This item only works in Hallow's Eve. Play the game here -

2506347092.name: Skeleton Foam Finger
2506347092.description: Grab this foam finger by the bone!

2261478942.name: Powerful Paintbrush
2261478942.description: Use this weapon combo to spread your imagination, and to vanquish those that refuse to appreciate your artistic endeavors!

155662051.name: Ghost Ship
155662051.description: Launch a deadly ghost ship at your foes to do 60 damage.

223439643.name: Overseer Sword & Shield
223439643.description: Click to swing your sword forward, dealing between 22 and 25 damage. Double click to spawn green flames and lunge forward, dealing double the damage.

999861927.name: Scrooge’s #1 Dime
999861927.description: The first dime that Scrooge McDuck ever earned and his most prized possession! (Probably ought to be handled with care.)

25162389.name: Classic Bucket
25162389.description: I has a bucket.  Nooo they be stealin' my Bucket.  This gear item is awesome for playing tag.

85145680.name: Pararocket
85145680.description: Shoot yourself into space with this awesome pararocket.  Then glide back down with your own parachute!

71597027.name: The Sea's Revenge
71597027.description: These are the tears that launched a thousand ships.  Ghost ships.  Into your enemies.

108875237.name: Sapphire Rapid Fire Shocker
108875237.description: Shock your foes into defeat with this rapid fire blaster!
