56561607.name: Dracovin's Wand
56561607.description: You must have a steady hand to cast the spells with this wand.

834681446.name: Bluesteel Metal Guitar
834681446.description:
The sharp steel might make you think it's a weapon. And it is – a weapon to rock faces off! Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

743692189.name: Skybound Gunblade
743692189.description:
Firing razor-edged knife blades gives new meaning to the term sharp-shooter. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

69964719.name: Trololololo Wand
69964719.description: Turn your enemies into trolls!  They'll be slower and very confused!

229909697.name: Opened Redcliff Basket Of Medieval Rabbit Valor
229909697.description: Sometimes bravery looks like foolishness. Inside you find... Redcliff Rabbit.

90718350.name: Bear Mine Gun
90718350.description: With the Bear Mine Gun, you strategically place two “bear mines” and remotely trigger them to come together at a high velocity for an explosive bear hug, instantly killing anyone caught in the middle.

1981813154.name: Sword of Starlight
1981813154.description: You have the power of stars!

59806354.name: Korblox Evil Eye
59806354.description: The Korblox place their evil eye on walls or even directly on enemies to spy on them at every turn. Then when the moment is right....kaboom!

136172718.name: Festive Tree Present
136172718.description: Part of the Festive Tree Package.  This gear item will spawn different surprise gear items in game.

93722515.name: Halloween Transmuter
93722515.description: Tranform anyone and everyone into spooky Halloween items!

47871635.name: Sonic Boom Tuba
47871635.description: Loud doesn't even begin to describe it.

95484354.name: Misfortune Cookie
95484354.description: It's not going to bring you luck but it might be fun.

537436189.name: Heihei
537436189.description: Moana’s friend, Heihei, will be with you through thick and thin! Be sure to see Disney’s Moana, in theatres November 23 in 3D!

212500257.name: Sharp Shark Sword
212500257.description: Do 15 to 35 damage per swing with this amazing Sharp Shark Sword (say that 10 times fast!)  Click and hold to do the special attack, which will unleash a tsunami, complete with hungry ,that you will ride for several seconds.  Anyone hit by the wave or sharks will take massive damage!

1665541125.name: Cardboard Greatsword
1665541125.description: It can slice and dice like the greatest of swords! Just don’t get it wet. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy! Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

108155504.name: Hot Wheels Spin Shotz Disc
108155504.description: Fuel your need for action with this hyper speed disc!  Launch your SpinShotz disc and watch it spin and give off free bonus health in game!  Learn more about Hot Wheels Spin Shotz at www.roblox.com/sponsoredpage/SpinShotz.

46846074.name: Ninja Darts
46846074.description: Unleash the fury of a million darts on your opponents.  Okay - so you'd have to throw it a few times to launch a million.  But the fury is real?  Yeah...what he said.

83704190.name: Bluster Buster
83704190.description: Harness air power to defeat your foes!  I'm not talking about planes.

47871646.name: Tornade
47871646.description: Toss this to unleash a virtual tornado, that is sure to blow your enemies away!

790968060.name: Wheel of the Black Pearl
790968060.description: The steering wheel of the legendary Black Pearl! Be sure to see Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Men Tell No Tales in theaters on May 26th!

131592085.name: Headless Horseman's New Head
131592085.description: Part of the Headless Horseman Package.

252564167.name: Gamer’s Guide Controller
252564167.description: Picasso had a paintbrush. You? This awesome controller. Tools don’t make the craftsman - but how many famous finger-painters do you know?

11452821.name: Claymore
11452821.description: Favored sword of the McBlox clan.

456226536.name: Merely's Pink Sparkle Time Hoverboard
456226536.description: Hover over the skies and speed over your challengers, sparkling pink all the way.

2804667002.name: Year of the Boar Lantern
2804667002.description: Happy Lunar New Year! Celebrate the new year with your own ghostly guard boar to protect you.

100469994.name: Danger Mace
100469994.description: Swing this mace for massive damage to your opponent.  If that doesn't keep him away, surely your spiky shoulders will!

1241156565.name: Attack Koala
1241156565.description: Oh he's a grumpy little guy. Faithfully follows you and unloads his frustrations on your foes.

375829909.name: 01010010 Enforcer Sword
375829909.description: Part of the 01010010 Enforcer package!  Click to swing at your foes.

782684707.name: Adventures of Captain Underpants
782684707.description: George and Harold have created the greatest superhero in the history of their elementary school—and now they've accidentally brought him to life!

257343597.name: Neon Octopus Cannon
257343597.description: Click to fire 8 ink shots, one from each tentacle in the direction you click!

60357989.name: Silly Stilts
60357989.description: You'll earn that scholarship to clown college in no time!

168140949.name: Dragon's Flame Sword
168140949.description: Are you the dragon or the dragon slayer?  Use the special key 'E', 'Q', 'G', 'T', 'L' to emit ice-fire from your left arm and throw fire balls at your foes.  If hit, your enemy will be set aflame and and will take 70 damage.

1047877698.name: RDC 2017 Builder's Trophy
1047877698.description: This exclusive trophy was awarded to the top winners of Roblox’s prestigious building competition, which took place during the RDC 2017 Game Jam.

368070589.name: Nickelodeon Blimp
368070589.description: Celebrate the Kids’ Choice Awards with a blimp that’ll super-size your efforts via a power up! Catch the KCAs on Nickelodeon, March 12th at 8pm/7c!

24841520.name: Magic Bunny
24841520.description: Magic bunny wants to help you find eggs that are hiding skyscrapers above you.  When you're holding him you jump extraordinarily high!!!

143606297.name: Team ROBLOX Bobsled
143606297.description: "Enough people say they know they can't believe / ROBLOX, we have a bobsled team!"  Sled all over ROBLOX in your sweet bobsled!

72069827.name: The Break Up
72069827.description: It's called the break up because it breaks things.

51757162.name: Korblox: Berserker's Claymore
51757162.description:
Crafted using their corrupted magic, this claymore is as deadly as it is heavy. Handed down from generation to generation to the mightiest Korbloxian warriors, this legendary weapon was once wielded by Canavus himself. 

With its ability to double its strength in the blink of an eye, this weapon outmatches almost all weapons at close range. Only the mighty knight Xargas is said to have be able to hold his own against this claymore!

99254203.name: Seranok's ROBLOX Tablet
99254203.description: Winner: Seranok. ROBLOX will be in touch to redeem this prize. Void if sold, traded, or deleted.

48159815.name: Shadow Dancer
48159815.description: No enemy stands a chance when you're coming at them with two shadow dancers!

204095670.name: Epic Flail
204095670.description: Think I need a ginger ale. That is such an epic flail!  This flail deals 35 damage per hit and will knock your enemies back by 10 studs. Can't fail with this flail!

292971046.name: From the Vault: Bandit Dog
292971046.description: From the vault of interns past, ROBLOX brings you - this bandit dog! Dued1's dog barks at you!

93722443.name: Skeleton Bone Staff - A Gamestop Exclusive
93722443.description: Why waste ammo when you can use bones?  Fires bones that do damage at your enemies.

236438668.name: Crossbow of the Sea
236438668.description: Shoots magical water arrows that spawn water wherever they hit.

124908832.name: The Londoner's Brolly
124908832.description:
Part of the exclusive Londer package granted to BLOXcon London
attendees who spent £25 or more in the RAF Museum shop on ROBLOX
goods.

24713330.name: Cerulean Vengeance
24713330.description: Revenge is a dish best served cold.

59848474.name: Korblox Deathspeaker's Spell Book
59848474.description: Cast one of three dangerous spells at your enemies - the Knights of Redcliff!

280662667.name: Gigantic Crossbow
280662667.description: They'll know who's boss when you show up with your giant crossbow! Fire huge arrows at your foes to deal 20 damage per hit. Double click to strike your foes with the crossbows blades. This attack will do 30-40 damage per hit.

2535102249.name: Sword of the Raven's Feather
2535102249.description: Light as a feather, sharp as a tack. Slash your foes with the dark power of the raven.

27858062.name: Dance Potion
27858062.description: One sip gives you uncontrollable dance fever!

64869906.name: Captain McGee's Throwin' Axe: A CVS Exclusive Item
64869906.description: They always said he was a strange bird.....

1183007014.name: BB-8
1183007014.description: The chipper, charming droid hero of the Resistance.

63253676.name: Skeleboard
63253676.description: It maybe made of bones but its rock solid! So watch out!

80576913.name: Electric Lightning Trap
80576913.description: It's electric! But contrary to the song...you can see it.

162979146.name: BLOXY 2014
162979146.description: This shiny BLOXY Award is awarded to the few and proud winners of ROBLOX's 2014 International Film Festival.

472607336.name: Turtle Backpack
472607336.description: Any damage dealt to you will be reduced by 40%.

169602103.name: Seranok's Rocket Jumper
169602103.description: Aim at the ground to propel yourself into the air!  Also shoot rockets at people.

330296266.name: Flying Reindeer
330296266.description: Fly high in the sky on your very own reindeer! Use 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D' or the arrow keys to control the direction of flight.

2530753967.name: Snowbot's Cane
2530753967.description: Everyone goes crazy for a sharp dressed snowbot. Part of the Snowbot package.

72644629.name: Lightning Orb
72644629.description: Summon lightning to stun your enemies!

19395497.name: Fruitcake
19395497.description: Fruitcakes are indestructible, and if you try to get rid of one, they just come right back. Maybe you can play catch with it?

121925044.name: Bombo's Bow and Arrow
121925044.description: Killer instincts lead to killer arrows.

143606407.name: Team ROBLOX Skis
143606407.description: Don't french fry when you should be pizzaing! Pizza!  Pizza! BAM.

928796097.name: Aqua Roped
928796097.description: Travel in sea-side style with this hovering Roped.

95951270.name: Korblox Bone & Arrow
95951270.description: It’s a classic longbow, with a certain distinction: it’s constructed of the finest, most durable bone. Take out one of your foes with this weapon and their body instantly turns into a skeleton.

124908320.name: Valiant Adventurer Sword
124908320.description: Get this hood when you get the Valiant Adventurer package. http://www.roblox.com/Valiant-Adventurer-item?id=124908373

153938986.name: Crazy Chicken Bow
153938986.description: Hit your foes with you your crazy chicken arrows. They'll end up with egg on their face and quite a bit of damage.

1427402073.name: Pale Retriever
1427402073.description:
A friendly floating pup who is loyal and spirited. Roll over. Play dead. Good boy. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

154727343.name: Lightning Wand
154727343.description: You control the weather now. Science!  Click your Lightning Rod to fire bolts of lightning in any direction you like.

292046825.name: Magical Unicorn Horseshoe
292046825.description: A ninja star and a boomerang, who could ask for anything more? Part of the Magical Unicorn package.

382837631.name: Opened Faces of Awesome Basket
382837631.description: You are A.W.E.S.O.M.E. Inside you find... Blue-eyed Awesome Face.

325755895.name: Captain Snowbeard's Flintlock
325755895.description: Shoot snowballs at your enemies! Upon impact, the snowball will burst into a bunch of pieces of snow and scatter around the area it hit. Anyone hit is dealt 8 damage, and snow obscures their vision by covering their screen temporarily! This item is part of the Captain Snowbeard package.

257343434.name: Crocopal
257343434.description: One click will have your foes running from this adorably vicious crocodile pal.

2008155070.name: RDC Participation Award 2018
2008155070.description: Thank you for participating in the 2018 RDC Game Jam!

522586178.name: Zombie Attack Bunny
522586178.description: You're nobody till somebunny bites you. Summon a zombie bunny by your side that will hop after and attack enemy that gets too close. He's loyal and will walk wherever you click nearby and attack anybody you wish!

1427401206.name: Green Hyperlaser Gun
1427401206.description:
Blast your enemies with a handy energy weapon, in a color that says, "Go!" Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

172246669.name: Paintball Pro
172246669.description: You are allied with no team.  You shoot for you.

77443461.name: Sword of Light
77443461.description: "Who is more foolish, the child afraid of the dark or the man afraid of the light?"

149612243.name: Sword of Unvanquished Snakes
149612243.description: It's said that Saint Patrick rid Ireland of snakes.  What do you think he did with them?  Put them in the sword of course!  Now you can use this sword's special attack to send 15 snakes slithering dangerously towards your foes.  Also functions as a regular sword and does 10 damage per hit.

294950095.name: The Blackthorn Key
294950095.description: Follow the clues. Crack the code. STAY ALIVE. Start reading the adventure for free today.

19704064.name: Ice Staff
19704064.description: Click on a location within 64 studs of your character to create a large wall of ice. The ice is slippery and nigh impossible to climb. Use it to block off corridors and routes of escape!

972187699.name: Future Crossbow
972187699.description: Why are we using a primitive weapon like crossbows in the future? Sometimes to go forward, you have to look backward. And they look really cool.

255800783.name: Golden Shuriken
255800783.description: As graceful as the falling leaves, as fast as the hunted gazelle.

1102656209.name: Bubble Trouble
1102656209.description: The winner of the 2017 Robot Building Contest, sponsored by Dreamworks Voltron! Congratulations to Pastal_Unikitty for the winning design!

29099749.name: Transmorph Ray Gun
29099749.description: Morph other players into objects.  Guy spawnkilling you?  Turn him into a hat, or an apple, or some other crazy thing!

188644205.name: Rapid Fire Snowflakes Shuriken
188644205.description: These rapid fire snowflakes deal 5-10 damage per hit.  If you can hit someone 5 times quickly, you'll freeze them in a block of ice for 20 seconds.

120749528.name: Chiefjustus Gavel
120749528.description: Dispense justice for all with this oversized justice gavel.  Dispense justice even faster with its secret moves!  Not unlike a ban hammer if I do say so myself...

880453518.name: Phantom Forces Combat Knife
880453518.description:
Looking for a fight? This is sharp, intimidating, and shiny. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

30847746.name: Trident
30847746.description: Short range weapon that can also be thrown (double click to throw).

174752400.name: Roman Catapult
174752400.description: Equip this catapult and click to spawn a giant catapult in front of you.  Click again to add a flaming brick to the catapult and watch it launch in any direction you point your mouse!  As it travels through the air it increases in size and will do 35 points of damage to anyone it hits.

66823631.name: Candy Cane Katana - A Walmart Exclusive!
66823631.description: Want some of this candy cane? I didn't think so.

49929767.name: Knights of Redcliff: Sword and Shield
49929767.description: Second only to the infamous Redcliff Archers, the Redcliff Knights who wield the sword and shield, are fast and efficient.  They see their target, and they take him out in 5 swipes or less.

223132403.name: Hot Wheels® Twinduction Car
223132403.description: Guide this Hot Wheels® Twinduction car around all your favorite places. Get it now!

621090617.name: Robot Rock Guitar
621090617.description: Roboboogie. Hit keys: 'Z', 'X', 'C', 'V', 'B', 'N' to play different notes.

467859890.name: Shadow Archer's Bow
467859890.description: Chargeable bow; click and hold to charge. Let go of the mouse button to release, which the arrow will travel in the direction of your cursor. Does 9 to 45 damage depending on how long you charge the bow. Part of the Shadow Archer package.

13745494.name: Turkey Leg
13745494.description: Gobble Gobble Yum Yum! Forks are lame...

106701702.name: Wizards of the Astral Isles: Limb Stretching Spell
106701702.description: Use this ancient script to make your arms ridiculously long.  Then hit people with them!

64647666.name: Cliche Staff of Zombie Infection
64647666.description: You know what happens if this touches you.

61963621.name: Telamax XR71 Shoulder Cannon
61963621.description: The Telemax XR71 Shoulder Cannon is a vital piece in every soldier's arsenal.  Shoot your enemies and revitalize yourself!

21439778.name: Otterhead Shortsword
21439778.description: The pommel is an otter head. That's so weird!

1466353882.name: Lex, the Elf Warrior's Sword
1466353882.description: Some say Lex obtained his blade from the Queen of Crows, others say a family heirloom. Only he knows for sure. Part of the Lex, the Elf Warrior package.

153939072.name: Bunneh Blade
153939072.description: This sword will make you fast as a hasty hare and double your walk speed.  The speed boost makes it easy to catch up to your foes and use the slash or upper-cut attacks.

16979083.name: Flashbang
16979083.description: All players within 64 studs of the detonation point are blinded for several seconds. Use them to your advantage!

273795078.name: Descendants Spray Can
273795078.description: Who’s your favorite Disney villain kid? Show off their mischievous style in celebration of Descendants, premiering July 31 at 8P on Disney Channel.

79446395.name: Toxic Goo Trap
79446395.description: Encase your enemies in toxic goo for fun and profit!  Okay maybe just fun.

2136391608.name: The Seventh Snake Spell
2136391608.description: You gotta loosen your tongue for this and be prepared to spit a lot! Click to summon snakes who will do your bidding.

181245120.name: Candy Bomb
181245120.description: Use this item in Hallow's Eve 2014 to rain deadly treats on your monstrous enemies. This explosive item is bound to add some monsters to your Monster Index.  This item only works in Hallow's Eve 2014. Play it here - http://www.roblox.com/Hallows-Eve-2014-The-Witching-Hour-Returns-place?id=180331551

383608755.name: Categgpult
383608755.description: Ultimate feline power in a tiny explosive shell. Be on the look out for the rogue Tabby.  Anybody close enough will be knocked back and dealt 40 damage.

23155792.name: Radical Orange Skateboard
23155792.description: This free gear item brought to you as part of our current Skate Park building contest promotion!

108149175.name: Dual Darkhearts
108149175.description: It's twice as dark as RGB(0,0,0) and it steals life from your enemies. What more is there to say?

1694623317.name: Red Dread Knight's Sword
1694623317.description: A radiant blade with singular purpose. Part of the Red Dread Knight package.

29345958.name: Vuvuzela
29345958.description: Annoy soccer player, soccer fans, or pretty much anyone else with this Vuvuzela.

80661504.name: Chartreuse Periastron Gamma
80661504.description: The sword men use to fight dinosaurs in space.

2906730676.name: Developer Pizza Launcher
2906730676.description: Get a freshly delivered pizza from a developer participating in the Pizza Party event and earn an awesome prize!

162857268.name: ROBLOX Summer Glider
162857268.description: Soar high above the skies or ROBLOXIA on this stylish- limited time only - glider!

1678314358.name: Crystal Blade: Amethyst Attack
1678314358.description: Use this mighty blade made of one of the world’s most revered stones to smash foes with style.

18482570.name: Scepter of Pharoahs
18482570.description: It shouldn't be necessary for a Pharoah to ever use this tool in combat, since, you know, anyone who wants to get to you has to go through an army of bodyguards. But hey, you never know.

10468797.name: Ban Hammer
10468797.description: For those favored by Telamon. Perfect for when you just have to drop the hammer on someone.

1074742019.name: Mr. Wing
1074742019.description: Sure, dogs may be man's best friend, but who's a ghoul's best friend? Skeleton bats of course. Faithfully follows you, click to have him do a swooping dive!

52180878.name: Ultimate Slide Skateboard
52180878.description: Time to show off as the coolest kid on the block!

190111117.name: Shards in the Code: Season One - Episode 1
190111117.description: Read a sneak peak of Shards in the Code Episode - 1 Volume 1. The battle to save Earth begins online, when an average teenager who loves to build worlds on ROBLOX soon discovers that the real world faces a grave danger that only he can prevent.  Available on Amazon!

152660131.name: Hot Wheels Gold Car
152660131.description: The Hot Wheels Gold car. The number one model for speed, power and performance. 0-60 in 5.4 seconds. Power: 520. Lap Time 1:20:5. Coolness: 10/10

2385192846.name: Throwing Lunchbox
2385192846.description: Cheese sandwiches again? Anyone want to trade? Click to toss your lunchbox at foes and send your sandwiches flying.

280662903.name: Blizzard Striker
280662903.description: Everywhere you go, the freezing snow follows. Anyone who gets close to you while you are wielding this sword will lose health due to the pain of being near your icy cold weapon.  Click to slash at your enemies, dealing around 15 damage per hit. There is a 20% chance your enemy will freeze into a block of ice for 15 seconds. This disables control over his character, making him unable to move and very vulnerable to your frozen attacks.  Let it go, indeed!

332755212.name: Festive Artemis Bow
332755212.description: Because- why not? When fired, arrows leave a candy cane beam trailing behind. Randomly colored ornaments spawn around where the arrow hit. This is one festive range attacked!

29532138.name: Bloxxy Radar
29532138.description: You can't run. You can't hide. You can only get bloxxed. This device displays the location of all players within 300 studs.

49491808.name: Staff of the Raging Storm
49491808.description: The storm that rages within is now external.

90220438.name: Deluxe Hook Shot
90220438.description: This deluxe grappling hook will pull small unanchored object (like other players) towards you.  When used on larger items, it will propel you toward the item or place.

149612167.name: Lucky Laser Gun
149612167.description: This lucky laser will shoot shamrock shaped pain at your opponent and do 10 damage per hit.

68539623.name: Korblox Sword and Shield
68539623.description: The Korblox both fight and defend with stony spikes.

150366274.name: Dual Gravity Coil
150366274.description: Wear these awesome dual gravity coils on your feet for extra spring in your step!

3039392931.name: Eggmin Launcher 2019
3039392931.description: Fires an exclusive egg for all time-traveling, dimension-hopping Egg Hunters. Works only in the Egg Hunt 2019: Scrambled in Time hub world. Catch these Eggmins before they hit the ground and break... fast!

152187131.name: Music Blaster
152187131.description: Music is destroy this generation!  Literally!  This awesome gun shoots your foes to do 10 points of damage - it's music to your ears!  Don't forget to try out this item's special by hitting the 'Q' key.

11563251.name: Fuse Bomb
11563251.description: Someone set us up the bomb! Make your time.

184758255.name: HOT WHEELS® RC Street Hawk™
184758255.description: Ever wonder what it would be like if cars could fly? Now you can take to the skies with Hot Wheels RC Street Hawk. Drive It! Fly It!

54130543.name: Sword Fish
54130543.description: Get it?  Cuz it's a sword...made of fish?

96095042.name: Sorcus' Chair
96095042.description: This is how he rolls...and trolls....  Sorcus' Chair came out of the Surly Gift of Sorcus II on October 26th, 2012.

152824068.name: Rare Egg Compass 2014
152824068.description: This gear item will only work in the official ROBLOX 2014 Egg Hunt.    This item will direct you to the nearest rare egg in a level.

254608905.name: Bladed Ninja Claw
254608905.description: Click to slash at foes with your deadly dangerous ninja claw. Click and hold to charge the claw for an extra dangerous attack.

244082303.name: Homemade Sword and Shield
244082303.description: This mighty homemade sword and shield set is perfect for any warrior.  The sword does 9-12 damage per hit. The mighty shield is activated when you press 'q'. This epic cardboard shield doubles your health and cuts down enemy damage by 50%.

241017568.name: Mythic Sword of the Tides
241017568.description: Time and tides wait for no man. Slash at your enemies, dealing 15 to 22 damage. Water splashes on the sword each time you swing. Double click to dash forward, dealing 25% more damage, increasing the maximum possible damage cap to 33. Hit the 'Q' key to activate its special, which creates 12 deadly waves around you in a circle, which rise from the ground.

25923196.name: Earth Day 2010 Seeds
25923196.description: Planting things is one way you can help reduce your carbon footprint.  It's also a great way to make some awesome hiding places for hide and seek.

566780253.name: Celestial Scimitar
566780253.description: Legend has it this intergalactic artifact was unearthed from beneath the landslide, after the Roblox supernova in the sky.

65079090.name: Dreamwalker's Dagger
65079090.description:
"To die, to sleep— /
To sleep—perchance to dream. / Ay, there's the rub!/
For in that sleep of death what dreams may come, /
When we have shuffled off this mortal coil"

405996670.name: Deep Sea Explorer Octopus
405996670.description: Part of the Deep Sea Explorer package. Click on enemies to throw this octopus at them. Upon contact, they stick to their face, temporarily blinding them by covering their screen with thick black ink.

51346271.name: Bamboo Dart Blowgun
51346271.description: From the infamous Shadow Ninjas of Robloxia comes this blowgun capable of firing 3 deadly darts at insane speeds.

147937377.name: Mardi G-Ray Gun
147937377.description: Shoot Mardi Gras colored lasers at your foe to do some festive damage.

892003497.name: Mimic Cooler
892003497.description: It's just a cooler full of delicious BLOXY Cola...or is it? Fires cans at your enemies to keep them at bay!

335085355.name: Overseer Smashing Hammer
335085355.description: Click to swing this hammer and whack enemies dealing 20 damage per hit.  Double click to bash the hammer against the ground to trip nearby foes. Hit 'Q' to summon half a dozen overseer minions, which will chase after your enemies dealing 10 damage per hit. After 30 seconds, the minions are removed and a 20 second reload kicks in.

85145757.name: American Archer
85145757.description: I claim this block for America! Launch flags with wild abandon.

46846246.name: Panda Friend
46846246.description: He's your friend.  But ask him to dance one too many times and he won't just grin and bear it.

22960435.name: Protest Sign: Noobs
22960435.description: In a mob? You're probably surrounded by n00bs.

151777652.name: Neon 80s Boombox
151777652.description: Part of the Neon Party Guy package.

124472052.name: Riptide
124472052.description: Win Percy Jackson's legendary sword, Riptide, by playing SFOTH: Percy Jackson Sea of Monsters Edition! Catch Percy Jackson: Sea of Monsters in theaters August 7.

16986649.name: Granny's Crossbow
16986649.description: She uses it to hunt wolves.

61916137.name: Chameleon Potion
61916137.description: No it's not a karma chameleon - and thank goodness for that!  This will transform your appearance to be like whatever you click.  Now you see me... now you think I'm a grey baseboard.

52180858.name: Footbag
52180858.description: Have some colorful fun with this colorful footbag! Pull off some cool moves and show it off to your friends! Time to enjoy the summer!

89488524.name: Ghost Minion
89488524.description: Heals you until you are more powerful than you ever were (150 hp).  But don't worry, if you die - he will avenge you!

223785350.name: EKoSS Bow and Arrow
223785350.description: The Emerald Knights are known for their legendary prowess with a bow. This bow and arrow do between 15 to 55 damage, depending on how long it has been charged.

30649735.name: Magnificent Magenta Paintball Gun
30649735.description: Everyone's screen can always use a little more magenta.

98346415.name: Carnagecopia
98346415.description: Slam other players with some pretty explosive leftovers! If you manage to hit 3 or more players, FOODPOCALYPSE mode is activated!  In FOODPOCALYPSE mode you can rapid fire for 10 seconds.

159199229.name: Bruin Mount
159199229.description: Ride in bearly affordable style. This baby bear will take you anywhere you want to go.

184758713.name: Giant Angelic Sword
184758713.description: Strike your foes and do 30 damage. After 5 strikes shoot fire to do an additional 30 damage!

250533235.name: Velociroblox
250533235.description: We bred raptors. Ride around on these clever dinosaurs and race to catch Jurassic World – In Theaters June 12. #TheParkIsOpen

501966315.name: Slime Skateboard
501966315.description: Skate around on this slime-tastic 4-wheel board and see how far you can go!

65868656.name: Blast-a-ton - A Level Up Contest Prize
65868656.description: Use the Blast-a-Ton to shoot all kinds of things at your enemies.  Will it be poison darts, a rabid dog, confetti?  Who knows?

75906942.name: Slappy Salmon
75906942.description: Win this by playing "Welcome to Stoogeville" and being the MVS (Most Valuable Stooge)!  Be sure to catch the Three Stooges Movie - in theaters April 13th.  Check out the game here - http://www.roblox.com/Welcome-to-Stoogeville-place?id=74885275  Tag - 3 Stooges, Moe, Curly, Larry

139577901.name: Festive Periastron Chi
139577901.description: The Sword men use to fight rabid reindeer... in space.

395205750.name: Knights of the Splintered Skies: Lightning Staff
395205750.description: Cast orbs that shoot lightning at your enemies when they get too close! Enemies hit are dealt 20 damage each.

172289170.name: Warrior of the Wood's Sword
172289170.description: Part of the Warrior of the Woods Package.  Each swing does 20, 25, 15, or 30 damage. If you're hit by the sword without it being swung,  Hit Q to make it rain swords to protect you from your foes for 15 seconds.

261762082.name: Hiccup the Dragon Rider
261762082.description: Hero of Berk, the original dragon rider, and champion of humans and dragons alike. That is a pretty solid résumé for a companion.

41855117.name: Battle Sleighs!
41855117.description: Just in time for winter - battle sleighs are here! Let the sleighing begin!

95354304.name: Sten Gun
95354304.description: Fires 500 rounds a minute, with over-sized, 50-round clips. While the strong recoil makes it inaccurate at long ranges, you should be ashamed of yourself if you unload fifty bullets and hit nothing but air. Each bullet does 15 points of damage. Multiply that by 50 rounds and you've got enough damage to defeat more than a couple foes.

169669671.name: Stravant's Lightning
169669671.description: Run like the wind and shoot deadly lightning beams at people. We're always having to tell him no lightning in the office...

292969139.name: From the Vault: Alpaca Plushie
292969139.description: From the vault of interns past, ROBLOX brings you - this giant alpaca! Defaultio's alpaca makes many animal noises and when you drop it, it grows intimidatingly large.

92627975.name: Orinthian Falcon
92627975.description: A noble guardian to help protect you on your quest.  And by protect, I mean attack all enemies.  Circles above you and attacks those enemies unfortunate enough to be selected as his prey.  This falcon is from the future and features 5 different attack modes.

19644347.name: Big Bag of Tix Plus Bomb Equals LOL
19644347.description: It's a big bag of tickets. It's a bomb. It's two things. No. Three things. It's also hilarious!

52625728.name: United States of Rock Guitar
52625728.description: This week, celebrate America in style!  This rockin' guitar plays some sweet tunes!

221241923.name: Emerald Dragon Master Staff
221241923.description: Click and hold to charge this massive dragon roar like blast. Upon releasing your mouse, you lunge forward, launching a deadly blue fireball at your enemies.  When fully charged, the crystal orb located on the staff lights up on fire. Minimum damage is 15, maximum is 100 if charged entirely. There's a 1 second reload in between each swing. Part of the Emerald Dragon Master Package.

3039376170.name: Video Star Egg Launcher
3039376170.description: Find your favorite video star and get an exclusive egg! Works only in the Egg Hunt 2019: Scrambled in Time hub world.

17237692.name: Haunted Cheezburger
17237692.description: Boo!  This cheezburger contains the ghost of another cheezburger.  What happens if you eat a ghost? You'll find out.

1208300505.name: Kylo Ren’s Lightsaber
1208300505.description: The feared weapon of Kylo Ren with three fiery red blades.

119934168.name: Minion
119934168.description: Get your very own Minion today! And don't forget to catch Despicable Me 2, in theaters July 3.

467109371.name: Pete’s Dragon Trophy
467109371.description: Display the trophy as a symbol of your excellence!

2470977704.name: Skeleton Grappling Hook
2470977704.description: When the ghouls and ghosts come after you this will surely prove helpful in making a quick, and dashing, get away.

68354853.name: Annoying Elf: Keith
68354853.description: These elves have a mind of their own!  Keith is no exception.  And he's got matches - I smell trouble...and hot dogs?

63721711.name: Accursed Vampire Bat Hand
63721711.description: Send bats flying towards your enemies.  Not only do they do damage, they come and bring your foe's health right back to you!

34898883.name: Positronic Platform Producer
34898883.description: Has a wall got you down, literally? Combat gravity the old-fashioned way with Positronic Platform Producer! Simply shoot at a wall to create a platform to stand on. Don’t get too comfortable though, as converting energy into mass can still prove to be a bit unstable, especially with walls that contain anchoritium.

1076255449.name: Hulk Hands
1076255449.description: Just make sure to do your breathing exercises if you get too angry. And remember, with great power comes great responsibility, to SMASH!

65954788.name: Redsteel Ranger Ray Gun- A Gamestop Exclusive
65954788.description: Part of the Redsteel Ranger Package.  Check it out here - http://www.roblox.com/Redsteel-Ranger-A-Gamestop-Exclusive-item?id=65957004

172248941.name: Penguin Power Pet
172248941.description: Click on equip to release your new penguin friend.  He will follow you around and if you click he will jump on your back and help you slide around the map.

76262706.name: Superhero Potion
76262706.description: It's a bird, it's a plane, it's a flying Robloxian shooting fireballs?

2620524562.name: Nightmare Guitar
2620524562.description: No stop signs, speed limit / Nobody’s gonna slow me down / Like a wheel, gonna spin it / Nobody’s gonna mess me around

101734094.name: Korblox Flying Oblivion Horn
101734094.description: Korbloxians use this trumpet to summon death from above.  Once the trumpet sounds, Skeletal birds swoop in to destroy the Korblox's foes.

67319408.name: Santa's Jolly Jetpack
67319408.description: Santa's a big guy.  Going down the chimney is easy - getting back up - not so much.  Enter Santa's Jolly Jetpack!

128162639.name: Emerald Knights of the Seventh Sanctum Spellbook
128162639.description: Use the spell contained in this book to help stabilize the warring clans of ROBLOX.  Click to summon a protective shield that you can then fire at enemies.

250407647.name: Star Butterfly’s Magic Wand
250407647.description: We don’t know how this wand works. We asked Star and she doesn’t either. But bad guys want it to take over the universe, so it must be special.

359178822.name: Orinthian Winged Jet Pack
359178822.description: Click and hold to hover.  Move your camera to go up or down!

471830826.name: Summer Games Torch
471830826.description:
The torch is symbolic of each person's ability to shine. 


The torch lights up when you click on it.

392057539.name: Red Retro Robot Ray Gun
392057539.description: Part of the Red Retro Robot package! A ray gun which shoots round laser pellet like projectiles at your enemies!

430065768.name: Deluxe Dance Ray
430065768.description: Shoot colorful rectangular projectiles at your enemies. Players hit will catch dance fever! They'll freeze in their tracks and dance uncontrollably for 10 seconds. They'll dance to one of five all new dances!

112593662.name: Beach Umbrella
112593662.description: Ready to hang on the beach? Pull up a chair. Oh wait - this gear will do that for you.  I like to use it to taunt my foes. Just chillin' out while they're runnin' with swords.

835779898.name: Rockin' Feline Guitar
835779898.description: I love every kind of cat. Press 'Z', 'X', 'C', 'V', 'B', 'N' and 'M' to play. When you press 'M', the guitar will make a meow sound.

2008154280.name: RDC 2nd Runner Up 2018 - Bronze
2008154280.description: Congratulations for being the Second Runner Up at the 2018 RDC Game Jam!

89487934.name: Medusa Head
89487934.description: Turn your enemies to stone for 5 seconds with this frightning Medusa head.

315573586.name: Halloween Bow and Arrow
315573586.description: When equipped you are instantly transformed into a warrior of Halloween!   Click and hold to charge, let go of your mouse button to release. Max charge is 3 seconds, indicated by a tiny black flame which lights up on the arrow. Depending on the percentage of charge, you can deal anywhere from 15 to 85 damage.

91360052.name: Suit Up Gun
91360052.description: Bunny suit up! Dress other players in one of four embarrassing outfits.

51760061.name: Korblox: DeathSpeaker's Zombie Creator
51760061.description: This once powerful wizard dagger, tainted by the DeathSpeaker blood now serves the Korbloxians well! Said to be wielded only by the strongest DeathSpeakers of Korbloxia, the dagger creates a Zombie of its victims and helps its Master do his bidding.

28671909.name: Yellow Card
28671909.description: Unsportmanlike Conduct!  One more time and you're out of here!

96669687.name: Trusty Blade
96669687.description: This well rounded sword is well suited for blocking daggers, but vulnerable to bigger blades.  Does 35 damage per attack.

74385438.name: Gravitron 3000
74385438.description: Toss this to negate gravity for everyone but yourself.

130167063.name: Virtual BLOXcon Power Sword
130167063.description: This sword is part of the Virtual BLOXcon Power Armor package.

67798397.name: Annoying Elf: Finsurf
67798397.description: Finsurf always has his mind on the numbers!  He might annoy you with some graphs, but he will definitely make sure every hit counts- by giving you extra strength!

181550181.name: Axe of the Divine Flame
181550181.description: From the darkest flames, I strike at thee! Click to swing dealing 15 damage, or double click to bash the axe down in front of you, dealing twice the damage to any enemies hit!

1886281601.name: Incredibles 2 Badge
1886281601.description: This is a signet justice and activating it lets you pursue evil even faster! Be sure to see Disney/Pixar’s Incredibles 2, in theatres June 15!

164017027.name: Ranger’s Apprentice: The Ruins of Gorlan
164017027.description: The Battle for Araluen Begins—Join the Adventure! Ranger’s Apprentice: The Ruins of Gorlan by John Flanagan

1609498185.name: Red Laser Scythe
1609498185.description: Red is the future. Slash this powerful laser scythe to do 30 damage per hit. Click and hold to do some animated swinging to unleash a laser projectile.

91517984.name: Terratronic Power Sword - A Gamestop Exclusive
91517984.description: Your opponents don't stand a chance when you've got this sword equipped!

1320966419.name: Dragon Warrior Spear
1320966419.description: Ryuuzoku, the dragon people of the north, are extensively trained in all forms of combat. This spear is awarded only to their fiercest warriors.

65082246.name: Elixir of Dreams
65082246.description: In a dream - you're stronger and faster.  This potion makes your dream a reality. Be careful when holding this potion.  When dropped, it has a very different effect.

129471151.name: ROBLOX Invisicar
129471151.description: The Admin-engineered ROBLOX Invisicar - moving ROBLOXians forward since... earlier today.

172921991.name: Golden Bloxxer
172921991.description: So many KOs, so little time.  This trophy was awarded to the ultimate bloxxers of 2014. Three cheers for the golden bloxxers!  This item will be awarded to the top 1000 competitors in the 2014 Clan Battle Arenas.

501942750.name: Blade of the Dusekkar
501942750.description:
Stand back! This explosive blade is built for battle! Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy! 

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

346686597.name: Rainbowrath: The Avenger
346686597.description: This magical rainbow unicorn blade will mean the end of all your foes. Click to swing the sword dealing 12 to 16 damage. Double tap the space bar to get wings to appear, which you can use to fly while swinging your sword!

96493688.name: Autumn Shuriken - A Target Exclusive
96493688.description: Oh wow - that leaf is travelling fast!  That's because it's not a leaf - it's a deadly shuriken.  Get this item when you redeem a card from Target in November.

76596269.name: Long-Range Proton Crossbow
76596269.description: Damage your enemies with the crossbow of tomorrow, today.

108153884.name: Lucky Clover Hammer
108153884.description: The hammer is lucky, but the nail is not.  Get the Lucky Clover Hammer when you redeem a ROBLOX Card from CVS in the month of March.

53130896.name: HotThoth's Voodoo Doll
53130896.description: Created in his own image, this cuddly doll is enchanted with some ancient magic. Only given to his special apprentices, this doll uses its magic to help its wielder, by increasing health, increasing movement speed and firing fireballs/ice shards at the wielder's enemies

939160890.name: Queen Mab of the Fae's Wand
939160890.description:
Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a ROBLOX toy – coming soon to retail stores!
Check out www.roblox.com/toys to learn more...

880499904.name: The Blade of the Federation
880499904.description: The official weapon used in the Wars of Reunification.

80597060.name: Fake Chartreuse Periastron Gamma
80597060.description: Cheap knockoffs of these sell in the bazaars of New Texas and the across the Outlands

82357079.name: Riot Shield and Billy Club Set
82357079.description: Rioters getting out of control? We'll put a stop to that!

1241587075.name: Personal Plane
1241587075.description: All the freedom of flying without all that meddlesome flight school or pilot's license.

1183008259.name: R2-D2
1183008259.description: This droid has been an invaluable companion to some of the galaxies greatest heroes!

107458531.name: Grim Axe
107458531.description: Beheads your enemies and causes them to walk around headless.  Don't stand too close to the head after the fact, it would be an EXPLOSIVE mistake!

60357959.name: Knights of the Seventh Sanctum: Sword and Shield
60357959.description: With their duty to stabilize Robloxia, they care not for what is right nor for what is wrong, but for stability. They are dangerous beyond belief and their undead nature strikes fear into the hearts of their enemies

170896941.name: Foul Poison Fowl
170896941.description: Shoots poisonous green fire!  Equip the Poison Fowl and watch as it flies around you in a defensive circle, shooting at nearby enemies (25 damage per hit) for as long as five minutes.

445151478.name: 4th of July 2016 Fireworks
445151478.description: Ignite the sky with these festive fireworks!

85145730.name: USA Fireworks
85145730.description: Our most sophisticated firework yet!  Spell out the name of the land that you love (as long as that land is the United States of America).

334620158.name: Baby Bao
334620158.description: A precocious panda and now your student as you begin your path towards martial arts mastery. Go see Bao in Kung Fu Panda 3 in theatres 1.29.16

271017217.name: Seagull Friend
271017217.description: Click to summon three seagull guardians who fly around you with their watchful seagull eyes.  If an enemy comes 60 studs of your character, the seagulls swoop down and they blast your enemies with powerful beams of water! Each blast does 13 damage per hit.

49059364.name: Crate of Snakes
49059364.description: Snakes.  Why'd it have to be snakes?

19397135.name: Jingle Bells
19397135.description: Remember, Jingle Bells are not for hitting.

2463675080.name: Bigfoot Feet Slippers
2463675080.description: Pretty sure these are your size….Equip to move at a blurring speed.

101078911.name: Touchdown Football
101078911.description: What do you do after you score a touchdown?  Spike that ball and dance like there's no tomorrow.

332774000.name: Mavis’s Slushie
332774000.description: Mavis’s favorite discovery in the human world would be this delicious icy treat. Drink it and enjoy the speed boost from the sugar rush!

92627988.name: Orinthian Mace
92627988.description: This is no ordinary mace. Leaves behind a damaging trail of energy everywhere it is carried.

243777016.name: Flaming Staff of the Nefarious Red Wizard
243777016.description: Acts like a flamethrower; click and hold to shoot flames in the direction of your cursor. Part of the nefarious red wizard package!

206136532.name: Giant Dinosaur Feet
206136532.description: Stomp around ROBLOX in these giant dino feet! Every step you take will do 10 damage to nearby foes and knock them back. If you manage to jump on someone's head while wearing these prehistoric bad boys, you'll stomp them until their health is gone.

33866728.name: Drum Kit
33866728.description: Darthskrill's drum kit can be yours!  Rock out like JParty and the Meme Lords with this stylish kit.

118281529.name: Harpoon
118281529.description: Catches small objects and brings them to you.

790967234.name: Ship in a Bottle
790967234.description: A token to remember your many adventures across the sea! Be sure to see Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Men Tell No Tales in theaters on May 26th!

54130559.name: Poseidon's Quake Trident
54130559.description: Shake the land and sea with Poseidon's Quake Trident!

270560835.name: The Bear Stack
270560835.description: Grizzly, Panda, and Ice Bear know how to travel in style – by stacking up and forming a fun bearstack!

304721834.name: Zombie Protest Sign
304721834.description: Let the world know what you think!

2646396550.name: Winter Warlock Wand
2646396550.description: What is this, some kinda trick?! Part of the Winter Warlock Bundle.

45941451.name: Danceblaster 7000
45941451.description: Best way to disarm your foe?  Make him dance!  Anyone who gets hit with the dance ray won't be able to stop the uncontrollable dance fever!

102705430.name: Incinerator 6000
102705430.description: Why 6000?  Because it shoots fireballs that are a solid 6000 degrees of burning power.  Hold the mouse to charge your shot for maximum fire power!  This fire will damage any player it touches - doing 70 damage over 5 seconds.

489196923.name: Xanwood Katana
489196923.description: Who ever heard of a wooden Katana? Click to swing; does 8 damage.

359179120.name: Midnight Motorcycle
359179120.description: Use 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D', or the arrow keys to control this maniac of a motorcycle.

110337853.name: Laser Guided Missile Launcher
110337853.description: Fire missiles that follow your target - press q for extra damage.

1363010936.name: Shuri’s Gauntlets
1363010936.description: Princess of Wakanda, Shuri possesses strength and power to lead. Display your achievements of conquering Roblox Innovation 2018 by displaying these gauntlets.

114020480.name: Pretty Pretty Princess Sceptor
114020480.description: Pretty pretty princesses wherever you go, raging like noobs as they see you.

503955938.name: Advanced Exploding Lab Table
503955938.description: A lab table fit for a senior mad scientist. Click to drop the table where you're standing. A few seconds later, it explodes! The table breaks apart and pieces flung everywhere as well as dangerous chemicals.

36913601.name: Broom
36913601.description: Fly all around town on your sweet broom!  This magic is only available in October so get yours today!

19111894.name: Wood Cabin Snowglobe
19111894.description: Remember when you grew up in a small cabin in the snowy woods of New England? Me neither. But maybe this snowglobe will help you imagine it.

152660258.name: Opened Hazardous Basket of Major Oversight
152660258.description: Buy the basket or don't. Fight with him or against him. It's all inconsequential to the Major.  Inside you find... Major Overseer.

230758501.name: Opened Korblox Basket of the Frozen Dark
230758501.description: Who knew that a basket could contain so much danger. Inside you find... Korblox Grand Marshal.

101854660.name: 2013 Firework
101854660.description: Ready for 2013?  Let everyone know how you feel with this explosive fire flower!

425120575.name: One Man Band
425120575.description: What did the one man band say when his drum rig broke and hit him instead of the drum? "Beats me!"  Equip and click to play a variety of different jazz songs. While walking and playing the mallets swing and hit the drum.

92142950.name: Explosive Super Glider
92142950.description: With the click of a mouse you are airborne. While in the air, you can drop deadly bombs on your enemies. The bombs do 100 damage per hit, but they have a small radius.  Aim carefully.

953518028.name: Birth of the Dragon Nunchucks
953518028.description: Inspired by a true event, the fight that created the myth, the legend. See for yourself in theaters August 25th!

32858741.name: Staff of Crimson Chaos Fire
32858741.description: Ignis Rex once scourged an entire nation with flames, creating in the process the vast glassy field now known as the Obsidian Flat, before he was eventually contained and imprisoned deep beneath the Earth.

2002056831.name: Virtual Book – Harry Potter
2002056831.description: Join Harry in his magical adventures as he discovers who he really is!

102705386.name: Earth's Might Staff
102705386.description: Summon a heavy boulder to drop on your enemies.  If you click and hold, the boulder will gain more force!

1587165780.name: Emerald Knights of the Seventh Sanctum Glaive
1587165780.description: The Emerald Knights of the Seventh Sanctum are greatly skilled with all manner long-ranged weapons.

72644644.name: Quantum Entangler
72644644.description: Create a clone of yourself and then choose to control youself or the clone.  Be careful, when clones are created there is a shock to the entire game!

89203876.name: Celestial Staff
89203876.description: Summon the rage of the skies!

489197999.name: Adurite Alterer of Destiny
489197999.description: "You shoot me down but I won't fall / I am adurite / You shoot me down but I won't fall / I am adurite" Click to slash dealing 14 damage.

109583846.name: Fairy Axe
109583846.description: Your enemies won't know what hit them!  Or how!  Or why!

405991634.name: Captain Rampage Sword
405991634.description: Part of the Captain Rampage Package! A spooky pirate themed sword which you can slash at your enemies. Dealing roughly 17 damage per hit. By double clicking, you shoot an old rusty ghost cannonball in the direction of your cursor. Enemies hit are dealt 65 damage. There is an 8 second reload before you can shoot another.

46132907.name: Checkerboard Sword
46132907.description: Check yourself before you wreck yourself!

97885552.name: Mauser .96
97885552.description: In addtion to damage blows your enemies dangerously far from where they were standing.

409746054.name: Dual Golden Super Fly Boomboxes
409746054.description: Nothin' but the hits.  Play the hottest jams (in fantastic boombox stereo) all over town.

26017478.name: Blue Bloxxers Paintball Gun
26017478.description: Get ready for the bloxxing of a lifetime!

99641902.name: ninjabart122's ROBLOX Tablet
99641902.description: Winner: ninjabart122. ROBLOX will be in touch to redeem this prize. Void if sold, traded, or deleted.

16975388.name: Configuration Tool
16975388.description: A tool for tweaking the Configurations of player made objects

304720206.name: Zombie Penguin Attack Horde
304720206.description: A horde of six zombie penguins! When an enemy is nearby, they'll slide on their bellies over to the enemy, then stand up with their wings out (in traditional zombie fashion) and attack the enemy!

22788064.name: Cobra Star
22788064.description: If the blades don't get you... the snakes will!

109583822.name: Leprechaun Harp
109583822.description: The harp that once through Tara's halls / The soul of music shed / Now hangs as mute on Tara's halls / As if that soul were fled / So sleeps the pride of former days / So glory's thrill is o'er / And hearts that once beat high for praise / Now feel that pulse no more

1469850646.name: Director's Clapboard
1469850646.description: Aaaaand ACTION! Click to clap the boards and push enemies backwards!

55917429.name: Knights of the Splintered Skies: Bow and Arrow
55917429.description: While their strength lies in their speed and mobility, the Knights of the Splintered Skies are no less skillful in their ability to wield the bow. Blessed with purity of light, their arrows pierce through their enemies and lights them in skyfire, slowing them down and doing massive damage over time.

57229371.name: Silly Guitar
57229371.description: Plays a nice silly tune for you - or make up your own tune!

478707595.name: All-Seeing Golem's Hammer
478707595.description: Click to swing and deal 15 damage per hit. Double click to do a powerful hammer slam which will create a massive shockwave.

104642522.name: Roped
104642522.description: Travel around the level on your motorized Roped.

21439991.name: A Very Special Monster
21439991.description: He has big big plans, but small small teeth.

16469499.name: Hi-Velocity Phaser 5700
16469499.description: The Hi-Velocity Phaser 5700 is named for its extreme speed.  The firing speed of this weapon is greater than any weapon in Robloxia which makes it very dangerous and imma firin it!

58574445.name: ROBLOX Portable Game System (RPGS)
58574445.description:
A 2d game in a 3d game?  You betcha!  Controls - : "d" is forward
 "a" is backward
 "w" is jump
 "left click" is shoot

49491781.name: Staff of Celestial Light
49491781.description: Staff of wonder, staff of light, take my enemies dark as night, stop them with your celestial light.

2544549379.name: Fall Periastron Xi
2544549379.description: The sword men use to fight mutated attack turkeys... in space.

83021250.name: The Fiery Sun
83021250.description: Launch the sun up like a toy.  Don't forget to find some shades and a hat though, I hear looking directly at the sun can blind you.

104642550.name: Duck
104642550.description: So cute.  Less cute when he won't stop following you around.

181355844.name: Dr. Gutpunch’s Glove
181355844.description: Dr. Gutpunch is prescribing one thing this Bloxtober: Pain! Roll with the punches with this glove, which came out of the Kirby Buckets Gift Box on October 21st, 2014!

34399428.name: Confetti Cannon
34399428.description: Shoot pure joy at your friends!

152766031.name: Opened Golden Basket of Heroic Adventures
152766031.description: To be a proper adventurer you must have the correct attire. Inside you find... Golden Cloak of Heroic Adventures.

356213494.name: Steampunk Bow and Arrow
356213494.description: Click and hold to charge this semi-rapid fire bow. Does 9 to 32 damage per arrow.

236403905.name: Sinister Korblox Wings
236403905.description: Soar above your enemies (and all of ROBLOX) to remind them you're always watching.

117498849.name: Wasp Wings
117498849.description: Equip this item and get wasp wings that give you speed, and more importantly the ability to charge your enemies with a deadly wasp dash.  Any hit while in wasp dash mode does 80 damage on impact!

1149193369.name: MeeBot
1149193369.description: MeeBot is a smart and creative JIMU ROBOT, a fun companion to bring on all your adventures!

118650365.name: Summer Skate
118650365.description: Wanna know what I'm doin' this summer?  You're looking at it. This sweet board is dynamically lit so that you can even skate after dark.

94233391.name: Ghost Dragon
94233391.description: Let the Ghost Dragon do your bidding!  Flies above you and sends out 100 points of damage on your behalf.

103234296.name: Redrune Raider
103234296.description: This powerful red dragon will follow you around and shoot fiery death balls at your enemies.

2445089071.name: Zombie Hunter Motorcycle
2445089071.description: I came here to fight zombies and drink Bloxy cola, and I just finished my can.

361950297.name: 8-Bit Sword
361950297.description: Slash your foes into 8-bit pixels!  Click to slash and double click to lunge.

1145358579.name: Cornucopia Blaster
1145358579.description: Using this handy dandy device, you are now able to force even your enemies to enjoy your holiday turkey

128160929.name: Book Worm
128160929.description: Use the bookworm to tunnel underground and teleport between locations in a level.

105351720.name: Groundhogger
105351720.description: Use this groundhog friend to dig holes into ROBLOX parts.  Then teleport all over the level by jumping in the holes.  Who knows where you'll end up?

64220933.name: Ghostfire Sword
64220933.description: This super fast sword will put you miles ahead of your opponents. Combine its speed with the damaging Ghostfire, and you're unstoppable!

1144705079.name: Neon Rocker Guitar
1144705079.description: This thing goes to 11...Lay out a solo then toss it away, like a real rocker. Part of the Neon Rocker package.

718258183.name: Attack Racket
718258183.description: They can't hit what they can't touch! Swing this tennis racket, firing flaming tennis balls at your opponent! If hit, the tennis balls deal 20 damage per hit.

1103012605.name: Spider Horde
1103012605.description: Whats better than one spider? Why not three!?

80576928.name: Tee Shirt Cannon
80576928.description: Shoots tee-shirts at your friends and has them wear the shirts you shot.  You can even customize which shirts come out of the cannon.

49052638.name: Deputy Bobby's Cowboy Boots
49052638.description: Sheriff Bobby runs faster and jumps higher than any cowboy in the west. That's why he always gets his man.

64372667.name: Skull Gladius - a CVS exclusive item
64372667.description: You're always ready for some deadly bloxxing with this sword!  Get this sword by redeeming a ROBLOX card from CVS in May.

1062304136.name: Spider-Drone
1062304136.description: A perk of the upgraded Spidey suit is that it comes with this awesome little buddy!

248285248.name: Homemade Motorcycle
248285248.description: Look ma, I made my own motorcycle!  Of course it's safe, it's virtual!

385780758.name: Brown Bunny Accoutrement
385780758.description: Run fast and jump high like a bunny!

161220552.name: Bundle of Fireworks
161220552.description: Light up the night!  Bright, Bright, Bright!

332747874.name: Polar Mount
332747874.description: Ride your very own furry, friendly, polar bear! Use 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D', or the arrow keys to control and hit space to jump. Use the control key to dismount.

66896638.name: Roblox Snowglobe 2011
66896638.description: Make it snow everywhere you go!

68603324.name: Venomshank
68603324.description: Because doesn't he deserve the most painful bloxxing possible?

173812248.name: Staff of Double Disasters
173812248.description: Swing this mighty staff above your head to summon double disasters!  A tornado and tsunami will trouble your foes while you are safe.

292969458.name: From the Vault: Alligator Plushie
292969458.description: From the vault of interns past, ROBLOX brings you - an angry alligator! ZolarKeth's alligator launches into the air and retrieves a basketball from the nether. The alligator then follows the player at a maximum speed of seventeen.

76768897.name: Egg Cannon 9000
76768897.description: The Egglord's personal armament. It ONLY works in the 2012 ROBLOX Egg Hunt level and it allows you spawn eggs for other players to find...

1047878121.name: RDC 2017 Winner Trophy
1047878121.description: This exclusive trophy was awarded to the top three finalist teams during the RDC 2017 Game Jam, honoring their outstanding achievement in Roblox development.

467895641.name: Bruin Fortune Hunter's Sword
467895641.description: A massive sword that you swing with such force that it does massive damage! Each swing it does 28 to 45 damage per hit. A Part of the Bruin Fortune Hunter package.

356213216.name: Gearworks Sword
356213216.description: A swift sword that does 12 to 18 damage per hit. Watch out for the steam though!

105289761.name: Beast Claws
105289761.description: Unleash the beast! Click to fiercely slash with both hands. Character growls and gets a speed boost when attacking.

72644603.name: High Five
72644603.description: I've got a high five with your name on it! Only if your name is 5...

473287763.name: RDC 2016 Game Jam Trophy
473287763.description: Game on! This trophy was awarded to the top three finalist teams in the 2016 RDC Game Jam held in San Jose in August 2016.

880433057.name: Roblox Surfboard
880433057.description: Cruise around the beaches lookin’ hotter than the weather, riding with your surfboard! (Surfboard!)

304719869.name: 10/9 - Zombie Escape Scooter
304719869.description: Zombies are coming and you are going to make it out alive! You knew this was going to happen and were prepared!  Click to throw out some zombie bait (brains) which will divert any zombies chasing you. Then scoot on outta there!

44115185.name: Judge Underwood's Gavel
44115185.description: No you're out of order!  This whole trial's out of order!

51302649.name: Knights of the Splintered Sky: Sword and Shield
51302649.description: The Knights of the Splintered Sky have descended to ROBLOX to help the Knights of Redcliff defeat the evil Zombies.  Are you brave enough to join them?

1241585476.name: Speedy Snow Boots
1241585476.description: Walking across the winter wonderland is a snap in these. Hit 'Shift' to use your super speed boost and leave snowy tracks behind you!

120307951.name: Noir Periastron Psi
120307951.description: The sword men use to fight unendurable black evil crawling with rabid dinosaurs... in space. Users who redeemed two ROBLOX cards from Walmart between June 27th and July 31st were awarded this sword. This is no longer earnable!

419241111.name: Dory Lantern
419241111.description: Congratulations, you found the Dory Lantern. Let it light up your way wherever you travel! Be sure to see Finding Dory in theatres June 17 in 3D

54694334.name: Vilethorn
54694334.description: Wrap your enemies in the vilest of thorns.

155661985.name: Sword of the Seas
155661985.description: Click to slash at your foes and deal 15 damage.  When you are tired of this, unleash the wrath of the waves upon your foes with the special attack key 'Q'

178076749.name: EKoSS Sword and Shield
178076749.description: Swing a fiery green sword at your foes to do some serious Emerald Knights level damage.

12547976.name: Space Sandwich
12547976.description: I want a space sandwich! And NO SPACE MAYONAISE!

25974222.name: Beach Ball
25974222.description: Have a ball with this classic beach toy.

70476451.name: Year of the Dragon Lantern
70476451.description: Light the lantern to invoke the protection of the ancient dragon spirits.  If anyone is foolish enough to attack you while you are surrounded by dragon spirits, well then maybe they get what they deserve.

64870021.name: Autumn's Blade - Sword and Shield - A Target Exclu
64870021.description: The leaves are falling, and so are your enemies!

286526788.name: Black Iron Grappling Hook
286526788.description: When you need a reliable grappling hook, you need black iron. Click to release the grapple, allowing you to grapple on to objects and scale up them.

4771618549.name: Eggphone
4771618549.description: This standard-issue cellular device contains information about your next mission. Good luck, agents!

583007360.name: Snow Knight Lance
583007360.description: Click to jab this at your enemies! Rapidly click to rapidly jab, hitting the enemy more and dealing more damage. Does roughly 15 damage per hit. Part of the Snow Knight's package.

123134886.name: BLOXY 2013
123134886.description: Lights, camera, action! This shiny BLOXY Award is awarded to the few and proud winners of ROBLOX's 2013 International Film Festival.

2222648398.name: DIY Flying Contraption
2222648398.description: Not too shabby for an DIY project, if I can say so myself.

126719120.name: Giant Ape Arms
126719120.description: Equip this gear to get gorilla-like arms. Clicking makes you punch, and any  player you hit with your fists will feel the wrath of the ape king!

40504724.name: Turkey Cannon
40504724.description: Shoots live turkeys!  Now if only we had a water gun that shot cranberry sauce...and ovens?

1466341532.name: Boulder Basher's Club
1466341532.description: He would like to SMASH! Part of the Boulder Breaker package.

97161222.name: Bluesteel Alterer of Destiny
97161222.description: The future of all lays within your hands.  Will you change the destiny of the world for the better?

56561570.name: Confusion's Cauldron
56561570.description: Confuse your enemies motion with this cauldron's powerful potion!

1033136271.name: Interplanetary Light Sword
1033136271.description: It glows with an otherworldly power...

243890860.name: Captain Cyborg Flintlock
243890860.description: Part of the Captain Cyborg Package!

69567827.name: Zephanon Phaser and Shield
69567827.description: In a world where darkness surrounds, there is only one way to remain safe.  This phaser and shield set will serve you well.

815545408.name: Professor Poopypants’ Ray Gun
815545408.description: Will George and Harold succeed in surviving Professor Poopypants’ class? Watch them in theaters on June 2!

2136389582.name: Makeshift Bow
2136389582.description: The finest of bows, crafted by your own hands.

62350846.name: Chief Guardsman Spear
62350846.description: Charge directly at your opponent or take them by surprise with a sideswipe attack.

675323785.name: Dragon Slayer Knight's Sword
675323785.description: Ready your sword for battle! Click to slash and lunge at your enemies! Dealing 16 to 20 damage per hit! Swings very ferociously dealing lots of damage. Upon killing enemies; their limbs turn ash black and burst all over! Part of the Dragon Slayer Knight package.

179369406.name: Creepy Spirit Friend
179369406.description: Click to summon this friendly spirit.  He will follow you wherever you go- lending you strength (and regenerating your health) until it reaches 150 points.

52625744.name: Picnic Basket
52625744.description: Hello pic-i-nic basket!  Activate this picnic basket and get yourself some delicious ROBLOX food!

3459922232.name: 8-Bit Wizarding Staff
3459922232.description: Wham, bam, alakazam! Click to spawn deadly fireballs at your foes.

19111883.name: Wooden Dreidel
19111883.description:
I have a little dreidel /
I made it out of clay /
And when it's dry and ready /
Then dreidel I shall play! /
PS - This dreidel is actually made out of wood, but the dreidel song was obligatory - Spin the dreidel and see how many chocolate coins you win!

292969932.name: From the Vault: Kawaii Cat
292969932.description: From the vault of interns past, ROBLOX brings you - this kawaii cat! Rukiryo's cat will follow you around and listen to your commands. You can tell it to follow and to stay. There's also a special word to make it evolve. Will you find it?

1001653705.name: Futurecycle
1001653705.description: The future is almost now....little bit longer...now. The future is right now. Use 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D', or the arrow keys to control this futuristic motorcycle.

37821008.name: ROBLOX Best Buy Card
37821008.description: To celebrate the release of ROBLOX Cards at Best Buy we're selling a limited edition ROBLOX Card.  In game, it transforms into 1 of several different ROBLOX electronics. For more information about ROBLOX Cards check out http://blog.roblox.com/

228588651.name: Eggstermination Slingshot
228588651.description: Sling eggs at your friends and foes to cover their screen in eggs. It's a great yolk!

346685995.name: Alpaca Mount
346685995.description: Alpaca your bags, you're ready to ride! Equip to spawn in front of you and simply hop on. Walks at a normal pace; however can jump super high.

35684857.name: Fortune Cookie
35684857.description: Nom nom nom... A mysterious stranger will be the key to my success?  Silly cookie...cookies are for eating...not prophesying...

2045764727.name: Robo Blaster
2045764727.description: This beauty is from the year 3050, and is banned in six star systems. But not this one.

491599826.name: Dog Man Virtual Book
491599826.description: It's Dog Man, the crime-biting canine who is part dog, part man, and ALL HERO! Read the book to learn more!

420178043.name: Max Crumbly Book
420178043.description: Max Crumbly is the undercover hero his middle school needs. Read the book to find out more.

48596336.name: Subspace Debonair Disguise
48596336.description: One sip of this potion and you're transformed into the nearest player. Your opponents will have fun trying to catch the real you!

91658290.name: Red Futurion Blaster
91658290.description: Part of the Red Futurion Package.

94794847.name: Vampire Vanquisher: Sword and Shield
94794847.description: Where the sword goes the shield follows, through the valley.

21439893.name: The Arabian Nights
21439893.description: "Imagine a thousand thousand fireflies of every shape and color; Oh, that was Baghdad at night in those days."

334620605.name: Rickshaw
334620605.description: The preferred mode of travel for any Kung Fu master! Pull one around today and go see the mighty Rickshaw in Kung Fu Panda 3 - in theatres 1.29.16

183826384.name: Sword of the Lands
183826384.description: Strike a blow for land kind when you use the Sword of the Lands!  Each hit will do 15 damage.  Hit the 'Q' key to create a giant land mass to raise you up towards the heavens and surround yourself with Earth, which you then fire at your foes below.

31314849.name: Barrel O' Monkeys
31314849.description: More fun than a... oh. Nevermind.

169602388.name: Intern Racing Chair 2014
169602388.description: 2014 interns race in style!  Ride this chair around and shoot rockets at your foes, all from the comfort of your ROBLOX office chair.

183665514.name: Axe of Blinding Justice
183665514.description: Chop through your foes, doing 20 damage with each swing of this mighty blade. As you wound your enemies you gain light which you can use to set off a solar energy explosion- doing 45 damage per hit.

211944997.name: Donut Delivery Moped
211944997.description: This stylish pink delivery vehicle will take you anywhere you want to go.  Click to eat some of your donut inventory.

14516975.name: Super-G LS33 Disruptor
14516975.description: The Super-G LS33 Disruptor is banned throughout the Federation. It's use against other Robloxians is classified as a war crime.

32353654.name: Moonwalk Dance Potion
32353654.description: We are here to change the world!

537435862.name: Pua
537435862.description: Moana’s faithful companion is here to join you on your journeys! Be sure to see Disney’s Moana, in theatres November 23 in 3D!

10831509.name: Knight's Sword
10831509.description: Keep down the peasant uprisings with this gleaming longsword.

49929776.name: Knights of Redcliff: Bow and Arrow
49929776.description: The Knights of Redcliff are well known for their talented archers.  Their unique Redcliff arrows are thought to be especially deadly and are crafted in complete secrecy by only one Redcliff family, that hands down the secret to each generation.

15668963.name: Geolocator
15668963.description: This military-grade geolocator is designed to withstand a 1000 foot fall. It will point true North in any environment, anywhere on the planet, with an accuracy of .0001 degrees...

522587921.name: Zombie STOPing Axe
522587921.description: Stop a zombie attack DEAD in its tracks. Swing this axe at enemies; dealing 15 damage each hit.

47597835.name: Ninja Blink Potion
47597835.description: You blink - you're in a new location.  Yeah - Ninjas are fast!

181469197.name: Giant Skeleton Arm
181469197.description: Swing this spooky magical skeleton arm around.  If you hit another player you'll knock them back to another time!When activated, the player swings the hand around. When the hand hits another player, the affected player is knocked far away from the origin of the hit and makes a slapping sound. Does no damage.

999866560.name: Scrooge McDuck’s Cane
999866560.description: The richest, most adventurous duck in the world always has an awesome sense of style!

61916108.name: Orb Crystal Launcher
61916108.description: Launch your crystals quickly for instant damage. Charge it for a bit and then launch?  Your foe is in a world of trouble.

96669697.name: Giant Blade
96669697.description: This giant blade is extremely powerful and does 45 damage. The blade's weight will slow you down slightly, but  when you're doing this much damage - it's hard to notice.

60888284.name: DarkAge Ninjas: Dual Kamas
60888284.description: Fast and Elegant. Strike at the hearts of your enemies or spin like the hurricane destroying anything and everything in your path!

501755654.name: White Sword Cane
501755654.description:
A cane to steady your gait when walking, and to eliminate your foes when fighting. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

176087597.name: ROBLOX U Frisbee
176087597.description: It's pretty much impossible to get through university without playing some Ultimate.

22971409.name: Nuclear Winter Icicle Gun
22971409.description: Your February 2010 Winter Contest entry was so hot, it was radioactive!

1402322831.name: Sword of Heartsongs
1402322831.description: By the power of my heartsong, justice will be served!

16688968.name: Gravity Coil
16688968.description: Equipping this item cancels 75% of gravity's effect on your character. This allows you to jump extra high, or to fall like a feather from great heights.

176087505.name: Tiger's Wrath Sword
176087505.description: ROAR!  Attack your foes with the speed of a tiger. If you are able to slay 5 foes with this mighty sword, you will be able to use its special Tiger Raig attack- which lets you slash over and over again and creates a red danger circle that will do damage to anyone within it.

3600620380.name: RDC 2019 Participation Trophy
3600620380.description: Thank you for participating in the RDC 2019 Game Jam!

1241586091.name: Spell Book of Ice Cold Revenge
1241586091.description: Revenge is a dish best served cold. This spell lets you deliver vengeance in the coldest form: ice.

103235041.name: Sinister Flying Magic Carpet
103235041.description: Dark magic gives this carpet the ability to fly.  Use it to fly high above other ROBLOX players.

122278149.name: Ro-torcycle
122278149.description: Ride around ROBLOX on your tricked out Ro-torcycle.  Features dynamically lit headlight and sweet rotating wheels.

101078350.name: Holiday Ham
101078350.description: Best way to stay healthy and strong this holiday season?  Enjoy some of this holiday ham!  Doubles your health!

12187348.name: Ronin Katana
12187348.description: A ronin is a samurai with no lord or master. These desperate men often become honorless swords for hire.

186959114.name: Snowman Sword
186959114.description: Slash to do some serious damage (34 damage per hit). If you blox your foe with this sword they are transformed into a snowman!

2261167878.name: Overseer Mage Staff
2261167878.description:
The eye that sees the past, present, and future.
Use it to throw terrible flames at your foes.

395449601.name: Redcliff Armored Dog
395449601.description: Summon your loyal Redcliff Dog. He'll follow you wherever you go and protect you from all danger! He will block damage and help you regenerate health at a faster than normal rate.  At your command, he'll attempt to scare off nearby foes with his ferocious bark.  If they don't heed his warning, he'll attack!

283754518.name: Rock Thunder
283754518.description: Your guitar has the lightning, now it's time to bring the thunder! You're gonna rock this stage. Change the chord using the keys, 'Z', 'X', 'C', 'V', 'B', 'N', 'M'. Alter the pitch using the keys 'G', 'H', 'J', 'K', 'L'. Hold shift to sharpen the chords. Complete the synchronized pattern of notes special (hit the ctrl key to begin) with at least 75% accuracy to shoot out non-lethal blue lightning.

1191149773.name: Falcon-Pack 9000
1191149773.description: Use the 'W' 'A' 'S and ''D' keys to fly into the sky, and the future, with this next generation shoulder mounted jet pack.

629895007.name: Viridian Throwing Knives
629895007.description: Fine ROBLOXIAN viridian carved to an incredible sharpness. Click to throw theses knives at your enemies dealing 25 damage!

1208300973.name: Rey’s Lightsaber
1208300973.description: A lightsaber with a rich history in the Star Wars galaxy!

261826521.name: Vive Le Minion Sword
261826521.description: Napoleon was convinced he could break the cycle and win a land war in Russia. That was the Minions’ idea. They also said go during winter. Oops.

218634097.name: Hover Roped
218634097.description: The hover technology you have been promised is finally here! Ride around ROBLOX on your very own hover Roped.

257810065.name: Attack Doge
257810065.description: So enemies. Much bark. Wow. For those of you that don't speak doge, click on an enemy to send your attack doge after them!  His bark is worse than his bite- because he doesn't bite! Wow.

147937443.name: Mardi Gras Sword
147937443.description: Laissez les bons temps rouler!  Your enemies don't stand a chance against this festive sword. Celebrate your victory over your enemies with a little confetti party.

300436644.name: Crayola  Carved Crayon
300436644.description: The Crayola Crayon Carver lets you carve anything you want into your crayon! Use this carved crayon to trace the Crayola logo all over ROBLOX!

124128001.name: stickmasterluke's Stick of Power
124128001.description: Spin like the wind and summon it using the Master of sticks power stick! Blast your enemies away and decimate them in 6 different fashions as you see fit.

125013849.name: Taxi
