125013849.description: There's no better way to get around ROBLOX!  Be careful though - if you hit other players it will do damage!

553937189.name: Pizza Kunai
553937189.description: Delicious and deadly. Click to grab kunai and throw up to 5 at once.

135518721.name: Sword of the Bright Knight
135518721.description: For the strong, for the weak, for justice!  This sword has multiple attack modes and does 20 damage points per lunge.

264290413.name: Red ROBLOX Racecar
264290413.description: Part of the ROBLOX Racer package!

397902579.name: Skater's Skateboard
397902579.description: Because a skateboard is a platform to be awesome.  This item came out of the Platformer gift on April 21st, 2016.

30393653.name: Saxophone
30393653.description: Making smooth jazz, one note at a time.

79736586.name: Ruyi Jingu Bang - A Walmart Exclusive
79736586.description: A better bo staff has never existed.

63253706.name: Fiery Bone Trap
63253706.description: Spread these around to ambush your opponents! Trapped into these bone traps they will be decimated by wild fire!

98219158.name: Luckymaxer's ROBLOX Tablet
98219158.description: Winner: Luckymaxer. ROBLOX will be in touch to redeem this prize. Void if sold, traded, or deleted.

492979024.name: Hunter of the Leaves Bow
492979024.description: Part of the Hunter of the Leaves package!  Click and hold to charge the bow; minimum damage is 15 per hit; if charged fully it can do as much as 100 damage per hit!

24440014.name: Springtime Cutlass Of Infinite Virtue
24440014.description: The Prince of Infinite Virtue is in trouble and only you can save him from the evil that surrounds.  Duty calls!

94233286.name: M1 Garand
94233286.description: This M1 includes an eight-round clip, with bullets that deal 35 points of damage to the body and insta-kills for head shots.

42067245.name: The Christmas Creep
42067245.description: You know when you start seeing Christmas stuff in stores in late September. It's HIS fault.

25926517.name: Protest Sign: Blame John
25926517.description:
A typical conversation at ROBLOX HQ 
Brighteyes: "Where's my double hat feature?" Silence... "I blame John."

20721924.name: Spartan Sword
20721924.description: Real Spartans actually hate it when other people argue over what is and isn't Sparta.

173751087.name: ALS Ice Bucket Challenge
173751087.description: Click to dump this ice water on another player, press 'q' to dump it on yourself!  Proceeds will benefit ALS research.

146057771.name: Heart Break Cake
146057771.description: Feed this sweet treat to anyone and they will immediately be so overcome with love that they will stop dead in their tracks!  This cake is really sweet though - so it might make them sick.

117544573.name: Rubyhorde the Rapacious' Treasure
117544573.description: Available as part of the Rubyhorde the Rapacious package.  Get the package by redeeming a $40 ROBLOX card from GameStop in June.

413200176.name: Unlucky Launcher
413200176.description: Shoot bad luck at your competitors by launching broken mirrors, umbrellas, and ladders at them! Upon impact, they trip onto the ground. There is a 30% chance they will temporarily be cursed with bad luck!  If they become unlucky they will suffer one of the following effects: They'll either be tripped nonstop, have a blurry screen, or have their walk speed revered so if they're walking forward, they are actually working backwards!

192537346.name: Penguin Shooter
192537346.description: Left click to fire a baby penguin from the launcher. The baby penguin will jump around, dealing up to 10 damage each second for 10 seconds. You can have 15 baby penguins running around at a time for a full on penguin swarm!

73232803.name: Dragon Slayers Sword and Shield
73232803.description: Protecting the people from dragons is its primary goal.  Whatever else you do with it is your own business.

182273948.name: Halloween Sparkler
182273948.description: Launch a bunch of festive sparkles to celebrate Halloween!

23727705.name: Spec Epsilon Biograft Energy Sword
23727705.description: The superintelligent cloud people of the distant future find the history of human conflict hilarious and ironic. To that end, they created these weapons to sell in museum gift shops as a living reminder of the pinnacle of human stupidity. (WHY DO YOU NEED HAND TO HAND WEAPONS WHEN YOU HAVE LAZORS?!) Because the cloud people are incorporeal, the swords are completely harmless and they allow their young to play with them.

135472231.name: Light Face Melting Guitar
135472231.description: That heavenly sound that will bring the house (and people's faces) down.

2548989639.name: Water Dragon Claws
2548989639.description: Whosoever dons these mighty claws will be bestowed with the power of the mighty ocean.

108149201.name: Dark Falchion
108149201.description: A trusty blade in all storms.

14492601.name: 4-String Roblocaster Premiere Guitar
14492601.description: ROBLOX Brings You...ROBLOX Brings You...ROBLOX Brings You... the most awesome electric guitar ever known to Robloxians!

225921137.name: Lucky Striker
225921137.description: Are you feeling lucky?  This sword does a base damage of 30, but maybe if you are very lucky- you'll do 45.

253518920.name: Cool Punk Kid Guitar
253518920.description: Part of the cool punk package

151311761.name: jmargh's Arm Cannon
151311761.description: Thar be danger ahead!  Shoot cannonballs at your foes. Hold down the mouse to charge the cannon to do maximum damage!

147143881.name: Sword Punch
147143881.description: Wear this mighty blade on your arm and strike your foes with the mighty punch of many pointy things!

29100449.name: Banana Peel
29100449.description: Always slippery in cartoons, but are they ever in real life?  I don't know, but they sure are hilarious!

2385189785.name: Pencil Sword
2385189785.description: Look out, I'm gonna rub you out!

146026944.name: ROBLOX Winter Games 2014 Silver Trophy
146026944.description:
Awarded to the mid scoring levels for dedication across all the Winter
Games, as indicated on the Winter Lodge Leaderboard.

92628074.name: Orinthian Blaster 3777
92628074.description: Blast your enemies into the next galaxy  with the Orinthian blaster.  Does 35 damage per hit.

329021694.name: Simon
329021694.description: The “Brains” of the outfit. With Simon around, you can always count on having a voice of reason to guide you on the right path. Be sure to catch Alvin and the Chipmunks: The Road Chip in theaters December 18!

206136361.name: Prehistoric Piercing Blade
206136361.description: Slash and lunge at your enemies to do 12 to 30 damage per hit.  Double click to jump in the air and tackle your enemy in true prehistoric fashion to do 35 to 60 damage. This blade gains power as you gain KOs. KO 5 other users to transform into a dinosaur and do double damange on all attacks!

236402747.name: Orbital Strike Piano
236402747.description: Call down a piano from the heavens and play to summon more deadly pianos to fall down on your foes.

16641274.name: Illumina
16641274.description: Telamon's favorite weapon from Sword Fight on the Heights. It is light, agile, and deadly.

1213389922.name: Magical Reindeer Throwing Wreath
1213389922.description: Reindeer love to play throwing wreathes, but they aren't very good at it. Toss at your foes for 65 damage. Part of the Magical Reindeer package.

300410436.name: Deluxe Mechatronic Spider
300410436.description: Click to spawn six deadly spiders. They will chase after any enemy daring enough to go near them. They deal five damage per hit, with six deadly spiders that adds up quickly! If close enough, they will shoot lasers from their robotic eye at you!

43245104.name: Jack Frost
43245104.description: He's worse than the Christmas Creep!

87361806.name: Meteor Staff
87361806.description: Let the fires and stones of the sky rain down upon all who dare defy you.  If your opponent gets hit by one of the meteors you summon, he will meet a swift end.  Only you are protected from the shower of debris that will rain down when you summon it.

71422361.name: Sword of the Unseen Eye
71422361.description: Unseeing, yet it sees all. Danger is lurking, where will it strike next?  Only the eye knows.

152832328.name: Faberge Egg Cloner
152832328.description: This gear item will only work in the official ROBLOX 2014 Egg Hunt - which is only open for a few more hours!. This item allows you to select a faberge egg.  If someone earns that rare egg while you are playing with them, you will also get the egg.

90220371.name: Dart Trap
90220371.description: This ancient dart trap will shoot poisonous darts at anyone who crosses its path.  Each dart does 45 damage points.

111876831.name: April Showers
111876831.description: I'm told they bring May flowers... or was it they may bring flowers?

27902406.name: OBC Skateboard
27902406.description: Outrageous Builders Club members love their bolting bling of a black and gold board. Rock on.

50454086.name: Egg Fuse Bomb
50454086.description: Get ready for a serious eggsplosion!

88885506.name: Military Spy Satellite
88885506.description: Use this spy satellite to spy on your enemies, regardless of where they are on the map.  Gives you a birds-eye-view of the map. Click on a location to zoom in and see what's going on there. Press x to leave the satellite view.

63721732.name: Enchanted Bat Flying Potion
63721732.description: Soar above your opponents with this epic bat potion.

427947884.name: Voltron’s Blazing Sword
427947884.description: Take up the sword of Voltron and continue the battle against the evil Galra Empire!

105430216.name: The Archon Blade
105430216.description: Delivering the swift justice of ages gone by.  Get this exclusive blade when you redeem a ROBLOX card from CVS by February 28th.

93136666.name: Sword of the Seven Winters
93136666.description: Summon the blizzard of seven winters, causing snow for you and all around you.  Lucky for you, you knew the blizzard was coming and can move quickly in the snow that slows your enemies.  Does 20 damage.

46846115.name: Ninja Jump Potion
46846115.description: Do some sweet ninja jumping with this ninja potion!

383609201.name: Champion Egg Beater Sword
383609201.description: Used to slay a magical dragon of old. This sword increases the chance of egg drops in PvP mode of the 2016 Eggventure. Click to swing the eggbeater and swipe them with it. While you swing, the eggbeater spins in a circular motion. Does 14 damage per hit.

116693715.name: Memorial Day Fireworks
116693715.description: These glorious fireworks will have you glowing in their sparkles all night long!  These fireworks look great in places with dynamic lighting enabled.

68354832.name: Blizzard Wand
68354832.description: Quit wishing for snow and make it happen...with this wand!    Also shoots icy blizzard balls at anyone near you.

398122525.name: Captain America's Civil War Shield
398122525.description: Vibranium Shield used by Captain America in his fight for justice! After you claim your prize be sure to check out Captain America: Civil War on May 6th!

1665540132.name: Skyboundless Hoverboard
1665540132.description: No boundaries for this board! The sky’s the limit! Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy! Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

48596324.name: Levitating Staff of the Cosmos
48596324.description: Send your enemies flying into the deepest regions of the Robloxian universe.

25545089.name: Ocherous Katana of the Setting Sun
25545089.description: I am anti-life, the beast of judgement. I am the dark at the end of everything. The end of universes, gods, worlds... of everything. And what will you be then, Dreamlord?

1929597345.name: Silver Speedster Convertible
1929597345.description: I mean, I could drive 55. I just don’t want to.

2136411578.name: 26th Century Weapon
2136411578.description: A elegant weapon from the future of the past...

107458483.name: Pompous, the Cloud
107458483.description: Fly this cumulus cloud all over ROBLOX.

3381453136.name: Mike’s Bike
3381453136.description: The perfect set of wheels for hitting up the arcade or fleeing from terrifying monsters. Stranger Things 3 premieres July 4 only on Netflix.

183355892.name: Double Fire Laser Gun
183355892.description: Click to fire two laser pellets. If they hit an enemy, they deal 15 damage. The 'Q' and 'L' keys toggle a light, and the 'X', 'C' toggle crouching and crawling.

132870835.name: Battling Boy
132870835.description: It's one kid vs an entire world full of monsters. And the monsters don't stand a chance. “The adventure of the year.” – Jeff Smith (Bone)  Read the first chapter today!

2008153361.name: RDC Winner 2018 - Gold
2008153361.description: Congratulations on winning first place at the 2018 RDC Game Jam!

53623295.name: Njay's Web Blaster
53623295.description: Everyone knows that Njay writes web code like nobody's business, but did you know he also shoots spider webs that stop people from moving and do some serious damage?

709399046.name: Stone Roped
709399046.description: Old fashioned look meets new fashioned technology. Works with standard roped controls.

144510568.name: Skull Cutlass
144510568.description: Part of the Captain Barnacle Bones package.

93667422.name: Splinter's Staff
93667422.description: Master Splinter is the Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles’ Sensei, teaching them how to fight and protect their home. Unlock his character in TMNT: Turtle Trouble and win his staff!

108148449.name: Leprachaun's Lucky Blade
108148449.description: I wouldn't try to take this guy's gold.  Get this item when you redeem a $10 ROBLOX Card from Gamestop in March.

21392417.name: Tambourine
21392417.description:
Hey! Mr. Tambourine Man, play a song for me, /
I'm not sleepy and there is no place I'm going to. /
Hey! Mr. Tambourine Man, play a song for me, /
In the jingle jangle morning I'll come followin' you.

27471379.name: Battle Wagons!
27471379.description: You're a pioneer, fighting for land and survival.  You've got one problem - other wagons stealing your resources! How do you solve it? Battle Wagons! Battle wagons is played with two Robloxians.  Each places his wagons on a grid that the other player can't see.  Then you guess where the other player's wagons are and fire away.  You sunk my battle wagon!

277955084.name: Mind Controlled Lasers
277955084.description: Fire red lasers from your eyes...well, eye glasses.

357834584.name: Menacing Mage Energy Ball
357834584.description: Click to cast the ball of engergy out of your hand, floating around, following you.  Throw it towards your foes and deal 10 damage per hit.  Let it gain power before clicking and it can do up to 75 damage. Part of the menacing mage package.

99119198.name: Face Melting Guitar
99119198.description: This axe plays guitar solos so epic that they literally melt people's faces.

27477255.name: Red Balloon
27477255.description:
Hast Du etwas Zeit für mich /
Dann singe ich ein Lied fuer Dich /
Von 99 Luftballons /
Auf ihrem Weg zum Horizont /
Denkst Du vielleicht grad' an mich /
Dann singe ich ein Lied fuer Dich /
Von 99 Luftballons /
Und dass sowas von sowas kommt

2045767145.name: Robotic Horse Mount
2045767145.description: These are the steeds favored by space cowboys.

12890798.name: Teddy Trap
12890798.description: So many lulz! You have to be a little clever to figure out the best way to use it... heh heh.

62350856.name: Ghostfire Dagger
62350856.description: Does tremendous damage. If you KO your opponent, you'll steal his extra health.

116040789.name: Mechatronic Spider
116040789.description: All you makers out there will appreciate all the effort that went into making this robotic spider!  Send the spider (and his friends) to attack your foes.

55917432.name: Knights of the Splintered Skies: Ballista
55917432.description: While their capability to melee combat their opponents is only rivaled by the RedCliff Knights, the Knights of the Splintered Skies also make use of some heavy artillery. The ballista, a strong long range powerful artillery, is capable of shooting bolts at ridiculous speed and power, and destroying multiple targets at once. With its hidden ability to fire lit bolts that do constant light damage, the ballista is a powerful weapon indeed.

116693735.name: Fang Of Anansi
116693735.description: "The surest poison is time"... but the second surest poison is contained in the spiders unleashed by this powerful sword. Slash and stab with the blade, or summon spiders to defeat your foe for you.

13206984.name: Wooden Club
13206984.description: Cavemen used these to hunt their prey. I'm pretty sure they needed a bigger one for the woolly mammoths.

98411393.name: R-Orb
98411393.description: Charge a powerful orb and hurl it at your enemies as you fly above them.

264990158.name: Gold Eagle Sword
264990158.description: A very stylish and patriotic sword, which you can run around with, making a red, white, and blue striped trail behind your character! Slash at your enemies, dealing about 20 damage per hit. If you blox someone with this an eagle swoops down from the sky and grabs your enemy and flies him away!

36568384.name: Face Off Potion
36568384.description: This potion creates a spell that hides the castor’s face. Perfect for those days where you just don’t want to face the world. Hold on a second… you’ve got a little NOTHING on your face.

46846024.name: Katana of Destiny
46846024.description: Do you fulfill the sword's destiny or does it help you fulfill yours?

116693764.name: Historic 'Timmy' Gun
116693764.description: This blaster is "favored by soldiers, criminals, police and civilians alike for its ergonomics, compactness, reliability, and high volume of automatic fire."

146071355.name: Heart Balloon
146071355.description: Let your heart soar - as high as this balloon!

221173389.name: Exploding Arrow Crimson Crossbow
221173389.description: This crimson crossbow fires an arrow that sticks to the first thing it hits and explodes after about 2 seconds. The explosion deals between 10 and 110 damage based on how long the arrow was flying through the air.

1903663829.name: Ultimate Summer Soaker
1903663829.description: This little number fulfills all your water war needs.

728205177.name: Spring Saber
728205177.description: Every rose has its thorn. Swing at your enemies dealing roughly 17 damage per hit!

55917409.name: Knights of the Splintered Skies: Morning Star
55917409.description: Just like their fellow Knights of the RedCliff, the Knights of the Splintered Skies are famous for their mastery with the Morning Star, but a lighter and faster version of it. Beware, as this one can break some heads!

674103772.name: Experimental Jetpack
674103772.description: Fresh out of R&D is our Jetpack prototype! Downside: only lets you jump far. Brightside: issue that kept exploding test subjects has been fixed!

569678090.name: Present Launcher
569678090.description: With this, you can fully embrace the spirit of giving by launching gifts at people. If hit, your foes will receive 20 damage!

183347165.name: Halloween Fireworks
183347165.description: Launches 14 fireworks one by one for quite a Halloween show!

427948872.name: Voltron Paladin’s Weapon
427948872.description: Employ the same tech used by the Voltron Squad members to activate a power up shield and block incoming attacks!

89203895.name: Celestial Sword - A Walmart Exclusive
89203895.description: "Many that live deserve death. And some that die deserve life. Can you give it to them?"

507803661.name: 8-Bit Roped
507803661.description: How does it roll when pixels are squares? Use either 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D' or the arrow keys to control the direction it moves. Hit the 'H' key to honk; hit space to jump.

431038614.name: Sword of Glowing Hope
431038614.description: Even in the deepest darkness, there is hope in the flash of my blade. This sword is lit up so it's bright in dark places and slightly glows. Slash at your enemies dealing 17 damage per hit. Upon slashing enemies, sparks emit out of the sword. Anybody killed will burst into neon green flame particles and vanish.

96669943.name: Spartan Sword and Shield
96669943.description: THIS IS ROBLOX!!!!!!!! Use this sword on your enemy and when they have less than 25% health - kick them into a pit of doom.

162857422.name: The Big One!
162857422.description: This is the grand finale of fireworks.  This doesn't load back up so be sure to save it for just the right moment!

159199204.name: Laserface
159199204.description: Rapid fire laser beams directly from your face to your foes.  Each hit does 5 damage, which adds up quickly as you rapidly fire a weapon from your face!

43708943.name: Magmarealm Spear
43708943.description: Spear the magmrealms enemies with this awesome spear.  Fireballs...we don't know what you're talking about!

86494893.name: Darksteel Katana of Ancient Illuminators
86494893.description: It shall not break, it shall not bend. If you think you can avoid its explosion, your time is at an end. Use the 'A' 'W' and 'D' keys to create an explosion that will leave your opponents reeling!

20064349.name: 2010 Fireworks
20064349.description: Always remember, ROBLOX fireworks are fun, but real fireworks are dangerous. Don't play with real fireworks unless a responsible adult is present.

390969719.name: Tix Sword
390969719.description: Tix make this sword more powerful. Click to slash and double click to lunge.

241017426.name: Mythic Sword of the West Wind
241017426.description: May you slash with all the colors of the wind. Slash your enemies, dealing 18 to 33 damage. Enemies also get pushed back from the force of the wind. Hit the 'Q' key, to activate the special attack causing you to spin around in circles and blow away nearby enemies.

97311482.name: Telewarp
97311482.description: Leave a hologram of yourself and then telewarp back to it at any point!

164016477.name: The 7D’s Magical Royal Ruby
164016477.description: Use this Royal Ruby with special healing powers to create your own The 7D game! The 7D premieres Monday 7/7 @10A on Disney XD!

140821168.name: Cloud 9 Snowball Launcher
140821168.description: Launch snowballs and fill up other players screen with fresh powder! The new Disney Channel Original Movie Cloud 9 premieres Friday JaNEWary 17 at 8P.

144980658.name: Happy New Year Horse
144980658.description: The Year of the Horse is a time of fast victories and unexpected adventure.

19396450.name: Santa
19396450.description: We recorded a bunch of santa sounds with Telamon, but those were terrible. So we found a new guy.

16951083.name: Mindgrapes
16951083.description: Mindgrapes are prized throughout the galaxy for increasing neural kinematics, granting incredible reflexes. This enhanced speed comes at a cost, however - your constituion suffers and as a result your body becomes significantly more fragile. WARNING: Mindgrapes are habit-forming. If you are not constantly consuming Mindgrapes, their energy will make you explode. You can't eat just one!

243791329.name: Double Sword Punch
243791329.description: Dual version of the original Sword Punch. Click to slash at your enemies, which does 19 to 26 damage. Double click to do even more damage.

192456288.name: Black Tie Affair Gun
192456288.description: Pick from one of 5 suits and fire them at your friends and opponents.

108234775.name: Spiral Knight Crossbow
108234775.description: Part of the Spiral Knight Package.  http://www.roblox.com/Spiral-Knight-item?id=108235056

1215506016.name: Frozen Halberd
1215506016.description: A trail of ice follows the halberd's blade as you swing furiously at your enemy. A hit will set the other player on fire and does 40 damage, and encases your foe in ice.

110703943.name: Sorcus Stool
110703943.description: The Sorcus Egg hatched into SORCUS STOOL! While it is a great asset to any Troll, the stool works best as a enhancement in your trolling with the Sorcus chair on your Epic Troll journey.

3600622810.name: RDC 2019 1st Runner Up
3600622810.description: You absolutely rocked the Game Jam at RDC 2019. Congrats on placing in the top 3! We can’t wait to see where your game goes next.

28664212.name: Soccer Ball
28664212.description: Perfect for kicking around with friends or a real match.

148812192.name: Pi Slicer
148812192.description: Slice your foes into pie slices? Sure, why not!

45513203.name: Star Hammer
45513203.description: Great men don't watch the stars, great men forge the stars.

253519495.name: Ultimate Drive Speedster
253519495.description: Click to spawn the vehicle. Then, hop into the driver's seat and speed away! Includes two passenger seats.

181196009.name: Scary Gremlin
181196009.description: He's sweet when you are around, following you everywhere you go. It's other people he doesn't like. Your scary gremlin will chase other players that get near you - if it touches them they will drop anything they are holding and become paralyzed with fear - crouching on the ground to avoid the scary beast.

158069143.name: Bloxster 2XH
158069143.description: Ride all over ROBLOXIA.  Hit H to honk and turn your headlight on and off with the X key.

57902997.name: Bongos
57902997.description: Dance to the rhythm of the beat!

147948041.name: Trophy of Wheeled Participation 2014
147948041.description: This trophy stands as proof that this user earned the long-jumping item (1) that was available during a 2014 event.

1213388821.name: Freezing Elf's Ice Sword
1213388821.description: A wise warrior never ventures onto the tundra unarmed.  Part of the Freezing Elf package.

257813288.name: Neon Mystery Cape
257813288.description: Sparkle and brighten up the skies in this sweet neon cape.  Jump into the sky and hold space bar to glide. Rainbow sparkles leave a trail behind you so everyone knows where you've been.

34398938.name: Birthday Pinata
34398938.description: Definitely makes my list of top 5 birthday activities!

160198658.name: Midnight Sword
160198658.description: Slash at your foes to do 10 damage. Charge the sword by holding down the left mouse button to change day to night, increase your walk speed, and increase the damage your sword does.

99199463.name: Frost Blade
99199463.description: Icy justice is yours!  This item is exclusively available to Walmart shoppers.

228589017.name: Boss Bunny Bow and Arrow
228589017.description: The boss bunny is the boss for a reason.  Boss bunny never misses a shot. Use his bow and arrow to fire arrows that do 35 damage per hit.

105351545.name: Dragon's Blaze Sword
105351545.description: Straight from the dragon's mouth - a flame to consume all.  Your received this sword for free if you redeemed a ROBLOX card from GameStop from February 1st, 2013 to February 28th, 2013.

1016183873.name: Golden Magic Carpet
1016183873.description: Ride your own golden carpet through the skies of Roblox! Use the 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D' or arrow keys to control the direction. A magical golden trail will track your path through the sky.

161282711.name: Patriot's Monster Truck
161282711.description: It is your duty to drive over all other RC cars. Anything less would be Un-American.

97756645.name: Merely's ROBLOX Tablet
97756645.description: Winner: Merely. ROBLOX will be in touch to redeem this prize. Void if sold, traded, or deleted.

62827121.name: Wand of the Evil Eye: A Gamestop Exclusive
62827121.description: The evil eye sees all.  It will take your enemies to a place where they cannot see.

903197575.name: Overseer Mace
903197575.description: Overseers understand the universal language of smashing things with a mace. Click to bash your opponents with this mighty weapon.

27902303.name: ROBLOX Skateboard
27902303.description: This black and red board shreds asphalt.

241511828.name: Mystic Sword of the Flames
241511828.description: Courage is fire. Slash away at your enemies and leave behind a burning trail of death.  This sword does 15 - 22 damage per swing, trail burns 5 damage per step.

1227732454.name: Dog Man 4 Virtual Book
1227732454.description: Dog Man is back with the purrfect sidekick. Can the daring duo save the day? Start reading to find out!

110702207.name: Scaley, the Dragon
110702207.description:
The Egg of Scales hatched into Scaley, the Dragon.

Born from the roots of earth, and scales like the steel of Anabaris, Scaley, descends upon thee with glorious power to wield.

178076989.name: Exploding Heart
178076989.description: Equip this exploding heart and click to throw it at your foes.  Anyone near the explosion will be thrown back and take 30-35 points of damage.

95951359.name: Skeleton Bomb
95951359.description: Fling deadly bone shrapnel at your enemies for fun and profit!  Okay probably just for fun.

419240423.name: Dory Hieroglyph
419240423.description: Congratulations, you found the Dory Hieroglyph. Get a boost of speed as you trot around the globe! Be sure to see Finding Dory in theatres June 17 in 3D

236403380.name: Earth Summoning Horn
236403380.description: Blow upon this mighty relic to summon a massive earthquake within a 30 stud radius of where you're standing. Unanchored bricks begin to shake and break apart, and players trip and fall to the ground, slowly losing health. Three shockwaves are sent out, dealing around 20 damage per hit.

1340206298.name: Rocket Skateboard
1340206298.description: This board isn't just cool, it's out of this world.

215354986.name: Heart Air Balloon
215354986.description: Let love carry you away! Literally.  Let love carry you away in a hot air balloon.

1380774367.name: Steampunk Hoverboard
1380774367.description: At long last, you can harness the mighty power of steam to give you the power of flight. Well more like the power to float close to the ground, but at high speeds. Ok well, high-ish speeds. It's definitely faster than walking.

64870000.name: Indomitus Leo: A Walmart Exclusive Item

99254437.name: Scython's ROBLOX Tablet
99254437.description: Winner: Scython. ROBLOX will be in touch to redeem this prize. Void if sold, traded, or deleted.

709229848.name: ROBLOX Egg Launcher 2017
709229848.description:
Use this launcher to rain down some eggs in the 2017 Egg Hunt Custom Game! 

On behalf of everyone at ROBLOX, thank you for participating in the 2017 Egg Hunt! 

Here comes the boom.

968188707.name: Gold Plated Selfie Stick
968188707.description:
Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out www.roblox.com/toys to learn more...

2830533679.name: Neon Tiger Mount
2830533679.description: Gaudy, fierce, and fast - the purrr-fect mount.

261439002.name: Winters Greatsword
261439002.description: Wield the power of everlasting frost and might.

97885289.name: Trip Wire
97885289.description: Use this item to lay a trip wire.  It will slowly disappear and trip anyone (but you) that walks over it.  They'll take quite a bit of damage with the fall.

186521342.name: The Iron Trial
186521342.description: From the imaginations of Holly Black and Cassandra Clare comes a heart-stopping, mind-blowing, pulse-pounding plunge into the magical unknown.

155696189.name: Skipper Seal
155696189.description: Your first mate has got your back.  Even when he's a seal.  Click on a foe to have skipper seal slap him silly.

33867401.name: The Adventures of Noob Boy: Part 1
33867401.description: Help save the noob from the angry green circles! Use A and D to move left and right, and W to jump. This is the first 2D platformer we have released in a gear, so come be a part of Robloxian history!  Get it for free when you redeem a Gamestop card in June 2011!

226206426.name: Spring Flowers Crossbow
226206426.description: Fire arrows which bloom into deadly flowers which spew poison at nearby enemies. Does 25 damage over 6 seconds to enemies within 8 studs of the arrow when it spews poison.

1903666770.name: Beach Umbrella Sword
1903666770.description: To protect you from rain, but not enemies.

223785065.name: Korblox Ice Claws
223785065.description: Freezing ice crystal claws, which stop your enemies cold in their tracks! Quickly slash with both claws at your enemies, dealing around 25 damage per strike. Each time you hit someone, they're significantly slowed for a moment, making it that much more difficult to get away. There's also a 10% chance of freezing your enemies solid blue for 3 seconds.

33879504.name: Flamethrower
33879504.description: It’s finally here, the flamethrower. A highly requested item, Robloxians everywhere can now smell the napalm in the morning. Or afternoon or evening as well I guess.

1230027322.name: Snowped
1230027322.description: Dashing though the snow is way more fun on this than any old one horse open sleigh.

62350883.name: Sword of Ancalagon
62350883.description: More than a mere sword, this amazing tool shoots Ancalagon's own Dragon Fire at anyone in the area.

1560608167.name: Inflatable Sword
1560608167.description: A classic April Fool's prank from medieval times was to swap a friend’s sword for an inflatable one. They rarely got the point, though.

30847685.name: Blunderbuss
30847685.description: The blunderbuss is a muzzle-loading firearm with a short, large caliber barrel, which is flared at the muzzle, and used with shot. The blunderbuss is an early form of shotgun adapted to military and defensive use.

68478587.name: Tempest Blades
68478587.description: These twin blades will cause your enemies twice the trouble!

24903474.name: Egg Compass
24903474.description: Points you towards the rarest egg in the level. Re-use often, in case the egg is moving.

93136802.name: Amethyst Periastron Kappa
93136802.description: The sword men use to fight robot lions in space.

467138029.name: Robot Dance Gun
467138029.description: Laser gun that compels anyone it hits to do the robot!

75550883.name: Rubber Chicken Wand
75550883.description: Your enemy is coming at you fast and furious with the Darkheart Sword.  What do you do?  Turn the sword into a rubber chicken of course.

12562390.name: Roman Candle
12562390.description: It's actually not Roman. It's made in Maryland. WARNING: Do not use fireworks indoors.

511931885.name: Exploding Pumpkins
511931885.description: Extremely festive and extremely dangerous to your foes. Click to deploy the bomb; it deals 60 damage, splitting up and multiplying into a bunch of smaller bombs.

243778818.name: Fallen Artemis Sword & Shield
243778818.description: When equipped this shield doubles your current and max health. Click to slash for 15 damage per hit.  The special attack repeatedly strikes enemies for 30 damage per hit, one hit per second. Release the left mouse button while charging the do a double slash for 15 damage per hit.

163995329.name: Epic Duck Roped
163995329.description: The silliest Ro Ped yet!  Hit the 'H' key to make it quack!  Hit 'Q' to make it rain ducks.

1665544157.name: Lillian's Moonglaive
1665544157.description: Slices through objects like a hot knife through butter. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy! Check out www.roblox.com/toys to learn more...

754871615.name: Dual Wield Ninja Scythes
754871615.description: Double the scythes, double the damage. Slash at your opponents to do 15 damage per hit!

583030187.name: Azure Mines Pickaxe
583030187.description:
The classic tool of the trade for miners, you'll be busting rocks and taking names. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

188868661.name: Snow Fiend's Daggers
188868661.description: The Snow Fiend dual wields these daggers.  Throw them individually and together. Each dagger does 20 damage.  Part of the Snow Fiend package.

131372632.name: Ghastly Ghoul Gun
131372632.description: Turn your foes into ghosts.  Part of the Ghastly Ghoul package.

71597060.name: Captain Steelshanks Recruiting Staff
71597060.description: Captain Steelshanks is recruiting a crew for his vessel, the Ironsides.  Don't want to be a pirate?  Too bad.

82711866.name: Alien on a Rampage Book
82711866.description: Every sci-fi fan needs to familiarize himself with his fellow extraterrestrials!  Collect a copy of Alien on a Rampage, a new book from Clete Smith.

160199141.name: ROBLOX Blimp
160199141.description: Celebrate good times!  Inflate your own personal ROBLOX blimp that travels around your head forever!  Well at least until you die or leave the server....

271017937.name: Radiant Seahorse
271017937.description:
"I only travel by seahorse these days. All the best people are doing it!"

Use the arrow keys or 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D' to steer your seahorse in whichever direction you'd like to go.

1560398824.name: Loyal Pizza Warrior Circular Sword
1560398824.description: Part of the Loyal Pizza Warrior package.

1829078563.name: Sun Slayer Sword
1829078563.description: The chosen weapon of the Sun Slayer. Each swing strikes true and swift.

1532311127.name: Eggmin Launcher 2018
1532311127.description:
Use this launcher to rain down some eggs in the Egg Hunt! 

Only works in Egg Hunt 2018

498752764.name: Flying Carpet of Books
498752764.description: Reading can take you places. Literally. Books version of the magic carpet; click to activate. Using 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D' or the arrow keys to control the direction it flies. Click again to hop off.

95258660.name: Explosive Spy Pen
95258660.description: This pen is certainly mightier than a sword!  Click twice and throw the pen for an explosive surprise.  Well it's not a surprise to you - you know it's an explosive spy pen.

379098145.name: Will Wilder Book
379098145.description: In this supernatural thriller, a 12-year-old’s quest to uncover his family’s secret past puts everyone he knows in danger.

295460073.name: Plunger Launcher
295460073.description: Launch deadly plungers at your opponents! Do 30 points of dirty damage with each hit!

70476425.name: Dragonshead Cannon
70476425.description: Seriously what did you think it would shoot?  Treasure? No - it's got to be the heads of lesser dragons.

105189286.name: Furno's Sword and Shield
105189286.description: Furno uses this sword and shield to defend his home against the evil  brains. Get his sword and shield for yourself by playing LEGO Hero Factory: Brain Attack! here http://www.roblox.com/LEGO-Hero-Factory-Brain-Attack-place?id=88419564

163355404.name: 8-Bit Phoenix
163355404.description: Your 8-bit phoenix will defend you until the very end!

23153742.name: Dastardly Skate
23153742.description: Top prize for the Big Air skate park building contest.

88143074.name: Poison Picnic
88143074.description: This green cake with a skull on it is irresistible.  Does 60 damage to any opponent who picks it up.  Why would they pick it up you say?  Because they have no other choice.

127506364.name: Knights of Redcliff: Deluxe Sword and Shield Set
127506364.description: Don't let this simple, elegant blade fool you.  This is the most deadly Redcliff sword yet!

64647651.name: The Necrosapien Staff
64647651.description: It's Latin. Look it up. Necromancers are supposed to like Latin.

142498104.name: Hockey Stick
142498104.description: Shoot pucks at your foes and check them into submission.

329021959.name: Theodore
329021959.description: The “Stomach” of the band. The only thing bigger than his belly is his kindness. As a heads up, you might not want to stand downwind of him though (he got “pizza toots”). Be sure to catch Alvin and the Chipmunks: The Road Chip in theaters December 18!

255800146.name: Ninja Whip
255800146.description: Keep calm and use your ninja whip.

1380788230.name: Steampunk Slasher
1380788230.description: An elegant weapon from a more refined time.

24419811.name: Protest Sign: Eggs are for eating.
24419811.description: Egg hunts are silly.  Who wants fabulous prizes and fun?

73888479.name: Spikesplosion
73888479.description: If you're not shooting off spikes, what are you doing?

1304339797.name: Giant Ninja Star
1304339797.description: It’s much more efficient to throw one giant star, rather than a lot of little ones. Click to pull the mighty star off your back and hurl at your foes.

90718505.name: Exponential Rocket Launcher
90718505.description: One rocket. Three rockets. Nine rockets.  The further your initial rocket travels, the more rockets it spawns, causing anywhere from 75 to 300 points of damage on impact, resulting in catastrophic damage for anyone that isn’t you.

122330194.name: Chicago News Man Cane
122330194.description: Part of the exclusive Chicago News Man package  granted to BLOXcon Chicago attendees who purchased the exclusive merchandise bundle.

945542990.name: Redcliff Archer's Crossbow
945542990.description: The Redcliff archers trains daily to master their aim. One bolt, one enemy down. Part of the Redcliff Archer package.

746686384.name: Winged Magical Staff
746686384.description: The perfect tool for fighting evil in the daylight or moonlight. Double jump to fly.  Control using 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D' or arrow keys. Click to shoot neon pink orbs at your enemies!

183704866.name: Spook Launcher
183704866.description: You're bringing spooky back. Launch ghosts, bats, or pumpkins at your foes. The pumpkins will obscure your enemies vision. The ghosts will terrify them into temporary paralysis.  The bat deals 25 damage.

268586231.name: Azure Dragon's Magic Slayer
268586231.description: Click to deal your foes 16 to 22 points of damage.  If you successfully blox your foe, they become a  skeleton! Click and hold to charge a special attack which creates a magic purple portal in front of you. It'll then suck in objects and players and instantly kill them if they come in contact with it!

398675172.name: Red Rolling Hoverboard
398675172.description: Click to spawn your very own hoverboard! Control your direction using arrow keys or the 'W', 'A', 'S', and 'D' keys. Hit Backspace to dismount.

675312894.name: Emerald Claw: The Envious Club
675312894.description: Im not sure where he got this, I don't think I want to know either... Click to bash this upon your enemies heads! Dealing 20 to 30 damage! You will either whack your enemy or swing overhead. Double click to forcefully swing from above; dealing massive damage and temporarily stunning them!  Part of the Emerald Claw: The Envious package.

461488745.name: Flaming Orb of Divine Pain
461488745.description: Cast deadly fireballs at your enemies with this orb. Enemies will be dealt anywhere from 25 up to 45 damage.

45941397.name: Fire Breathing Dragon Friend
45941397.description: He only breathes fire when he's really mad.  So you shouldn't worry...just don't make him mad.

215355157.name: Rainbow Disco Hyperbike
215355157.description: Ride around in style. This bike will leave a rainbow trail of light to mark where you've been

168143042.name: Galactic Laser Gun
168143042.description: Foes from all planets will fear your wrath!

150366320.name: Spring Crossbow
150366320.description: This crossbow fires springs at your foes to do 12 damage per hit. Occasionally you'll fire spring flowers which do double damages.  Spring has sprung!

164207580.name: Red Convertible
164207580.description: Zip around the streets of ROBLOX in your sweet red convertible. Let the virtual wind flow through your virtual hair and feel the joy of summer!

75550928.name: Garbage Can Shield and Wooden Sword Set

31839337.name: Torch
31839337.description: Try to set the night on fire! The updated torch looks best in ROBLOX games with dynamic lighting.

88146486.name: First Class Fencing Sword
88146486.description: Fence your way to a gold medal with this first class sword.

1402445648.name: Giant Ice Bow
1402445648.description: Winter is here and you’re ready to make sure everyone survives. This bow will freeze your foes and do a fair amount of damage.

14876573.name: Spec Beta Biograft Energy Sword
14876573.description: In 2113, decades after the initial release of the hugely successful Spec Alpha biograft energy weapons, the US government began research on a top-secret upgrade. The breakthrough was to use artificial diamonds to forge the blade itself, rather that carbon nanofibers. The new weapon was very effective, but obscenely expensive. Only a hundred were ever made.

168142114.name: Ham Fists
168142114.description: "Eat the ham, Tina."  After you eat the ham, your fists will turn into ham fists - which you can use to punch your foes. Each hit does 15 damage.

880432781.name: Summertime Water Balloon
880432781.description: The best way to cool off is to stay hydrated. (At least that’s what you should tell your friends when you bombard them with water balloons)

164207842.name: Pool Noodle
164207842.description: Swing your pool noodle with all you've got!  Anyone it hits will be pushed back.

1016512413.name: Tiger Warrior Club
1016512413.description: Tigers don't typically use weapons, so they'll have to improvise. Click to swing and bash enemies. Part of the Tiger Warrior Package.

2226815033.name: Wand of Flurry
2226815033.description: Blow away your enemies with a flick of your wrist!

152233094.name: The Drop
152233094.description: It's time to drop the bass... on your foes... Drop this awesome bass on your friends or foes when it gets too heavy.

268533320.name: Meerkat Horde
268533320.description: Spawn a horde of 6 attack meerkats which you can command to chase after your foes.

94233344.name: Trench Warfare Shotgun
94233344.description: The Trench Gun shoots up to 20 bullets in a single round, with a wide spray around your target, making it super easy to hit nearby enemies. There are only six rounds in a clip, so time your reloads wisely!

114020557.name: Korblox - Fallen's Spine Blade
114020557.description: In the heat of battle, when the weapon fails him, a true Korblox warrior is not afraid of ripping his spine apart and slashing through his adversaries.

295460702.name: Super Slash Cat Claws
295460702.description: Claw at your foes and do 15-30 damage per swipe. Double click to dash forward while swinging both claws! This will make both claws slash at your enemies, which can do up to twice the damage.

2649068009.name: Dog Man 6 Virtual Book
2649068009.description: Dog Man is back! Get this virtual item to read more!

2907611562.name: Fanciful Leprechaun Walking Cane
2907611562.description: You can tell by the way i use my walk Im a leprechaun, no time to talk. Part of the Fanciful Leprechaun bundle.

23156134.name: Digital Green Skateboard
23156134.description: This skateboard is brought to you free of charge, as a part of our current Skate Park building promotion!

190094159.name: Super Rocket Launcher
190094159.description: When activated, this rocket launcher releases a deadly five-round barrage of rockets which fly straight up after a short jaunt forward towards your target.

298087401.name: Fusion Gatling Blaster
298087401.description: This gun has two modes; rapid-fire lasers, and a flamethrower attachment. You can alternate between the two by hitting the 'Q' key.  For the laser shots, you click and hold, and the upper barrel slowly begin to spin with a Gatling-fire like sound effect. It gets faster and louder, shooting projectiles more rapidly until it's at its maximum speed. This is rapid-fire, so there's dozens of lasers hitting your enemies all at once. They each do 8 damage.  The flamethrower, you click and hold as well, which a moderate sized flame blows out from the under-barrel of the gun.

152822847.name: Eggray 2014
152822847.description: This gear item will only work in the official ROBLOX 2014 Egg Hunt.  Use the Eggray to determine if the egg that you're hunting is in the server that you've joined.

49491736.name: Dracovin Spell Book
49491736.description: Dracovin's spells are world renowned for their force and accuracy.  4 of his spells can be yours today!

76596299.name: Phantom Falchion: A Walmart Exclusive
76596299.description: It appears in the dark, seemingly from nowhere.  Before you can see the wielder, it strikes!

45201977.name: First Aid Kit
45201977.description: Why aren't they just called aid kits? Or bandaid boxes?  Why the word first?

1241156683.name: Swordfish Sword
1241156683.description: Ironically swordfish are pacifists who hate conflict. This one makes a very fine sword though, click to slash and lunge through enemies.

398675588.name: Solid Gold Skateboard
398675588.description: Why buy gold plated when you can have solid gold. You deserve the best.  This sweet board emits golden sparkles when you're going at top speeds.

277956390.name: Non-Hovering Board
277956390.description: Some people might think this is a skateboard, but they'd be wrong. This is just a hover board that's missing its hover functionality.

335087161.name: 2016 Fireworks
335087161.description: Start this amazing new year off with a bang! A beautiful, loud, fire in the sky bang.

1492225511.name: Throwing Bolts
1492225511.description: Being struck by lightning is a shocking experience.

113299641.name: Personal Fighter Jets
113299641.description: Mini jet fighters that strike at your command! They'll circle your head until you are ready to unleash the fury!

548019247.name: Sword of Kubo’s Father
548019247.description: Pick up the sword of Kubo’s father and use it to ward off evil on your many adventures! And even if there is no evil, it looks pretty awesome.

18409191.name: Spikey Stick of Civilized Negotiation
18409191.description: You think this is your land. Actually, it's mine. If you have a problem with that, let's talk about it.

313532292.name: Space View-Master
313532292.description: We think it won’t be a long, long time before touchdown brings you ‘round again, Rocket Man. Because with this nifty device you can hover about just like in zero gravity!

1076467071.name: Anubis Staff
1076467071.description: The scales of judgement forged into a mighty weapon for Anubis' long journey. Part of the Anubis package.

233520425.name: iLift Two
233520425.description: Next time someone asks - "Do you even lift?"  You can let them know exactly how much you lift... with iLift Two.  Click to spin the dumbbells around- charging them for your deadly throw.  Damage ranges between 10-20 per hit.

20056642.name: Noisemaker
20056642.description: Man is that irritating. Stop it.

125859450.name: Crystal Sphere Drop
125859450.description: Icosahedral geodesic sphere to be exact. Launch this flagpole at your foes and then wait for the ball to drop.  5.4.3.2.1

549914888.name: 4th Annual Bloxy Award
549914888.description: This award was given out to the winners of the Annual BLOXY Awards, honoring the best game creators, builders, artists, and video makers on ROBLOX.

208659586.name: Brilliant Throwing Knives
208659586.description: Click to launch a knife at your foes.  Does up to 22.5 damage per hit.

537374622.name: Old Timey Hot Air Balloon
537374622.description: Up, up, and away! Equip and click to spawn the hot air balloon; hop in the seat and click around and hold your mouse button to guide the balloon around in the direction of your cursor. Flames ignite by the engine above as you're ascending

243788599.name: Hedgehog Horde
243788599.description: Release the hedgehogs!  Click on enemies to get your hedgehogs to attack them!

271017031.name: Sushi Scooter
271017031.description: The people want sushi, and they want it now! Drive around using 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D', or the arrow keys. Hit X to toggle the headlight and H to honk. Click with your mouse to grab a sushi snack from the crate on the back of the vehicle and eat it.

71597048.name: Steelshanks Armament
71597048.description: Pirates don't fight fair. They bring guns to sword fights.

999864256.name: Scrooge McDuck’s Giant Ruby
999864256.description: Every adventurer needs to find a precious stone at one point in their career! Them’s the rules.

515687925.name: Nerf Candy Basket
515687925.description: This is Advertising. Engage in the festivities with the basket of goodies!

10730984.name: Black Iron Mace of Pwnage
10730984.description: Dispatch your enemies with extreme prejudice. Swings slow, but does a lot of damage if it hits.

162857357.name: Portable Beach
162857357.description: One click and you're on an instant beach vacation... complete with sand castle!

35293856.name: Atomizer
35293856.description: Split yourself into pieces to evade your enemies!

114491710.name: W.A.R.P.: The Reluctant Assassin
114491710.description: Eoin Colfer, bestselling author of the Artemis Fowl books, returns with a new series, W.A.R.P., featuring time travelers, magic, a gorilla arm (time travel side effect) and danger… really creepy, scary, danger.

25741198.name: Hot Potato
25741198.description: Left click to activate, then pass it off before it explodes!

65554735.name: Spam Cannon
65554735.description: Shoot spam at your friends! Includes such classics as - "donate plox" and "post this on ten items and get on free"

891924036.name: Grand Samurai Katana
891924036.description: When the world is at peace, a gentleman keeps his sword by his side. Click to hack and slash your opponents up to 12 damage. Part of the Grand Samurai package.

174752245.name: Silver Crossbow
174752245.description: Click to fire an arrow.  Each hit will cost your opponent 12 damage points. Occasionally, you will shoot a flaming arrow that does 65 damage points.

1748604797.name: Han Solo’s Dice
1748604797.description:
The lucky dice of Han Solo might bring you some luck as well, at least with speed.
Be sure to watch Solo: A Star Wars Story, in theaters May 25!

2016189421.name: Beach Bigfoot Surfboard
2016189421.description: Surfs up, bruh! Part of the Beach Bigfoot package.

168141496.name: Bladed Tutu
168141496.description: You'll be looking sharp in this bladed tutu. Spin attack to do 15 damage to your foes and teach them the true meaning of the black swan.

71037028.name: Flying Magic Carpet
71037028.description: Fly through the skies of ROBLOXia on this magical carpet.

512422543.name: Dark Summoner Staff
512422543.description: Summon a bunch of spooky undead creatures around you which will protect you and chase anybody nearby! Part of the Dark Summoner Package.

1245307956.name: Tundra Explorer Dual Hooks
1245307956.description: Slash your way though your frozen foes.

1191128759.name: Ram Mount
1191128759.description: Ride across the rugged terrain on this sure-footed ram mount. He might be stubborn, but his horns always get the point across.

250534394.name: BLOXikin Horde
250534394.description: Spawn an evil BLOXikin wizard, who summons 12 to 16 BLOXikin minions to serve by his side. The wizard's minions will attack your foes to do 5 damage per hit. However, if your enemies can kill the wizard, his minions will perish as well!

503957396.name: Deluxe Coil Gun
503957396.description: With lightning in your hand, the future is yours! Shoot electric blue beams of electricity at enemies. Deals 15 damage per hit and stuns enemies for a moment!

44084783.name: Tomahawk
44084783.description: Long distance danger - free of charge!

163355764.name: Rotten Rocky's Guitar
163355764.description: Part of the Rotten Rocky package.  Use  Z, X, C, V, B, N, M to play this cool guitar! Hold shift for sharp notes!

139593916.name: 2014 Fireworks
139593916.description: 2014 swiftly approaches... but it's not quite as swift as these 2014 rockets! Light up the night with these sweet fireworks!

477910063.name: Deluxe Rainbow Magic Carpet
477910063.description: A super sized magic carpet that seats two players!

264990548.name: USA Sparkler 2015
264990548.description: Shoot out red, white, and blue sparks!

57983479.name: Hula Dog
57983479.description: He thinks it's always Aloha Friday.

164015715.name: Cartoon Network Skateboard
164015715.description: Shred into summer with this cool Cartoon Network skateboard! Are you CN what we’re sayin’?

232522034.name: The Specialist's grenade
232522034.description: Click and hold to have a chargeable bar appear on your screen. It'll quickly rise and lower. The closer the bar is to being full, the further you can throw the grenade. Let go of your mouse button when it's within a reasonable range of where your target lies. Be careful though - you can also be damaged by this grenade, which does 60 damage.

107458461.name: Noobcaik
107458461.description: Throw this to a friend to spam him with noobish comments.  He will be temporarily blinded.

846794018.name: Bluesea Soarer
846794018.description: This powerful blue dragon will follow you around and shoot fiery death balls at your enemies.

190880295.name: 2015 Fireworks
190880295.description: Light up the night to celebrate 2015!

97885508.name: The General's .45
97885508.description: Does 40 damage per shot.  Six shots per round.

2845994810.name: Valkyrie Sword
2845994810.description:
An enchanted weapon once wielded by a mythical warrior. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

2535102910.name: R0b0-Penguin
2535102910.description: Warning: Core Temp Unstable. Faithfully follows, releasing ice and electricity as he goes.

118281463.name: Land Shark Shooter
118281463.description: Shoots out sharks that lurk beneath the land. Aim a shark at your foe and he'll never see it coming... unless he can see through the ground.

53917288.name: Walrus
53917288.description: I am the eggman.  They are the eggman.  I am the WALRUS!

50938765.name: Scythe of Singularity
50938765.description: This mighty weapon will leave you spinning.  Literally.

112591865.name: Deluxe Beach Ball
112591865.description: Hit the ball back and forth with friends.  Just another chill day on the ROBLOXIAN beachfront.

402304782.name: Crimsonwrath: The Red Wrath
402304782.description: For when you're really mad bro. Send your enemies to meet their maker... or whatever. Click to slash; double click to lunge. When using, your speed is boosted 4 points making you slightly faster, enough to trail behind enemies which flee. Each kill, the sword gets even stronger for a few seconds! When killed, enemies turn into flaming transparent red ghosts which quickly fade away up into the sky!

106064277.name: Cupid's Beloved Blade
106064277.description: In addition to dealing five points of damage per strike, this blade turns your opponent into a lovely shade of pink! Double tap "W" for a spin attack, double click for a homing attack, or press "A", "W", then "D" for a "pinksplosion"! Each special attack does 10 hit points of damage.

2409286506.name: Bat-tle Axe
2409286506.description: Can I AXE you a question? I promise to get my POINT across.

1748603889.name: Sabacc Playing Cards
1748603889.description: A deck of Sabacc cards that can be enjoyed when you watch Solo: A Star Wars Story, in theaters May 25!

139578136.name: Sword of Swords
139578136.description: Yo Dawg!  We heard you liked swords, so we made you a sword made of swords so you can slash while you slash.

431047232.name: Winter Adventurer's Sword
431047232.description: Click to slash; double click to lunge. Dealing roughly 20 damage per hit. Part of the Winter Adventurer's package.

32858586.name: Frostbrand
32858586.description: A weapon bestowed upon Azurewrath's elite personal bodyguards upon the attainment of rank.

154727487.name: Evil Green Science Goo
154727487.description: This goo will stop your foes in their tracks!  Hit your friends or foes with this stuff and they'll lose their ability to jump and slowly lose the ability to move. Eventually the evil green goo will take them over and they will become this goo. Your target will be no more.

169602010.name: Merely's Web Slinger
169602010.description: Nobody slings web like Merely.  Nobody. Srsly.

67755182.name: Deluxe Snowball Cannon 3000
67755182.description: Faster than every other snowball cannon on the market, the Deluxe Snowball Cannon 3000 can fire multiple shots in quick succession.

34247537.name: Birthday Dance Party Potion
34247537.description: Quite possibly our most dancetastic dance potion yet!  Dance like nobody's watching!

158069110.name: Poisoned Skeleton Scythe
158069110.description: Dangerous to anyone who get's hit. In addition to the slash damage, there is a 25% change of poisoning anyone you hit. If poisoned your foe will be unable to jump and can only walk at half speed.

123042140.name: Golden Fleece
123042140.description: Win the Golden Fleece by playing the Percy Jackson edition of SFOTH! Don’t forget to join the best quest ever on Digital HD, December 3rd.

60357972.name: Flaming Hedgehog Cannon
60357972.description: Because laser guns are way too predictable...

2463693263.name: PumpKing Chopper
2463693263.description: The perfect bike to ride with during a full moon in the dead of night.

1119905579.name: Coco - Marigold Petal
1119905579.description: A precious treasure that represents passion and creativity! Use its power to draw inspiration for yourself as you set out on your own journey!

431042935.name: Autumn Elf's Enchanted Dagger
431042935.description: Part of the Autumn Elf package!

869125445.name: 8-Bit Crossbow
869125445.description: This 8-bit crossbow deals 20 damage upon impact on a player.

382837475.name: Opened Basket of Delicate Flight
382837475.description: I can fly twice as high. Inside you find... Violet Spring Butterfly Wings.

903199054.name: Redcliff Battleaxe
903199054.description: When evil looms, Redcliff Knights answer the call, with this might axe! Click to slash enemies, unleash a mighty lunge attack to do more damage.

58574452.name: Go Fish
58574452.description: Challenge your friends to see who can catch the most fish!

65545971.name: Mega Annoying Megaphone
65545971.description: It's not just a megaphone, it's mega annoying!

15973059.name: Protest Sign: We'd Rather Have User GUIs Later...
15973059.description: We don't know what GUIs are, and we don't want to know. If you ask us, there's enough goo in ROBLOX without making things any more gooey. We will fight to the death anyone who disagrees.

57229313.name: Bug Juice
57229313.description: It doesn't come in a jar. It comes from who you are.  But seriously - this stuff will make you jump like there are 100 spiders after you.

44561400.name: Shrunken Head
44561400.description: Are you the head salesman of the jungle?

215392741.name: Merely's Green Sparkle Time Hoverboard
215392741.description: Hover over the skies and speed over your challengers, sparkling green all the way.

76170515.name: Alien Parasite
76170515.description: Steals your enemy's health and replenishes your own!

928913996.name: Adurite Guitar of Rock Excellence
928913996.description: Rock out on this ulta-rare adurite guitar. It vibrates at a frequency to make tunes sound extra sweet. Use the keys: 'Z', 'X', 'C', 'V', 'B', 'N', and 'M' to play different tunes. Hold shift while pressing to sharpen the notes.

53623350.name: Telamon's Foe Hammer
53623350.description: For when a ban hammer just doesn't hit hard enough.

261827192.name: Neon Rainbow Phoenix
261827192.description: Your guardian phoenix follows you and protects you by shooting different color fireballs at your foes. Each hit does 25 damage!

11453385.name: Katana
11453385.description: The katana originated in the Muromachi period (1392–1573) as a result of changing battle conditions requiring faster response times. The katana facilitated this by being worn with the blade facing up, which allowed the samurai to draw and cut their enemy in a single motion. Previously, the curved sword of the samurai was worn with the blade facing down. The ability to draw and cut in one motion also became increasingly useful in the daily life of the samurai.

191261808.name: Dark Pegasus
191261808.description: Fly around on your dark horse.

1363019628.name: Black Panther - Dagger
1363019628.description: Join forces with Black Panther while you explore the Innovation Event! Be sure to see Marvel Studio’s Black Panther in theaters February 16!

149612200.name: Leprachaun's Gold Rainbow Laser Gun
149612200.description: This powerful laser gun shoots dangerous rainbows at your foes.  Charge to do max damage of 50 points.  Look for a surprise at the end of the rainbow!

483308681.name: Redcliff Elite Sword
483308681.description: Click to slash dealing around 16 damage per hit. Double click to lunge dealing around 25 damage.

139308319.name: ROBLOX Stocking
139308319.description: Only Builderman knows what's inside.  Happy Holidays!

108148416.name: Sophisticated Blade
108148416.description: His sword movements are as sophisticated as the sword's hilt.  Get this item when you redeem a ROBLOX Card from Target in the month of March.

891900286.name: Ancient Dragon Firecracker
891900286.description: Pow pow! Toss for a small pop! Part of the Ancient Dragon package.

168141301.name: Ice Dragon Slayer
168141301.description: Are you the dragon or the dragon slayer?  Use the special key('E', 'Q', 'G', 'T', or 'L') to emit ice-fire from your left arm and throw ice balls at your foes.  If hit, your enemy will become partial frozen, slowing their movement and doing 15 damage.

121121915.name: Shadow Master Katana
121121915.description: Part of the Shadow Master Package- available exclusively to users who redeem a ROBLOX card from Gamestop in July.

218631227.name: Red ROBLOX Glider
218631227.description: Soar through the skies. It's definitely the most scenic way to travel!

73799348.name: The Axe of Undoing: A Walmart Exclusive
73799348.description: This axe will be the undoing of everything!  Awarded when you redeemed a card from Walmart in March, 2012.

515687734.name: Nerf Blaster
515687734.description: This is advertising. Show off your love with Nerf by blasting away!

223785473.name: Redcliff Wings
223785473.description: Soar above your foes on the wings of the Redcliff!

461489128.name: Wizard Flight Spell
461489128.description: Take flight with this magic spell!  Jump to begin flight; control using 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D', or the arrow keys. Hit the space bar again to stop flying.

110335886.name: Rare Egg Compass - Egg Hunt 2013
110335886.description: This item will only work in the official ROBLOX Egg Hunt 2013 level for the duration of this year's egg hunt.  This item will help you find one of three rare eggs.

94119269.name: Molecular Atomizer
94119269.description: Protect yourself with this Molecular Atomizer, the best defense against all the zombies and werewolves running through ROBLOX. And don't forget to watch the premiere of Girl vs. Monster Friday, October 12 at 8p/7c on Disney Channel!

37347141.name: Jumpin' Jack's Trick And Treat Bag
37347141.description: As you take damage, your power meter increases. Eat candy from the bag to release this power in the form of a hyperactive sugar rush!

18010691.name: The Awe Star
18010691.description: Awe... SNAP! As of November 13, 2009 there are exactly equal numbers of Awe Stars and Ninja Masks of Awesomeness in existence. If you combine both items, the Awe Star becomes a weapon of Ninjitsu domination!

48159731.name: Spring Sword of Growth
48159731.description: As spring plants grow, so does this sword.  One might wield it easily at first, but with each blox, it becomes larger and larger.

253485047.name: Galactic Hot Dogs
253485047.description: Read Galactic Hot Dogs & join Cosmoe the Earth-Boy and Big Humphree on an adventure on the Neon Weiner, the finest flying food truck in the galaxy!

95951330.name: Skeleton Scythe
95951330.description: Swing at your enemies to do 20 damage per hit.  Press "E" three times to summon a small army.

183797762.name: Otterhead Longsword
183797762.description: And you thought the Otterhead Shortsword was cool!  Hit 'Q' to get the sword to spin in a circle and do 20 damage per hit. Otherwise, click to attack and do 10-15 damage per hit!

97932897.name: d4rk886's ROBLOX Tablet
97932897.description: Winner: d4rk886. ROBLOX will be in touch to redeem this prize. Void if sold, traded, or deleted.

163348987.name: Cymbals
163348987.description: Clash!  Slam these babies together to make a loud sound!  Does no damage.

82707577.name: Serpent Staff
82707577.description: Lob poison darts at your enemies in a snake like fashion.

127506105.name: Korblox Mage Staff
127506105.description: Use the powerful dark magic of the Korblox to summon a row of spears from thin air!  If they don't hit your opponent on the way down, they'll hit them as they explode!

188643628.name: Killer Whale Launcher
188643628.description: These whales nuke you!  Shoot whales at your foes to do 10 damage per touch- ie instant KO.  To zoom, you roll your mouse wheel and use either 'Q' or 'Z'.

2620420065.name: Snow Wolf Companion
2620420065.description: A great companion is always by your side, even in the coldest weather.

24903431.name: Eggdentifier 2010
24903431.description: The Eggdentifier 2010 is the latest work of the Abbitray Institute.  It identifies which eggs are in a place and how many of them there are.  A very useful egg hunting tool indeed!!!

74385418.name: Glory Launcher 2012
74385418.description: With this heat seeking missile launcher, your foes don't stand a chance.

467109039.name: Dragon Tooth Power Up
467109039.description:
Hold the tooth to fly into the sky like Elliot.

You hold it, you jump to fly, and you'll come down slowly.

21351465.name: Maraca
21351465.description: So annoying it might just make everyone ban musical instruments from their places.

302418416.name: TubeHeroes DanTDM
302418416.description: An unparalleled scientist, inventor and chemist to come on your adventures with you!

341110180.name: Rainbow Omega Katana
341110180.description: Slash and lunge at your foes with this amazing katana to do 12 to 16 points of damage.  The power of Rainbow surrounds this Katana.

65079094.name: Retro Candy
65079094.description: Put your enemies to sleep with six pieces of this delicious retro candy.

78665215.name: Crossbow of the Blades
78665215.description: Yo dawg, I heard you like weapons, so here's a crossbow to shoot swords while you shoot your crossbow.

21445765.name: Crowbar
21445765.description: Use this to smash things up real good!

16201628.name: Delete Tool
16201628.description: A Delete Tool that can delete entire models for Group Building

93709266.name: Polar Bear Cub
93709266.description: All the fun of a polar bear with none of the aggression.

19399456.name: Kwanzaa Kinara
19399456.description: During Kwanzaa candles are placed in a special candleholder called the Kinara. There are seven candles (Mishumaa Saba) used, each representing one of the Seven Principles (Nguzo Saba) of Kwanzaa.

110337884.name: Egg Cannon 2013
110337884.description: Launches mostly decoy eggs so you can distract your fellow hunters with false eggs. Keep an eye out though, occasionally the cannon launches a real egg!  Only works in the Games Egg Hunt 2013.

2646379006.name: Yeti Hunter Spear
2646379006.description: It could be dangerous out there, better take this. Part of the Yeti Hunter bundle.

58574431.name: Untimely Crossbow
58574431.description: Untimely demise?  Untimely Halloween theme?  Who knows!

217901450.name: The Gigantic Tome of Eggs
217901450.description: What eggs do you have? Which games contain which eggs? This tome tells you all that and more!

233633874.name: Worldwide Stunna
233633874.description: Sling the fury of the entire world at your foe.  Upon striking another person, the globe causes them to spin as the earth would. They are immobilized for several seconds.

152822815.name: Opened Sparkle Basket of Bunny Time
152822815.description: Bunny Basket of Sparkle Time?  You should always take time to sparkle and shine.  Inside you find... Sparkle Time Bunny Ears.

112593687.name: Deluxe Blue Roped
112593687.description: This stylish blue roped will keep you traveling in deluxe style.  It moves faster than the red roped and does sweet jumps with more ease than ever before.

4771619789.name: Eggmin Cannon 9000
4771619789.description: The eggmin's personal armament. Rain down eggs all day with this cannon in Egg Hunt 2020 games!

638034686.name: Snowball Gloves
638034686.description: Summon a snowball in your hands and throw it at friends! Click and you hold your arms out together and a create a snowball in thin air. Click again to throw it, like any other snowball!

105189783.name: Trollamon
105189783.description: This Tiny Trolling Telamon will follow you around and throw his precious fried chicken at your enemies- doing 15 damage per chicken strike.  Justice has never been more savory.

257807125.name: The Dragon Eye
257807125.description: A mysterious and powerful artifact. What it does, we’re not quite sure. But, every time we touch it a dragon appears. So, yeah, it’s power must be used wisely.

117498793.name: Poisonous Butterfly
117498793.description: Drop the jar to unleash the poisonous butterfly!  It will drop little balls of poison as it flutters around you.  As you get close to enemies it will throw extra poison at them.

66896565.name: MissileToe
66896565.description: No one is going to want to meet you under the missiletoe this year.  Shoots missiles with toes at your enemies.

1117743696.name: Anti-Vampire Stake
1117743696.description: When you invite a vampire over for a "stake" dinner, I don't think they'll appreciate the joke. Lunge at vicious vampires for 20 damage.

54694329.name: Sword of the Summer Sun
54694329.description: The pain of a million sunburns...

170903610.name: Intergalactic Sword
170903610.description: Do planetary amounts of damage with this intergalactic chainsword.

36913598.name: Haunted Pumpkin Staff
36913598.description: Summon tons of pumpkins with just the twirl of your staff!  Watch out the darkseeds are especially dangerous.

160189720.name: Donut Danger
160189720.description: These dangerous throwing donuts do 20 damage per hit. Do not stop throwing these donuts.

49929724.name: Knights of Redcliff: Battle Axe
49929724.description: When Redcliff Knights are proficient with the battle axe, their knight masters know they are ready for the next deadly challenge.

1789546750.name: Hypobike
1789546750.description: Organically powered awesome bicycle. Travel at regular speed and leave a trail of burning light behind you.

434289516.name: BFG Dream Horn
434289516.description: The BFG dream horn will provide a spellbinding experience through your journey at ROBLOX’s summer camp!

230729032.name: Opened Chosen Basket of the Overseer
230729032.description: He is the chosen one. Inside you find... Overseer Chosen.

2506365260.name: Skeletal Scythe
2506365260.description: This just cuts right down to the bone.

268533563.name: Retro Super Villain Laser Gun
268533563.description: This is what villains of the past thought laser guns would look like in the future. Shoot turquoise green beams at your foes to do 20 damage per hit. If you've got more time, you can click and hold to charge and do up to 65 damage per hit!

26013203.name: Freeze Ray
26013203.description: Stop your enemies in their tracks and freeze them in a giant block of ice.

52625733.name: Merica Airwalker
52625733.description: Cuz this is my United States of Whatever....

141759818.name: Sleep Wand
141759818.description: You're getting very sleepy!  Put your nearby foes to sleep for a short while.

365642085.name: Frozen Blue Ice Crossbow
365642085.description: Fire ice cold arrows at your foes, which will occasionally freeze them upon hit. Each hit does 20 damage.

16986805.name: Pumpkin Pi
16986805.description: This is for everyone who complained that the last contest was too easy... MUAHAHAHAHAAHAHAHAHAHAHA!

186958653.name: Frozen Flail
186958653.description: Click to use the flail to hit your enemies. This does 15 damage. Double click to quickly whip the flail in front of you in a slashing motion, which does 20 damage. Click and hold to swing the flail around in a circular motion above your shoulder.

123134949.name: BLOXcon Hall of Fame 2013 Award
123134949.description: You. Win. This trophy is awarded to winners of ROBLOX's 2013 Hall of Fame. Bask in the glory of being one of the community's top builders!

1469987740.name: The 5th Annual Bloxy Award
1469987740.description: This award was given out to the winners of the Annual Bloxy Awards, honoring the best game creators, builders, artists, and video makers on Roblox.

91294485.name: Hungry Lion Friend
91294485.description: He's hungry, but he's also your friend.  So he probably won't eat you.... probably.

228588772.name: Tough Chicks Throwing Stars
228588772.description: These chicks are tough and bound to do a lot of damage!

179369627.name: Ghost Ride
179369627.description: Sit atop this dark spirit and fly through the night.

93746675.name: Crash
93746675.description:
Get Crash and your in-game wingman! You never know what he's going to do next. 
Brand New Crash & Bernstein Mondays at 8:30PM/7:30c on Disney XD!

99174250.name: Magic Snowman
99174250.description: It's the most magical time of the year!  Also the coldest....

114020538.name: Astral Cloak of Transportation
114020538.description: All magical secrets are held by the Wizards of the Astral Isles, but they don't mind lending out this cloak.  Just don't ask how it gets you from A to B.

233519998.name: Bunny Ninja Master Sai
233519998.description: The great bunny ninja masters could slice very quickly, as well as hop great distances through the air. They could even channel powerful bunny bombs to fling their enemies far from them.

86494914.name: Dual Katanas of the DarkAge Clan
86494914.description: These ancient katanas have been passed down from generation to generation of DarkAge ninjas.  Only the most agile may learn to wield the dual katanas.

2008153855.name: RDC First Runner Up 2018 - Silver
2008153855.description: Congratulations on being the First Runner Up at the 2018 RDC Game Jam!

2620441860.name: 2019 Spinning Noisemaker
2620441860.description: Ring the new year in with as much noise as possible.

110337828.name: Common Egg Compass - Egg Hunt 2013
110337828.description: This item will only work in the official ROBLOX Egg Hunt 2013 level for the duration of this year's egg hunt.  This will point you in the direction of one of four common eggs.

49929746.name: Knights of Redcliff: Morning Star
49929746.description: The Redcliffs victory over the Sorcutrolls is widely attributed to the use of the Morning Star.  The Redcliff Morning Star can break body joints and we all know that when a head joint is broken - it's an instant game over.

149638899.name: Lepremon
149638899.description: Trollamon's favorite Leprechaun friend is here to throw exploding gold at anyone silly enough to try and come near you.

1030943683.name: Roblox Pom-Poms
1030943683.description: Cheer on your favorite team, or anything, with these pom-poms!

99206951.name: Holiday Ray Gun
99206951.description: Light up the tree (and everything else!) with this holiday ray gun!  Available exclusively to users who redeem a $25 Walmart card in December

114020505.name: Knights of RedCliff: Battle Horn
114020505.description: Blow thy horn and blast thy foes as the noble RedCliff Eagles swarm unto the battlefield doing justice to thy goals.

147937284.name: Disco Ball
147937284.description: The party don't start 'til you walk in... This sweet disco ball makes everybody want to dance.

134109039.name: Sorcus's Scythe Of Death
134109039.description:
Behold, all souls are mine; the soul of the father as well as the soul of the son is mine: the soul who sins shall die.
Available in the ROBLOX Halloween 2013: The Witching Hour event in Battle - http://www.roblox.com/Early-Beta-Access-Phase-2-Halloween-2013-The-Wi-place?id=130815926

40811356.name: Frosted Santa, Harbinger of Christmas Creep
