40811356.description: The FIRST jingle announces his presence to the world. The SECOND jingle causes only chaos. The THIRD jingle offers great opportunity. The FOURTH jingle will be the last, and then, my friends, the music stops.

501940219.name: Wanwood Sword Cane
501940219.description:
Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out www.roblox.com/toys to learn more...

420160506.name: Deadly Laser Vision Polar Bear Mount
420160506.description: Rideable polar bear that shoots deadly laser beams out of his eyes. Hop on his back and use 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D', or the arrow keys to move around. Click to shoot deadly lasers from the polar bears eyes. If hit, your opponent will take 40-70 points of damage.  Disclaimer- this is not a real polar bear. No polar bears were harmed in the making of this virtual polar bear robot. Please do not attempt to ride polar bears irl. Please do not attempt to attach lasers to real polar bears. Does not require batteries.  Is virtual.  Is subject to additional disclaimers in very small print below the bottom of this visible text. Not really though. If you meet a polar bear - please be cool and don't approach it.  This is actually good advice for pretty much any bear.

2535479252.name: Classic Bionic Arm
2535479252.description: We can rebuild you, we have the technology, and you’ll be better, stronger, faster! Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy! Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

101191388.name: Dual Illumina
101191388.description: Light and deadly- twice as deadly as a single Illumina!  This item came out of the Coolest Gift on December 21st, 2012.

76170545.name: Race the Sunset
76170545.description: Another original ROBLOX 2D game.  Can you beat the sunset?

66426103.name: Gamaboi
66426103.description: Play the fabulous Quest for Glory 2! 3 ultimate boss fights will challenge you to your very core!

18426536.name: Apple Pie
18426536.description: I know banana cream is the traditional comedy throwing pie. I know that. But people don't eat banana cream pie for Thanksgiving, unless they work in a comedy factory and get them for free. Careful, the apples are hot!

121385328.name: Super Strong Man
121385328.description: Eating these veggies will make you big and strong and ready to power slam anybody!

183665594.name: Light's Reflection Sword
183665594.description: This sword belongs to the one destined to vanquish the shadows.  It's wielder will glow in the burning flames of destiny and do 35 damage per strike.  This sword will collect the light energy of it's enemies which can be used to aid your jump as you attack in midair.

153939226.name: Wild Bunny Horde Attack
153939226.description: When bunnies attack- the true ROBLOX story.  Deploy your attack bunny and he will summon all his bunny clan to fight on your behalf.   After you deploy the bunny holes spawn and bunnies pop up to follow your commands.

236443047.name: Regular Carpet
236443047.description: You walk past a rug shop, where a clerk tries to sell you a magic carpet.  You tell him you don't want a magic carpet today. He then admits to you that he was lying, and this really is just a regular carpet. His whole life is a lie. Then he starts crying. You kind of have to buy it after that.  This is a regular carpet and it literally does nothing.

206566653.name: Primeval Crossbow
206566653.description: This item gets better with more use!  Shoot arrows at your foes, and the more you use it the faster you are able to reload it! Eventually you'll be firing so quickly that you'll unleash the bow's primeval rage!  You'll hear the mighty dinosaur roar and the arrows will flame as you unleash tons of arrows at once.

218631022.name: Laser Throwing Stars
218631022.description: Nothing cuts like laser! Throw these at your foe to do tons of damage!

16924676.name: Tic Tac Toe Board
16924676.description: Play a quick game of Tic Tac Toe with a nearby player! (Get close to another player and click on them to start a game - they need to accept your challenge for the game to start).

183355969.name: Metal Fists
183355969.description: Punch with your vicious metal fist to do 15 damage. If double clicked, you swing the fists into each other.  Anyone unfortunate enough to get caught between them takes 50 damage! Click 'Q' to smash at the ground with the fists, creating boulders from the ground. Anyone hit by these boulders is dealt 40 damage. Click 'E' to knock your fists together, creating a shock wave. If hit, a player is knocked back and dealt a tiny amount of damage.

78026639.name: 1337 R0807
78026639.description: Its a head, with a mouth that shoots Rockets?? Classic Cannon head!

91360028.name: Puppet Master
91360028.description: The puppet master runs the show!  Force others to do your bidding - and look silly.  Why?  No one asks the puppet master why.

1132884456.name: Chopper Broom
1132884456.description: Hey bud, wanna race? Equip and click and drag to rev your engine and fly around in the direction of your cursor.

2549005282.name: Roblox Character Encyclopedia
2549005282.description: A comprehensive guide to some of the most of popular characters from the world of Roblox, complete with an exclusive Outrageous Builderman figure!

85879465.name: Torso Cannon
85879465.description: Yummy yummy yummy, I've got cannons in my tummy!

86492467.name: Stealth Ninja Potion
86492467.description: Turn into a stealth double jumping ninja!

85145662.name: Lunar Lander 2D Game
85145662.description: Land on the crate and get it home safely.  One of the most challenging 2D games yet!

4771621161.name: Star Creaeggtor Cannon 9001
4771621161.description: Don't shoot this cannon at 3 AM! (what happens next will shock you!) Find you favorite video star creator and earn this exclusive egg!

18466105.name: War Turkey
18466105.description: Nobody wants seconds with this turkey.  The first throw does enough damage!

306163602.name: Overseer Spider Mount
306163602.description: Climb aboard your very own spider. Walk on the ground or climb up walls!

161211085.name: Triple Plungers
161211085.description: Because dual plungers is not always enough!  Fire these disgusting plungers at your foes to do 20 damage per plunger hit.

439307591.name: Fruity Pebbles Power Up
439307591.description: This is advertising. Yet also delicious. In fact, so delicious that if you use it in game you will find yourself jumping to new heights

98253592.name: Rukiryo's ROBLOX Tablet
98253592.description: Winner: Rukiryo. ROBLOX will be in touch to redeem this prize. Void if sold, traded, or deleted.

869123788.name: 8-Bit Frog Friend
869123788.description: A faithful friend who follows you around, just keep him away from the road.

1178843200.name: Jumanji Rhino
1178843200.description: Partake in the adventures of Jumanji with this rhino in our Roblox experience!

180300142.name: Trick or Trap Jackolantern
180300142.description: Place this tricky little pumpkin in the ground.  It will grow and call out to other players.  If the players touch the pumpkin they will receive a trick or a treat.  The trick is a deadly explosion.  The treat is a delicious chocolate bar.

220289039.name: Egg Launcher 2015
220289039.description: You're opponents won't know what hit them! Actually they definitely will - as there will be egg on their screen!

467137230.name: Spinning Robot Helmet
467137230.description: Your head is spinning! And it's unstoppable! Click to toggle the front light on and off.

75550907.name: Sports Victory Blaster
75550907.description: Best part of a touchdown? The victory dance afterwards. This will make everyone you shoot act like they just scored a touchdown.

14130887.name: Maniacal Pumpkin Bomb
14130887.description: I can't decide which is better. The huge explosion, or the maniacal laughter that precedes it.

78005022.name: Flak Cannon
78005022.description: Designed for advanced players, this weapon is extremely powerful if you get the timing just right.  Mess it up?  You might just end up with a wipe out.

139578207.name: Tri-Laser 333
139578207.description: Does exactly what the name says - shoots three lasers.

382837706.name: Opened Delicious Basket of the Crispiest Chicken
382837706.description: You eat so many chicken legs you're going to turn into one! Inside you find... Fried Chicken Hat.

336370943.name: Laser Gun of Tomorrow
336370943.description: Click to fire a burst of 5 neon teal colored lasers! Each do 8 damage. If all 5 hit their target, that's a total of 40 damage!

19328185.name: Snowball
19328185.description: Life is like a snowball. The important thing is finding wet snow and a really long hill....

72713855.name: Gigantoform
72713855.description: Double your size and and tower over your opponents.

186868641.name: Snow and Arrow
186868641.description: Click and hold to pull the arrow back further, charging it and increasing its damage. Minimum damage is 5, and maximum is 66.

435116927.name: Katana of the Golden Snake
435116927.description: Click to slash dealing 22 damage. When your opponent least expects it, double click to dash at him and strike dealing up to 50 damage!

53623322.name: Sorcus' Sword of Judgement
53623322.description: "Judge a man by his questions rather than by his answers" -Voltaire

14719505.name: Cavalry Sabre
14719505.description: You're ready to defend the Wild West with this sabre!

53130850.name: Brighteyes's Sparkling Shillelagh
53130850.description: Made with solid oak, and sprinkled with some Brighteyes’s magic, this sparkling Shillelagh, will help you bend some bones! Watch out, this Shillelagh hits hard!

91518057.name: Terratronic Ray Gun - A Walmart Exclusive
91518057.description: Blast away anything that gets in your way.

188853857.name: Arctic Fox Tail
188853857.description: Wear this arctic fox tail and spin to hit your enemies and deal 22.5 damage per hit.

273970482.name: Hot Pepper Launcher
273970482.description: That's a spicy pepper!  Shoot red, green, and yellow peppers at your foes. When your foes get hit by a red pepper, they will turn red and run around, flailing their arms uncontrollably! Green makes your opponents vomit greenish bricks. If your foes get hit with a yellow pepper, their speed will be reduced.  Each pepper does 20 damage per hit!

315565799.name: Electrowarrior Boomerang
315565799.description: Throw this glowing boomerang at your foes. Each hit will do 30 damage!

2620451289.name: Deluxe Luxury Magic Sled
2620451289.description: Not to be confused with the “Luxury Magic Sled”; the Deluxe has speed AND comfort.

22788102.name: Math Homework
22788102.description: I was doing my math homework and there was this problem about if a plane travels at 11x the speed of a train and the train is 3x.....blah blah blah...I made a plane!

64447616.name: Poisoned Apple
64447616.description: "But hardly had she a bit of it in her mouth than she fell down dead."  This came out of the Kitchewitch Gift on 10/25/2011

16433862.name: Bat Sword
16433862.description: na na na na na na na na BAT SWORD!

15731350.name: Leland the Lolturtle
15731350.description: Leland does it for the lulz.

21440120.name: Protest Sign: Save the Zombies
21440120.description: Just because they are flesh eating monsters doesn't mean they don't have rights!

212296400.name: Magician's Cloak
212296400.description: Talk about energy efficient - you can travel all over ROBLOX using only the power of magic- and this cloak.

201756469.name: Smashing Guitar
201756469.description: Rock that solo and when you're done - smash this guitar and watch it burst into flames- in true rock star fashion!

77443436.name: Swordbreaker
77443436.description: Fights like a sword - breaks enemies swords - who could ask for anything more?

243791145.name: Bluesteel Katana
243791145.description: “Only by living at the edge of death can you understand the indescribable joy of life.”

427949130.name: Rainbow Blaster
427949130.description: This is advertising. But that don’t matter - does it, Hot Shot? This is a dandy blaster that’s loaded with the full spectrum of colour! Bang.

188644771.name: Captain Skeledeath's Axe
188644771.description: Part of the Captain Skeledeath package.  This axe does 16 damage per hit. Double click to do a special skeledamage attack which does 25 points of damage.

173781053.name: Bacon Launcher
173781053.description: Equip this awesome bacon launcher to start cooking that sizzling bacon. Click to fire bacon at your foes.

59805584.name: Korblox Krossbow
59805584.description: The Korblox Krossbows are powerful against all enemies.  Use the secret move, and it's unstoppable.

88885497.name: S-79 Speed Stunter
88885497.description: This explosive creates a 10-second poisonous cloud with a 20-foot radius, slowing affected players' movements for up to ten seconds and doing 10 damage per second if you get caught in the cloud.

50938746.name: Fermion Blade
50938746.description: Beware the wrath of the holder of the Fermion Blade. It may look cheerful, but after feeling its power, you probably won't be.

1304344132.name: Ninja Battle Hog Mount
1304344132.description: Ride this fearless battle hog into war against your rival ninja dojo.

283756680.name: Ultraviolet Blaster
283756680.description: Pew! Pew! Neon magenta laser beams are everywhere, but you don't care because you're the one shooting them! This weapon is good for shooting things from a distance. Hit 'Z' to activate the scope and use the mouse to zoom in and get a better view of the target.

37347081.name: Acursed Mummy Hand of Head Shot

1587175338.name: Orinthian Crossbow
1587175338.description: Don’t get caught up in the crossfire.

398122908.name: Robloxian Battle Shield
398122908.description: Use this to keep you safe and looking fierce - 'cause you are a champion and we want to hear you roar! Preferably louder than a lion. Claim your shield as part of the Battle Arena

69947367.name: Knights of the Seventh Sanctum : Dual Duel Axes
69947367.description: You're dueling.  Your opponent has an axe... but you have two!  Wield the unholy relics of the Seventh Sanctum and no one else stands a chance... unless they have these axes too.  But how likely is that?

90211299.name: Tiger Skin
90211299.description: When you are wearing this - you become stronger and faster.  Enemies will fear your touch as a single strike while wearing the skin will disarm them...literally.

94794833.name: Cloak of the Undying
94794833.description: Adorn this cloak, and none shall stand in thou's way, m'lord.

790979662.name: Lightning McQueen Companion
790979662.description: Have Lightning McQueen by your side as you watch Disney•Pixar’s Cars 3 in Theaters June 16, 2017!

59190534.name: Statue Staff of Stony Justice
59190534.description: Your enemies will have a heart of stone.  Because you've petrified them!  Petrifies your enemies 1/10 times.

99254241.name: DailyBasis' ROBLOX Tablet
99254241.description: Winner: DailyBasis. ROBLOX will be in touch to redeem this prize. Void if sold, traded, or deleted.

243007180.name: HEX Spitter
243007180.description: A genuine Hex style laser blaster- shoot lightning lasers at lightning fast rates.

73829193.name: Grimgold Periastron Beta
73829193.description: The sword men use to fight bears... in space.

229909386.name: Opened ROBLOX Basket of Self Eggspression
229909386.description: "But mom, metal music is how I eggspress myself!" Inside you find... Eggcelent ROBLOX Headphones.

939132399.name: Bubblegum Bomber
939132399.description:
Swoop from above and glide in colorful style. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

71037056.name: Magic Lamp
71037056.description: Rub the lamp, and a genie appears to grant you a wish.

24419822.name: Protest Sign: Egg Hunt Nao
24419822.description: What do we want?  Egg Hunts!  When do we want them?  Soonish!

180298135.name: Morblox the Terrifying's Sword
180298135.description: You'd be afraid too... Part of the Morblox the Terrifying package.

74385386.name: Razevenge
74385386.description: Razevenge is a dish best served cold.

26417031.name: Magical Rainbow Pony
26417031.description: Magical rainbow transport pony!!! Fell out of ReeseMcBlox's Mystery Pony Pinata.

215355320.name: Bloxster BZR
215355320.description: If you ain't first, you're last!

140490812.name: Eccentric Time Keeper's Sword
140490812.description: Part of the Eccentric Time Keeper Package.  Available when you redeem a $40 ROBLOX card from GameStop in January.

83704165.name: Icedagger
83704165.description:
"Is this a dagger which I see before me,
"The handle toward my hand? Come, let me clutch thee. /
I have thee not, and yet I see thee still. /
Art thou not, fatal vision, sensible / 
To feeling as to sight? or art thou but /
A dagger of the mind, a false creation, /
Proceeding from the heat-oppressed brain?"

24839406.name: Bad Bad Bunny
24839406.description: Bad Bad Bunny likes to confuse egg hunters with his explosive decoy eggs!

32199868.name: ROBLOX Interns 2010 Mug
32199868.description: They say inspiration is fueled by delicious coffee...and Chavez - but that's something else altogether.

36568603.name: Porter's Pumpkin Pitchfork
36568603.description: Whether posing for a rural portrait, shoveling some hay, or eating the biggest salad ever made, this gothic pitchfork is perfect for when normal forks just aren’t big enough (or if your spoon is already too big). Also works very well for fending off all those things that go bump in the night.

186868758.name: Snowy Gravity Coil
186868758.description: As you walk, leave behind a trail of ice, and as you leap, the north wind gives you a boost the whole way, lifting you high and dropping you gently.

22152171.name: Ceramic Potion
22152171.description: Dust from Atlantis, ground unicorn horn, and cookie crumbs. This potion increases your max health, at a slight cost to speed.

16200508.name: Surface Tool
16200508.description: A tool to change the Surfaces of objects during Group Building

483899693.name: Viridian Hoverboard
483899693.description: Roll in high fashion with this stylish viridian board.

1360077860.name: The Duke's Blade of Due Process
1360077860.description: Swift justice. Cuts through red tape like no one’s business.

945527020.name: Emerald Knights of the Seventh Sanctum Lance
945527020.description: A more elegant weapon for more civilized age. Does 5 to 20 damage per thrust. Part of the Emerald Knights of the Seventh Sanctum Lancer.

180313580.name: Halloween Roped
180313580.description: Riding this Roped is an otherworldly experience!  You'll be transformed into a spooky ghost as you ride around town.  Press 'X' to emit a scary light from your Jack O Lantern. Hit 'Shift' to get a boost your speed for 15 seconds.

93536867.name: Zombification Injection
93536867.description: Steal other people's life force to transform yourself into a powerful and angry zombie.  As a zombie, use your powerful hammer to do 40 damage per hit to other players.

155414424.name: Terra Warrior Staff
155414424.description: Part of the Terra Warrior package.  Allows you to fling earth at your foes doing 35 damage per hit.

123234673.name: Camping Machete
123234673.description: Perfect for chopping firewood... or your foes!

65469908.name: Skull Cracker - Level Up Exclusive
65469908.description: Does this even need a description?  This cracks skulls!  Dante's weapon of choice!

15179006.name: Helen The Hiphipapotamus
15179006.description: Meet Helen, the Hiphipapotamus. Helen is the #1 toy in Robloxia and if you want to find her in a toy store, you better be packing heat to deal with all the other crazy parents trying to buy one.

85145626.name: Bear Arm
85145626.description: You have the right to bear arms and to bear other people's arms...yeah it's literal.

2316760298.name: Staff of Healing
2316760298.description: Asclepius, son of Apollo, Greek god of medicine grants his power to this staff. Click to heroically heal the injured.

54130552.name: Starfish Shooter
54130552.description: Launches a starfish, and it will stick to your target.  Shoot too many starfish and it might obscure your opponent's vision!

63721700.name: Black Steel Throwing Bats
63721700.description: Because when you need the job done right, you need Black Steel.

64160538.name: Ghost Invisibility Elixir
64160538.description: Pop out at your enemies when they least expect it.  This magical elixir makes you completely invisible to other players for a limited amount of time.

72069855.name: Cupid's Revenge
72069855.description: Love hurts.  No it doesn't really, but these arrows do!

176087640.name: ROBLOX U Free Stuff Launcher
176087640.description: Stuff! People love stuff!  Launch free pizza and tee shirts from this cannon.

286527185.name: Merely's Bluesteel Hoverboard
286527185.description: Merely is basically the Tony Hawk of hoverboarding.

55302225.name: Independence Roman Candle
55302225.description: What better way to show off your independence than lighting off a Roman Candle?

527384527.name: Mostly Ghostly Potion
527384527.description: How can you be mostly ghostly? Click to fly around as a ghost; your character appears transparent and can fly!

16895215.name: Darkheart
16895215.description: It's darker than RGB(0,0,0) and it steals life from your enemies. What more is there to say.

515688568.name: Pumpkin Launcher
515688568.description: Show your Halloween spirit and blast pumpkins all around.

507797529.name: 8-Bit Skateboard
507797529.description: Go on a radical adventure with this 8-bit board. Click to spawn in front of you, hit Ctrl P to pick back up!

1513262045.name: Unicorn Nunchuks
1513262045.description: Unicorns may be peaceful, but their horns aren’t. Ouch! Click to swing at your foes to deal 18 to 26 points of damage per hit.

139578571.name: Spec Chi Biograft Energy Sword
139578571.description: After the Christmas wars of 3010 all promised never to forget. People knew they must remain vigilant to protect against the revolt of the Santa bots and the factory elves.  This sword was specially designed to protect against festive robots of all seasons.

928806888.name: Red Fidget Spinner
928806888.description: Red is where it's at! The fidget spinner will spin when you click on it and each time you click on it, the faster it will spin.

115377964.name: Laser Finger Pointers
115377964.description: The second you equip these, lasers will begin to shoot from your fingers. The color of the laser is up to you. Each click will cycle between a red (does damage), green (heals players), or blue laser (pushes and trips other players). Just be careful--once this is equipped, the lasers will fire! Looks great in places with dynamic lighting!

583026228.name: Polar Warrior's Spear
583026228.description: Click to lunge this spear at your enemies; dealing roughly 20 damage per hit.  Part of the Polar Warrior's package.

66416616.name: Zeus's Lightning Bolt Staff
66416616.description: Hurl lightning at your enemies.  Because they probably deserve it.

11450664.name: Slateskin Potion
11450664.description: Ingredients: one part dust from the oldest mountain, two parts dirt from the deepest sea, three parts lava from the core of the earth, and one splinter from the Rock of Prometheus. Drinking this potion transforms your skin into rock, allowing you to take more damage than the average Robloxian. It also makes you heavier, which will slow you down slightly.

11115851.name: Shadowy Ninja Star of the Silent House
11115851.description: In a space where there is no room, behind a waterfall that makes no sound, stands the Silent House, which does not exist.

184760397.name: Steampunk Bow
184760397.description: Click and hold to build up steam pressure so you can shoot your arrows!  Once you have enough pressure, you can release to fire a heated piece of rebar at your foes to deal 35 damage. If you max out the boiler pressure, the bow will instead fire three pieces of rebar in a fan-shaped pattern. No matter how many projectiles you fire, their speed is determined by the amount of pressure in the system.

129457095.name: Captain Underpants Book
129457095.description: Captain Underpants is back—in full color, super cool graphics!  Go back in time and find out how Captain Underpants was created!  Follow George and Harold on their wild adventure and get ready to laugh out loud!

161075864.name: Hiccup's Flaming Sword - Sponsored by HTTYD2
161075864.description: What every dragon trapper needs. One end coats the blade in Monstrous Nightmare saliva, the other sprays Hideous Zippleback gas!  Learn how to code your dragon - check out the video on the Bloxcon page http://www.roblox.com/event/bloxcon.

725802037.name: Star-Lord’s Blaster
725802037.description:
Defend the galaxy and equip yourself with some speed!

Be sure to watch Guardians of the Galaxy: Volume 2 in theaters May 5!

152173291.name: Opened Violet  Basket of Equal Cosmic Time
152173291.description: Everything is in perfect balance. Inside you find... violet equinox.

1602503043.name: Wakandan Shield
1602503043.description: See Captain America fight to save the universe in Marvel Studios Avengers: Infinity War. In theaters April 27th!

180298769.name: Swarm of Bats
180298769.description: Your loyal bat colony will follow you and do your bidding.  Click a player within a 100 stud radius and the your swarm of bats descends upon them - doing 5 damage per hit. These bats are not just any common colony, they are also trained to do a special attack.  Press 'Q' to begin firing bats forward from your arms, which deal 5 damage per hit.

686806111.name: Brainy Smurf
686806111.description: When in doubt, you can always count on Brainy to have the answer! Be sure to catch Smurfs the Lost Village in theaters April 7th!

1145081326.name: Fang of Tsuchigumo
1145081326.description:
Beware this venom in the form of a blade. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

225921000.name: Rainbow Magic Carpet
225921000.description: Ride your own rainbow through the skies of ROBLOX! Use the 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D' or arrow keys to control the direction. A magical rainbow trail will track your path through the sky.

1560400932.name: Chef de Cuisine Frying Pan
1560400932.description: Food fight! Click to fling hot food at your foes. Part of the Chef de Cuisine package.

101079008.name: Fancy Skateboard
101079008.description: Who says skaters are slackers?  Not us!

34398653.name: ROBLOX Grab Bag
34398653.description: It's filled with ROBLOX goodies just for you!

11419882.name: Red Stratobloxxer
11419882.description: How to rock: 1) Equip Red Stratobloxxer. 2) Change notes by pressing [f,g,h,j,k,l] 3) Left click.

18268645.name: Disintergrex Blast Gun
18268645.description: Veteran space pirates swear by these, though they are hard to find these days. Manufactured specifically to combat robots in the War of the Second Uprising, the Disintergrex uses patented tri-pulse technology. Thus the hugely successful marketing slogan: "If it's still moving, shoot it three times!"

230758639.name: Opened Bluesteel Basket of Spiky Pwnage
230758639.description: Nothing beats the feel of genuine bluesteel! Inside you find... Bluesteel Horns of Pwnage.

124127383.name: Merely's Sparkle Time Hoverboard
124127383.description: Hover over the skies and speed over your challengers, sparkling all the way.

76170471.name: Hedgehog Friend
76170471.description: Why can't they just share the hedge?

30847733.name: Vine Staff
30847733.description: Creates a wall of vines around your character. Anyone attempting to get through the vines tends to get stuck.

1149193097.name: Valentine’s Throwing Stars
1149193097.description: Throw deadly love at your enemies!

416846710.name: Epic Golden Sword and Shield
416846710.description: Click to swing dealing 15 to 22 damage; double click to spin-dash at your opponent while on fire!

126719093.name: Not-so-friendly Ghost
126719093.description: Orbits around you ready to strike your foes down at any minute!

13206856.name: Jungle Guitar
13206856.description: Great for jamming in the jungle or making rhythms in the rainforest.

30393548.name: Grapple Hook
30393548.description: Seize the day (and pretty much anything else you want to seize) with this grappling gun.

456221232.name: Party Blaster Paint Gun
456221232.description: Ain't no party like a paint gun party, cuz it stains and it's hard to wash out. Fire paintballs of all different colors at your enemies!

346687267.name: Green Elf Bow
346687267.description: Click and hold to charge your arrows.  Depending on how long it's charged, damage can range between 9 and 33. If fully charged, you can fire three arrows at once, dealing around 70 to 80 damage!

939151180.name: Business Cat's Business Briefcase
939151180.description:
What do you keep in a case like this? It's all business, baby! Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

104642566.name: Fake C4
104642566.description:
Tick tick tick...this one's a dud!  Prank your friends with
this fake C4.

106064315.name: Noxious Chocolate
106064315.description: Share this candy with your enemies.  Forces them to eat the candy (which is poisonous) and causes them to drop their weapons!

88143166.name: Vaulting Pole
88143166.description: Victory is only one jump away.

106064469.name: Year of the Snake Lantern
106064469.description: Carry this lantern and let the snakes protect you.  The spirits of snake ancestors will follow you around and harm anyone they touch (everyone other than you of course!).

292044716.name: Woodland Archer Bow
292044716.description: Part of the Woodland Archer package!

206799274.name: Emerald Hyperbike
206799274.description: Travel at hyperspeed and leave a trail of burning green light behind you.  Now with improved acceleration!

110337782.name: Fabrege Cloner - Egg Hunt 2013
110337782.description: This item will only work in the official ROBLOX Egg Hunt 2013 level for the duration of this year's egg hunt.  When you enter the egg hunt level- set the fabrege cloner to one of a select set of fabrege eggs.  If someone in the level finds the fabrege egg you've selected while you are in the level with them, you receive the egg as well!

156467963.name: Redcliff Ballista
156467963.description: Fire arrows from this giant powerful Redcliff Ballista and do 50 damage per hit.

71422340.name: Giant Iron Sword of Sundering
71422340.description: This giant sword can only be wielded by the strongest of Robloxians.  Are you up for the challenge?

566780416.name: U.Fun.O
566780416.description: The crackle of the radio, a message in the evening sky - looks like you’ve had a close encounter of the Roblox kind!

119101539.name: Regeneration Coil
119101539.description: The latest in the power coils family - the health regeneration coil will help you regenerate your health quickly.

25535467.name: Red Pirate Juice
25535467.description: Yo ho ho and a bottle or juice! Arrrg!

19382057.name: Candy Cane
19382057.description: When you grow up candy doesn't taste as good, so enjoy it now. And that thing adults say about too much candy giving you a stomach ache is a lie, btw.

103338520.name: ROBLOXIAN Damage Orb
103338520.description: Equip these and leave them by pressing 'Q' in your wake—they only do 20 hit points of damage to other players, but each time they hit an orb, you gain a 60% speed buff!

139578061.name: Smashing Drum
139578061.description: Make beautiful music... by smashing this on someone's head!

36042596.name: ROBLOX 7-Eleven Card
36042596.description: To celebrate the release of our 7-Eleven cards, we're selling this virtual ROBLOX Card for a limited time only.  When you use it, it transforms into 1 of 9 different convenience store items!

11373617.name: Staff of the Woodlands
11373617.description: Druids of the Great Forest use the mystical powers of this wooden staff to camouflage themselves as they travel through the hinterlands. Use of this staff renders your character difficult to see for a short while.

3600625118.name: RDC 2019 Champions Trophy
3600625118.description: Congrats on your Game Jam victory! Your teamwork, creativity, and outstanding development skills serve as an inspiration to creators worldwide.

317593302.name: The Pharaohs Guard Sword
317593302.description: Click to slash, dealing 14 to 17 damage. With each slash you'll unlock the ancient power of the Pharaoh's Guard and have a chance at preforming a secret attack or enjoying a hidden power up!

66426498.name: Kami Potion
66426498.description: Fly around the world shooting laser beams out of your eyes.  Can you think of a better way to spend an afternoon?  Because I can't.  And I really tried.

89487903.name: Monster Axe
89487903.description: This axe is a monster!  Initial strike gives you 25 damage points and it continues to damage your opponent someone decides to remove the axe.

356212121.name: Steampunk Attack Birds
356212121.description: These friendly birds will fly around you, protecting you from anyone who comes near.  They'll swoop down and attack, doing 25 damage per hit!

94794774.name: Crescendo, The Soul Stealer
94794774.description: Forged with fiery flames and a demon's eye the Crescendo ascends from its ancient sleep with a thundering tone.

674104921.name: Robux Blaster
674104921.description:
Ever wonder how Robux are made? Well it ain’t like this since these are only lasers shaped like Robux. Now go out and make it rain...laser beams! 

**Item does not grant Robux**

105351503.name: Dragon's Blaze Dagger
105351503.description: The path through a dragon den is very rarely flame free.  Get this exclusive dagger when you redeem a ROBLOX card from Sainsbury's by February 28th.

32355759.name: Bag O' Noobs
32355759.description: Aim carefully at your foe and release a group of three noobs. Aim really carefully and you might even make someone catch noob-itis.

1033137155.name: Deluxe Green Roped
1033137155.description: This stylish green roped will keep you traveling in deluxe style. It moves faster than the red roped and does sweet jumps with more ease than ever before.

257837994.name: Heather’s Boots
257837994.description: We stole Heather’s boots. Then, we blamed her dragon and said she ate them. The perfect plan! And now you get boots! (You’re welcome.)

80576952.name: Time Bomb
80576952.description:
Black shell, white clock, Cadillac, / yeah
The bomb's a time bomb

972189904.name: Future Hammer
972189904.description: Smash them back to the stone age with this mighty hammer.

204485737.name: Golden Bow and Arrow
204485737.description: This golden bow is stylish and effective.  Click and hold to charge your arrows and increase the damage your arrow does! When you hit your enemy with a fully charged arrow they will turn into solid gold for 15 seconds. Press 'Q' to use the bow as a grappling hook.

460099901.name: Anti-Gravity Acorn
460099901.description: Use this Acorn to reach new heights as you look for a safe place to hide it! And be sure to see Ice Age: Collision Course, in theaters July 22!

163354553.name: Bluesteel Midas Hand
163354553.description: The Bluesteel Midas Hand will turn anything into beautiful Bluesteel!

42845853.name: Super Freeze Ray 2011
42845853.description: The only thing strong enough to counter a freeze ray?  A steaming cup of hot chocolate!

21802000.name: Sword of Nefertiti
21802000.description: Wrath of the gods. And those ancient Egyptian gods were pretty wrathful.

181245094.name: Troll Summoner
181245094.description: Use this item in Hallow's Eve 2014 to summon the elusive trolls!  This item only works in Hallow's Eve 2014.  Play the game here - http://www.roblox.com/Hallows-Eve-2014-The-Witching-Hour-Returns-place?id=180331551.

60888200.name: DarkAge Ninjas: SunFire Scroll
60888200.description: Use the power of the scroll, to unleash a torrent of sunfire blast around you!

26774629.name: Ego Expander 2400
26774629.description: He's got a big ego.  In fact, it may be so big that his head explodes!

59190543.name: Azurewrath's Return
59190543.description: His Magnificence keeps this dagger in his boot for emergencies and it always comes back.

112591894.name: Beach Battle Sword
112591894.description: The battle for beach supremacy is on!  Send walls of water crashing on your enemies.

47597760.name: Golden Chakram of the Sky Palace
47597760.description: This chakram was said to belong to a reclusive group of ninjas so enlightened that it was said they could communicate with inanimate objects. Legend has it they never carried more than one weapon, because they could call out to it from anywhere in the world, and it would always faithfully return.

420161128.name: Pogo Stick
420161128.description: Jump higher than you've ever dreamed!

2846003729.name: Green Flashlight
2846003729.description:
It’s so dark and there’s probably monsters! I can’t see anything! Get me out of here! (CLICK) Who, me scared? Nah. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

462294549.name: Rainbow Fireworks
462294549.description: This is advertising. But enough about that, you just got to ignite the light and let it shine. You got some fireworks so let the colors burst!

1990279115.name: Great White Mount
1990279115.description: Take a bite out of the sky with this hovering friendly shark.

85879447.name: Galactic Forcefield Glove
85879447.description: Charge the glove to blast your enemies!  Foes beware - touching someone while they charge the glove will result in immediate shock!

108875216.name: Implosion Bomb
108875216.description: Click once and then toss the bomb onto the ground- away from yourself of course! The implosion bomb will beep for five seconds and then implode. Everything flies inward and anyone hit will take 100 damage points!

226206639.name: Spring-loaded Jumping Stilts
226206639.description: Tower above your fellow Robloxians in these spring-loaded jumping stilts.  Then jump around. Jump around. Jump up jump up and get down.

1180417820.name: Neon Laser Launcher
1180417820.description: There is no sound in space, but that doesn't mean colors can't be loud.

477911027.name: Rainbow Disco Hyperbike with Sidecar
477911027.description: Take a friend on your crazy hyperbike adventures!

168140813.name: Flaming Halberd
168140813.description: A trail of fire follows the Halberd's blade as you swing furiously at your enemy. A hit will set the other player on fire and does 50 damage.

1180418251.name: Diablo Bow
1180418251.description: Oh how far the mighty have fallen. Use this item to soar above the crowd and shoot arrows in 1 of 2 modes. The first mode allows for a concentrated strong shot and mode two allows for rapid fire.

19703041.name: Christmas Tree Lights
19703041.description: My mom likes the little white ones. But everyone knows big clunky colored lights are best! Comes in 7 or 8 colors! Shoot them at a Christmas tree to decorate it!

163351966.name: Quadshooter
163351966.description: Because sometimes you just have to shoot four things at a time. You can fire four times, three times, before you have to reload!

302280931.name: Spider Morning Star
302280931.description: Click and hold to spin the spider in a circular motion. Release the mouse button when you're ready to send the spider hurling towards your foes.

658805662.name: Flame Guard General Sword
658805662.description:
Click to swing the sword and spawn a row of red ice crystals out in front of you. They'll burst in flames and anybody too close and hit by the shards is dealt 10 damage per hit! The closer you are to these, the more dangerous they are.

Part of the Flame Guard General package.

47262108.name: Kunai
47262108.description: The weapon is small, the danger is great.

11999247.name: Subspace Tripmine
11999247.description: WARNING: HIGH EXPLOSIVE DEVICE. When triggered, this devastating weapon rips a gashing hole in the fabric of reality - subsequent spacetime reification results in a large explosion. USE: Drop mine. Once the mine stops moving, it will enter subspace and become invisible. At this point the mine is armed. Touching the mine will set it off...

88143093.name: Pigs Boson Collider
88143093.description: Utilizing the Large Hilarity Collider, researchers created the conditions immediately after the Big Chuckle and discovered the emergence of the Pigs Boson, the fundamental particle of funny that will destroy your target for hilarity.

162857316.name: ROBLOX Summer Sparkler
162857316.description: Click this item to shoot sparkles into the sky!

2463683230.name: Spooky Spectral Attack Lollipop
2463683230.description: All tricks from this treat. Click to release this sweet weapon to attack on its own.

402305186.name: Nonmagic Carpet
402305186.description: This carpet used to be magic.  You bought it at a rug shop from a crying salesman because the situation was really awkward... Still it's cool to think that princesses and tigers used to fly around on this thing you just walk on when you enter the foyer.

42847923.name: Sword of the Winter Winds
42847923.description: Harsh and cold just like the winter winds...

86492583.name: DarkAge Assassin Crossbow
86492583.description: Once the bolt has been loosed, it's too late.  DarkAge assassins shoot with deadly accuracy.

27171403.name: Battle Axe
27171403.description: Win the battle with this awesome axe.  Features two attack modes.

21392199.name: Chocolate Milk
21392199.description: Yes, there is an irritating slurping noise.

1363011928.name: Black Panther - Spear
1363011928.description: Obtain the spear to be swift. Can you complete the missions faster than everyone? See Marvel Studio’s Black Panther in theaters February 16!

118281490.name: Seahorse
118281490.description: Celebrate World Ocean Day by riding a giant seahorse!

65546284.name: Shuriken of the Clan of the Crescent Moon
65546284.description: A superior man is modest in his speech, but exceeds in his actions.

181356054.name: All Hallow's Sword
181356054.description: Slash at your foes and deal 15 damage per hit.  If you're looking to do something a little more interesting - hit 'Q' to grow vines that will stun and trap anyone within a 15 stud radius.  The 'E' key will shoot 10 vines in front of you to hit your opponents - doing  12 damage. Finally - press the 'X' key  to activate a vine like shield, which arises from the ground and surrounds you for 20 seconds. It does 20 damage to anyone who runs into it.

1074738432.name: Gigantic Bat Wings
1074738432.description: On leathery wings, you rule the night. Click to take flight and own the sky, using the 'W' 'A' 'S' and 'D' keys to move around.

181469279.name: Spine-Chilling Sword
181469279.description: Activate this sword to unleash a trail of fire.  Swing at the things that lurk in the night (or anything else) to light them on fire with your otherworldly flames for 10 seconds and do 10 damage.

17527923.name: Pumpkin Bucket
17527923.description: It's in the "Horror" genre because it can hold a horrifyingly large amount of candy. Nomnomnom!

321345839.name: Neon Nate: The Horse Lord
321345839.description: He's not your little pony any more. He's a HORSE!

939131179.name: Aluminium Selfie Stick
939131179.description:
Because you can't always bother strangers to take your picture. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

12562495.name: R-80
12562495.description: R-80s are so fun that they're banned in all 50 states. Celebrate the birth of your country by blowing up a small piece of it!

35682284.name: Scepter of Divine Indignation
35682284.description: Call upon the might of the heavens, infused into near-unstoppable orbs of power. Features three different modes for added variety when you’re obliterating all that stands in your way.

70476446.name: Drachenstein The Guardian
70476446.description: Drachenstein The Guardian will follow you and shoot fire at anyone who comes near you.

1060280135.name: Evil Knight Sword
1060280135.description: This blade draws power from the user, its cursed blade growing stronger as the wielder is lost to despair.

232520546.name: Sir Kitty McPawnington's Sword and Sheild
232520546.description: Slash, slash, scratch your enemies to deal 25 damage. Press and hold the 'Q' key to block. This slows you down, though it doubles your health. By clicking, you can whack your enemies with the shield. This does 30 to 40 damage. If you successfully hit someone with the shield, a cat screech sound plays. Part of the Sir Kitty McPawnington's Package.

35809502.name: ROBLOX Toys R Us Card
35809502.description: To celebrate the release of ROBLOX Cards at Toys R Us we're selling a limited edition ROBLOX Card.  In game, it transforms into 1 of 8 different ROBLOX toys. For more information about ROBLOX Cards check out http://blog.roblox.com/.

69567879.name: Dark Alien Hatchling
69567879.description: When you see this egg - you better run!  As soon as the alien hatches, it's too late!

168142620.name: Boxing Glove Launcher
168142620.description: Shoot dangerous boxing gloves at your foes.  They'll probably see it coming... but that's half the fun!

2350122208.name: Cobalt Interplanetary Light Sword
2350122208.description: Its power other planetary, its glow otherworldly...

72069888.name: Heartbreaker
72069888.description: "You're a heart breaker / dream maker, love taker / Don't you mess around with me!"

127506324.name: Overseer's Axe
127506324.description: The Overseer has an endless arsenal of weapons, but the one weapon he knows he can always count on is his axe! Swing this at your foe to do up to 25 hit points of damage per hit. That's not enough for you?  Your foe will also encounter the wrath of an orb with a laser beam.

99610601.name: enyahs7's ROBLOX Tablet
99610601.description: Winner: enyahs7. ROBLOX will be in touch to redeem this prize. Void if sold, traded, or deleted.

174752553.name: Civil War Artillery
174752553.description: Equip and click this gear to drop a real live cannon in front of you.  Control the cannons direction with the 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D' keys - lift and lower it with the cannon with the 'Q' and 'E' keys.  When you've got your shot set up - sit on the cannon and click! Hitting the 'X' key will remove it from the map.

33732371.name: Gork, Your Caveman Shoulder Friend
33732371.description: He would be a better conversationalist if his vocabulary were bigger than 12 words.

99119158.name: Speed Coil
99119158.description: The gravity coil's speedy brother!  Use this coil to boost your speed.

155662087.name: Anchor Cannon
155662087.description: Anchor your competitors in place.  They'll be unable to walk for 10 seconds.

164174394.name: Protest Sign: Save the Fireworks
164174394.description: Every year millions of innocent fireworks are exploded. Save the fireworks by buying them and keeping them safe from cruel arsonists!

1149579825.name: Winged Guitar
1149579825.description: We are jejune stars, with winged guitars.

1377987605.name: Jovial Jester's Staff
1377987605.description: Spread joy and cheer, by order of the king! Part of the Jovial Jester package.

22969230.name: Emerald Scatterblaster 2000
22969230.description: To make ammo for the Emerald Scatterblaster you heat emeralds until they're vapor.  Load the emerald vapor into the scatterblaster and you're good to go!

939148317.name: Gold Microphone
939148317.description:
You can't do a mic drop unless you pick one up first. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

257342981.name: Tiny Pony Stampede
257342981.description: Summon upon a stampede of ponies to charge at your enemies with lethal force!  Click and drag to summon the ponies and indicate their starting point and running direction.

90242059.name: Adventure Island
90242059.description: Check out the latest and best new 2D game on ROBLOX.  Explore and survive on Adventure Island!  Use "ASWD" keys to move, "W" to jump, "Enter" to shoot, and "Enter" + "W" to superjump.

75906973.name: Wooden Mallet
75906973.description: Woo-woo- woo!  Win this prize by playing "Welcome to Stoogeville" and winning as Curly!  Be sure to catch the Three Stooges Movie - in theaters April 13th.  Check out the game here - http://www.roblox.com/Welcome-to-Stoogeville-place?id=74885275  Tag - 3 Stooges, Moe, Curly, Larry

109583797.name: Leprechaun Vine Scroll
109583797.description: Those little leprechauns have tricks up their sleeves!  And scrolls... so many scrolls!  Scrolls that wrap people in vines so that they can't move!

13206887.name: Spooky Guitar
13206887.description: Perfect guitar for the monster mash or a graveyard bash...

341108783.name: DarkAge Kunai
341108783.description: Throw 5 at once!  Upon equipping a kunai, you can click 4 more time in the next 1.5 seconds to equip all five!  Each deals 15 damage.

212296936.name: Red Hyperlaser Gun
212296936.description: Everyone knows that red is the fastest color laser beam. That's why it's a one hit KO.

124126528.name: Seranok's Golden Chalice of Fame
124126528.description: Hold this chalice while it oozes fame all around you spawning pawns as you go.

542184488.name: 8-Bit Duck Friend
542184488.description: No need to hunt for this duck, this faithful friend will spawn on click and follow you around. Click around nearby and he'll fly to that designated spot as well.

37821996.name: Riddling Skull Sword
37821996.description: Next time someone says "riddle me this" you can let your sword do the talking.

151292047.name: Staff of Staff
151292047.description: This staff is ready to do maximum staff damage.  The Staff of Staff fires tiny damage-causing bloxikins at your foes to do 15 damage per hit.  Hit the 'Q' key to perform a special attack.

1856115349.name: Knife of lolololeris
1856115349.description:
It’s loleris’s knife and it’s sharp! Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

401277404.name: Trophy of Participation 2016
401277404.description: This trophy stands as proof that this user earned the heely-wheely item that was available during a 2016 event.

148791372.name: Pi Launcher
148791372.description: What better way to celebrate Pi day than with this Pi Launcher? Throw all kinds of flavors of pies at your foes.  Like real pies, each has it's own flavor... damage flavor that is.

24294377.name: Scribbly XD
24294377.description: Wanna scribble? I got more paint than the East Side Gallery.

69499452.name: Laservision Shades G3
69499452.description: ROBLOX brings you Laservision! Shoot  lasers from your eyes like a CIA agent!  Sweet!

152971952.name: Opened Retro Egg Basket of I Has
152971952.description: You has a basket.  Inside you find... Agonizingly Blue Bucket of Doom.

152173333.name: Opened Cool Egg Basket of Spring
152173333.description: Stay cool with this traditional spring egg basket.  What's inside? You'll have to wait and see! Inside you find... B.A. Bunny!

40493542.name: Sword of the Autumnal Winds
40493542.description: Leafing your enemies in your dust....

1076457286.name: Count Bloxula Sword
1076457286.description: This blade contains a power more evil than evil itself. Part of the Count Bloxula package.

98341183.name: mygame43's ROBLOX Tablet
98341183.description: Winner: mygame43. ROBLOX will be in touch to redeem this prize. Void if sold, traded, or deleted.

409745306.name: Sword of the Epicredness
409745306.description: Click to slash, dealing 16 to 22 damage. Hit the 'Q' key, to shoot red flames out in all directions, which will slow your enemies and deal 25 additional damage!  The sword sends out an explosive neon red orb from its center which quickly expands and explodes. Anybody caught in the explosion is dealt 40 damage.

85150872.name: Golden Cobra Staff
85150872.description: Snakes!  Why does it always have to be snakes?

880506541.name: Attack Sloth
880506541.description: He just wants a hug...a real slow one...Does 5 damage and slows down your opponents!

70353298.name: Protest: ROBLOXians Against SOPA
70353298.description: ROBLOX is against online censorship. Read our full position on SOPA/PIPA here: http://blog.roblox.com/2012/01/stop-online-piracy-act-sopa-and-roblox-our-stance/. If you agree, show your support with this sign!

97886188.name: TheGamer101's ROBLOX Tablet
97886188.description: Winner: TheGamer101. ROBLOX will be in touch to redeem this prize. Void if sold, traded, or deleted.

12145515.name: Wooden Sword
12145515.description: Wooden swords and painted wings and ephemeral treasured things.

125013799.name: Battle Slingshot
125013799.description: Battle your foes with this rapid firing slingshot!

102705454.name: Tornado Summoner
102705454.description: Summon the might of the air and unleash a wave of cyclones on anyone near you.  When these gale force winds are summoned close to foes, they're sure to be blown away!

335086410.name: Dual Spec Gamma Biograft Energy Sword
335086410.description: Dual wield version of the Spec Gamma Biograft Energy Click to slash, double click to lunge.

135949881.name: Hatched Walking with Dinosaurs Super Egg
135949881.description: Wow – you know a lot about dinosaurs!  This item was awarded to all users who answered all 4 questions in the Walking With Dinosaur quiz correctly.  When you take this in game you will be able to charge other players!  Also – don’t miss Walking with Dinosaurs – in theaters December 20th!

191261930.name: Black and White Sword
191261930.description: Click to double slash your opponents. A successful hit deals 25 damage. Beware a wielder of this sword's jump.  After jumping they will spin around leaving phantom blades that will do 10 damage per hit.

243790334.name: Golden Steampunk Gloves
243790334.description: Swing your mighty (and heavy!) gloves at your foes. Each hit does 15 damage and launches your rivals away from you with great force.

44116233.name: Megaphone
44116233.description: Yeah! Blah blah blah!  Weeoooo weeeooo! WHHHHHATT?

18479966.name: Chakram
18479966.description: Basically this is a flying ring with one very sharp edge all the way around. It hits hard, but has a long cool down time. It's best used to pick off enemies who are already damaged, or to seriously soften them up before entering melee combat.

12909278.name: Banjo
12909278.description:
I want to be a rock star, and travel really far, and buy / me a big expensive car. /
And make lots of money and find me a honey. /
And live in nice big house where it's sunny. /
With a pool and I'll be cool. /
I'll always have a gig cause I'll be big. /
I'll have parties and friends and places to go, /
The only problem is I play the banjo. - Ryan Shupe

904534702.name: Speedy Hiking Boots
904534702.description: You'll make it to the summit in no time! Hit 'Shift' to use your super speed boost!

93725362.name: Sword Of The Behemoth - a Walmart Exclusive
93725362.description: "Hark! Hark to the wind! / 'Tis the night, they say, / When all souls come back from the far away-- / The dead, forgotten this many a day!"

302502491.name: Spider Slasher
302502491.description: Click to slash double-click to lunge and do 12 damage. When you lunge, you also shoot a web in the the direction of your cursor. If it hits somebody, their speed is reduced to 6 for a few seconds, giving you an opportunity to catch up to them. While slashing your enemy with the sword, there is a 30% chance of poisoning them!

16200373.name: Color Paintbrush
16200373.description: A simple tool for changing the color of objects during Group Building

55917420.name: Knights of the Splintered Skies: Hydrian Elixir
55917420.description: Over the centuries, many have wondered how the KoSS descend upon the realm in times of peril. Only but a few know, the true source of the KoSS' power. The Hydrian Elixir grants the KoSS the ability to grow wings and fly for a short period of time. Not only does the elixir give them the ability of flight, but also increases their strength twofold and the wings attack anyone that get near them!

450565762.name: Attack Raccoon
450565762.description: Loyal as they come, but dangerous as a poison snake. He'll poison your foes as fast as you can click.

138761013.name: Sparkle Time Lump of Coal
138761013.description: We told you it was unlucky!  This item came out of the unluckiest gift on December 16th, 2013.

189756588.name: Christmas Tree Sword
189756588.description: This dangerous holiday sword may look fun, but it will be anything but for your foe. Each hit will do 34 damage and if you manage to KO your opponent they'll be wrapped up like a gift.

904534058.name: Marshmallow Shooter
904534058.description: They're not just for eating anymore. Click to fire toasty treats.

121385262.name: Zombie Dog
121385262.description: This loyal undead friend will poison any foe that gets in your way.

2222652960.name: Ornate Katana
2222652960.description: Never sacrifice form for function, go for both.

100472063.name: Sharp Looking Hat - the Gear
100472063.description: It's not just sharp looking. It's actually sharp! Throw this hat at opponents to do damage with its razor sharp edges.  Don't worry about getting it back - it magically appears back on your head after it hits something.

287426148.name: Omega Rainbow Sword
287426148.description: The power of all future rainbows is at your finger tips. Click to slash, dealing 18 to 22 damage per hit. Double click to dash forward with the speed of a magical rainbow!

754869699.name: Deluxe Pirate Hook
754869699.description: For the pirate who lives life with flair.  Click to swing this stylish pirate hook at your enemies; dealing 12 damage per hit.

78005082.name: Sci-Fi MedVac 4300
78005082.description: Heal yourself and your teammates with this Sci Fi MedVac

73232825.name: Wraith's Screech Potion
73232825.description: His scream pierces all that come near him.

121385230.name: Stinky Underwear Launcher
121385230.description: Avoid the stinky underwear at all costs!

82711870.name: Snarffle from Alien on a Rampage
82711870.description: Meet Snarffle.  One little alien (and one BIG problem) in the new book Alien on a Rampage from Clete Smith.

25977812.name: Flowersplosian
25977812.description: Experience the true meaning of flower power.

454733927.name: MonStar
454733927.description: This is advertising. And a new companion coming through like a train. Be Real? But being imaginative is so much more coolio to jam with!

178076831.name: Redcliff Crossbow
178076831.description: Fire arrows at all that would dare cross the mighty Redcliff. Each hit will do epic damage.

84417281.name: Dubstep Boombox
84417281.description: Because Dubstep is the new cool.

79446473.name: Rail Runner 5000
79446473.description: When you absolutely must put a rail through somebody.

257840933.name: Hiccup’s Trusty Shield
257840933.description: It’s saved Hiccup more than once, and he fights dragons - you know…that breathe fire. What better endorsement for a shield is there?

163350265.name: Ye Olde Fire Breath Potion
163350265.description: Guzzle this down to shoot flames out of your mouth.  What an impressive party trick!

61459718.name: The Tormentor's Axe
61459718.description: Only the very best escape the hot steel of the Tormentor's Axe!

59175777.name: Deadly Thorn Potion
59175777.description: Use the potion to grow powerful thorns all over your body.  Your enemies don't stand a chance!

176219131.name: ROBLOX U Foam Finger
176219131.description: Root, root, root for the home team!  Raise your foam finger in victory and high five other fans!

21064230.name: ROFL Waffle
21064230.description: You can't have ROFL Waffles and pancaiks for breakfast.  You have to choose.  I'm on team waffle!  This is our first gear of the week. It will go off sale on 1/29/10

1760404984.name: Teapot Launcher
1760404984.description: Have you seen my teapot collection? Here, take a closer look.

190094270.name: Ridable Raptor
190094270.description: Jump on this dino to ride it. Use the 'W' and 'S' keys to move forward and back, and use the 'A' and 'D' keys to turn left and right. Pressing space will cause the reptile to leap, and pressing left shift will dismount you from it.

511930668.name: Zoom Broom 5000
511930668.description: The fastest broom on the market, be sure to hold on tight! Equip and click and drag to fly around in the direction of your cursor.

380204314.name: Lucky Throwing Axes
380204314.description: May the luck of the Irish be with your aim. Each hit does 28 damage!

93136674.name: Uppercut Sword
93136674.description: This gigantic sword will throw your enemies into the air and let you do as much damage as you can for 5 seconds.

88885268.name: Discus 2012
88885268.description: Throw this discus far enough and you'll get an explosive reward.

93536827.name: Zombie Bomb
93536827.description: This bomb summons powerful zombies to feast on your enemies.  Occasionally it will unlease a zombie explosion that kills on contact.

2445084910.name: Ghostly Possessed Sword of Terror
2445084910.description: A ghostly sword, possessed by the souls of slain warriors, thirsty for revenge...Click to release its binding and it attacks on its own.

78367424.name: Tiger Friend
78367424.description: If a tiger is chasing you and your friend, you have only one chance at survival.  Trip your friend.

858740936.name: Robo Arm Cannon
858740936.description: Sometimes, you just need a bigger boom.

119917513.name: Instant Treehouse
119917513.description: Part of the fun of summer is hanging out 24/7.  Now you have a place to hang out wherever you go.

152824174.name: Rare Egg Cloner 2014
152824174.description: This gear item will only work in the official ROBLOX 2014 Egg Hunt- which is only open for a few more hours. This item allows you to select a rare egg (but not a faberge egg).  If someone earns that rare egg while you are playing with them, you will also get the egg.

517827255.name: Double-Bladed Scythe
517827255.description: Double your terror, double your fun. Click to attack. Anybody hit will take serious damage!

43567614.name: Santa's Grappling Gun
43567614.description: How did you think he got back *up* the chimney?

105351572.name: Skeletal Sword
105351572.description: Victory comes with a price.  Get this exclusive sword when you redeem a $25 ROBLOX card from Walmart by February 28th.

54130537.name: Seashell Snare
54130537.description: She sells seashells by the seashore.   But she doesn't mess around.  This shell is a trap that will ensnare any enemies that get too close!

37816777.name: Ghostwalker
37816777.description:
The boast of heraldry, the pomp of power, /
And all that beauty, all that wealth e'er gave, /
Awaits alike th' inevitable hour:- /
The paths of glory lead but to the grave.

37694914.name: Garlic Necklace
37694914.description: This necklace prevents Vampires from doing too much damage when they get close.  Works only in our special Halloween level -http://www.roblox.com/Halloween-CTF-Vampires-vs-Werewolves-item?id=18454366

187840979.name: Penguin Horde  Attack
187840979.description: Click to drop penguins who will attack your foes- doing 15 damage per hit.

15177716.name: Taco
15177716.description: ROBLOX is built on tacos from Chavez.  Also Pancho Villa!

154727251.name: Super Speedy Purple Potion
154727251.description: This speed potion is very nearly perfect.  Once activated your walk speed will be increased to 50.  One side effect we should mention is that you will turn temporarily purple and sparkly.  Like we said ... very nearly perfect.

127506257.name: Knights of the Splintered Skies: Wind Summoner
127506257.description: This extremely powerful horn summons a row of tornadoes that will destroy everything (and everyone) in their path!

26945832.name: Ruler
26945832.description: Because these lines can't rule themselves!

16200420.name: Material Tool
16200420.description: A tool for changing the Material of objects during Group Building

183665171.name: Neon Throwing Stars
183665171.description: Your foes will certainly see these brightly colored throwing stars coming!  Each star deals 12.5 points of damage and will stick to its target for increased intimidation.

277954704.name: RC Tiny Tank
277954704.description: Click to spawn your very own remote controlled tank!   Use 'W', 'A', 'S', and 'D' to steer it. Click to fire a blue projectile with an awesome blue fire trail as it flies toward your target. Each hit does 25 damage.

319656563.name: Dual Axe Monsters
319656563.description: These angry little monsters will follow you around and throw deadly axes at your foes!

24396804.name: CocoWHAAA?
24396804.description: You're in a rainforest and you're thirsty.  You see a coconut with what looks like a straw coming out of it.  Wait is that a straw? No. It's a fuse!  Run it's not a coconut.

68233678.name: Red Energy Sword
68233678.description: The last scientist who knew how to make energy swords passed away in a horrific energy sword accident.  Don't worry, he wasn't using his own energy swords (which function perfectly!).  He was testing a competitor's imitation sword when the energy suddenly exploded.  But this is not the end for energy swords!  They will live on.  How?  That's for another energy sword desciption.  How did we get these ones?  Duh - they were hidden in the scientist's basement.

27133214.name: Binoculray
27133214.description: Binoculrays allow you to see further than you've ever been able to before.  They're so powerful, you'll even be able to see through walls.

81154592.name: Firebrand
81154592.description: "O! for a muse of fire, that would ascend the brightest heaven of invention."

34399318.name: Cupcake Launcher
34399318.description: I personally think that most cupcakes are too delicious to be launching at people's faces, but I can understand that some people disagree.

128209615.name: Flame Ronin Katana
128209615.description: May the fires used to forge this katana protect you always.Get this exclusive item when you redeem a ROBLOX card from F.Y.E. in September.

835780770.name: Winterfang: The Fateful
835780770.description: Across the frozen tundra Winterfang ran, tracking his master's scent over a hundred miles. He would never abandon a friend in their time of need. Simply equip this item and he will spawn in front of you- ready to ride.

583157224.name: Snowflake Shield and Sword
583157224.description: Take up arms against the frozen winter wind!

621089209.name: Static Shock Sheep
621089209.description: Do androids dream of electric sheep? Equip and this robot sheep will follow by your side. Click on enemies to get him to run up to them and shock them!

327365543.name: Rocket Sled
327365543.description: A rocket powered sleigh will take you anywhere you want to go! Use the arrow keys or 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D', to control your sleigh.

103234612.name: Military Remote Control Plane
103234612.description: Now you're ready for the ultimate reconnaissance mission!

228588531.name: Staff of Eggstra Large Eggs
228588531.description: Summon a giant flaming egg from the sky which will crash down and fling your foe far from his current location.

32858662.name: Staff of Azure Ever Ice
32858662.description: Azurewrath had been held in durance deep withing the Vidre Cova for aeons. Then he escaped and, in his counterstroke, plunged the world into a new ice age.

98253569.name: Plad's ROBLOX Tablet
98253569.description: Winner: Plad. ROBLOX will be in touch to redeem this prize. Void if sold, traded, or deleted.

2316759705.name: Microscope Launcher
2316759705.description: Don’t just spread germs, fire them!

25740034.name: Sword Cane
25740034.description: At first glance you look like an innocent person who has some difficulty walking - but then, bam!  It's a sword and you're slashing left and right.

146026904.name: ROBLOX Winter Games 2014 Bronze Trophy
146026904.description:
Awarded to the lower scoring levels for earnest effort across all the
Winter Games, as indicated on the Winter Lodge Leaderboard.

91450692.name: Terratronic Health Core
91450692.description: Activate and toss this health core to form a healing circle, giving life to all within it.

10472779.name: Bloxy Cola
10472779.description: Warning: Bloxy Cola may be habit-forming.

83021217.name: Shark Launcher
83021217.description: What did you expect it to shoot?  Missiles?

126719148.name: Monster Attack
126719148.description: Grow fiery horns and charge at your foes.

20519646.name: Icicle Cannon
20519646.description: The perfect gift for super villians everywhere. This medium to long-range weapon shoots icy spikes at your enemies. The spikes explode and do splash damage. Wicked cool.

300410799.name: Evil Duck Roped
300410799.description: The most sinister roped yet!  Hit the 'H' key to make it quack!  Hit 'Q' to make it rain ducks.

13838639.name: Atomic Disintegrator 3100
13838639.description: Great for destroying those pesky humans.  On the flip side - excellent for stopping alien invaders.  Which side will you fight for?

425121415.name: School's Out Launcher
425121415.description: Schools out- time to launch all your school items at your friends! Launch an apple, book, and diploma for your friends to interact with!

187688069.name: Polar Bear Attack Claws
187688069.description: Slash at your enemies with these polar bear claws to do 15 damage. Double click to grab a player and do 40 damage.

57229357.name: Paper Sword
57229357.description: Okay - let's be real here - a paper sword does as much damage as well....paper.  But it does do some other silly stuff.

60678464.name: Metal Guitar of Awesomeness
60678464.description: You'll have all your friends dancing when you play the Metal Guitar of Awesomeness.  Get the Metal Guitar of Awesomeness for free when you purchase a ROBLOX Card at Walmart during the month of September..

49491716.name: Princess Mischief's Wand
49491716.description: Your appearance displeases me!  Wave, wave, poof!  That's much better!  Don't you think?

1708354246.name: Pinata Mount
1708354246.description: A candy-filled friend to call your own, just don’t let anyone take a swing at him.

313547087.name: Flying Vacuum
313547087.description: Brooms are so 1600s.  The modern witch definitely uses a vacuum! Click and hold to point the broom in the direction you wish to fly.

2350119937.name: Blue Rolling Hoverboard
2350119937.description: Click to spawn your very own true blue  hoverboard! Control your direction using arrow keys or the 'W', 'A', 'S', and 'D' keys. Hit Backspace to dismount.

101715440.name: Angalacon's Crossbow
101715440.description: A dragon's danger is not from his teeth alone.  Fire flaming arrows soaked in poisonous dragon venom at your foes to do 19 damage.

21001552.name: Insert Tool
21001552.description: An Insert tool for building with sets

14131296.name: Machete
14131296.description: Hack through jungles with this machete. Eversharp!

152823565.name: Egg Cannon 2014
152823565.description: This gear item will only work in the official ROBLOX 2014 Egg Hunt - which is only open for a few more hours.  This awesome Egg Cannon launches fake eggs to confuse your competitors.  Occasionally it will fire out a real egg just to keep it interesting.

41457719.name: Chocolate Gelt
41457719.description: Who knew money could be so yummy!

93536844.name: Zombie Launcher
93536844.description: Shoot powerful hungry zombies at your enemies.  Watch and laugh as they chase your foes and bite them - stealing 10hp each second.

148790984.name: Trophy of Wheeled Participation 2014
148790984.description: This trophy stands as proof that this user earned the long-jumping item (3) that was available during a 2014 event.

21416138.name: Spec Gamma Biograft Energy Sword
21416138.description: In the aftermath of World War VII, isolated pockets of human survivors raided ruined government labs, looking specifically for these weapons. The Spec X program had been accelerated in the late 2120s as the prospect of an all out metahuman vs. machine war became increasingly likely. Prized for their ability to slice through viridian steel exoskeletons, the US was determined to find a substitute for the pure diamond required for the manufacture of the Beta models. Sapphire, while still exorbitantly expensive, allowed the army to produce blades that were 95% as effective as the Betas, at only 20% the cost.

387286257.name: Bunny Laser
387286257.description: Fire a laser at your foes to turn them into an adorable bunny rabbit! Be careful with your aim as this laser can travel through other players - to hit multiple players at once!

15932306.name: Starblox Latte
15932306.description: Drinking a Starblox Latte is a great way to add a little speed to your step - but if you drink too many your head might explode.

330295904.name: Festive Laser Blaster
330295904.description: Jingle bells, jingle bells, blast them all with lasers! Fire red and green projectiles that do five damage per hit.

253518869.name: Famous Bloxstar Guitar
253518869.description: Part of the Famous Bloxstar package!

42845684.name: Dusek Car
42845684.description: The Dusek Car is faster than any other car.  Not because the car itself is super high performance...because Dusek is driving.  A shiny yellow 'vette with a special Dusek hood ornament.

143606363.name: Hot Chocolate Launcher
143606363.description: In the right hands, hot cocoa can be quite dangerous.  Shoot a stream of burning hot cocoa at your foes - if you hit them, they'll take 50 damage and their screen will be splattered with chocolatey goodness.

233657188.name: Bunny Roped
233657188.description: Why hop when you can roll?

130113146.name: Hyperlaser Gun
130113146.description: Everyone knows that blue is the fastest color laser beam. That's why it's a one hit KO.

93536785.name: Zombie Axe
93536785.description: Does 15 damage per swipe and summons some Zombies to eat your enemies brains.

1132887630.name: 8-Bit Pumpkin Launcher
1132887630.description: It's dangerous to trick or treat alone, take this! Click to lob 8-bits of bursting pumpkins at your foes.

16200199.name: Model Dragger
16200199.description: A Model Dragger for Group Building

287424278.name: Orinthian Electroslasher
287424278.description: Click to slash, dealing 16 to 20 damage. Hit the 'Q' key to spawn three Orinthian warrior minions in front of you, which will chase nearby enemies, dealing 10 damage per hit.

83704179.name: Joint Breaker
83704179.description: It does exactly what it says it does.

24791472.name: Chocolate Bunny
24791472.description: Eating this yummy chocolate bunny will give you a sugar high that makes you run at lightning fast bunny speeds.

31839411.name: Fire Extinguisher
31839411.description: This fire is out of control.  Gonna burn this city.  Burn this city.

16969792.name: Resize Tool
16969792.description: A tool for resizing parts during Group Building

1183006601.name: Porg
1183006601.description: Porgs are inquisitive creatures who flock about the rocks and roost in the cliffs of Luke Skywalker’s secluded island.

181245141.name: Monster Compass
181245141.description: Use this item in Hallow's Eve to determine which monsters are in a level and where they are.  This item only works in Hallow's Eve. Play it here - http://www.roblox.com/Hallows-Eve-2014-The-Witching-Hour-Returns-place?id=180331551

467935723.name: Robot Guard Dog
467935723.description: More loyal than Hachikō, this guy will go after anyone who gets too close. Each bite does ruffly (get it?) 22 damage and lasers do 18 damage.

553939167.name: Bloxster STB
553939167.description: Leave 'em in the sparkles and dust.

18017365.name: Crimson Katana of the Unsetting Sun
18017365.description: If not for victory and honor, then what?

90718686.name: Conjuror's Fist
90718686.description: Instantly crushes anyone and anything unfortunate enough to be below where you’ve summoned it.

18474459.name: Paint Bucket
18474459.description: U has a bucket! This is a tool of mass vandalism. Hold down the left mouse button and drag to paint everything! Of course, you *could* put it to more constructive use, especially in a Group Building place.

159199263.name: Bo Staff 7000
159199263.description: Use this futuristic Bo Staff to slash at your foes and do 15 damage.  Hit 'Q' to activate its special ability - a forcefield that instantly kills your foes.

2435999037.name: Niffler Companion
2435999037.description: The Niffler loves shiny objects, can you find them here on Roblox? Be sure to watch Fantastic Beasts: The Crimes of Grindelwald on 11.16

1016184293.name: Coffee Cruiser
1016184293.description: When you need coffee, make it come to you! Drive around using 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D', or the arrow keys. Hit 'X' to toggle the headlight and 'H' to honk. Click with your mouse to fuel up on coffee yourself so you can keep cruising!

2190016098.name: Above Top Secret Jetpack
2190016098.description: An essential gadget for every spy.

36107470.name: Halloween Paintball Gun
36107470.description: Get them while they last.  October only!

125859483.name: NY Pizza Frisbee
125859483.description: What's more fun than eating a delicious New York style pizza?  Throwing it at your friends!

11377306.name: Silver Ninja Star of the Brilliant Light
11377306.description: In a light that casts no shadow, across a barren plain that affords no shade, range swift figures in immaculate flowing robes.

105179506.name: Pyrox's Flame Staff
105179506.description: Pyrox’s flame staff burns everyone in his way. Earn this prize in the LEGO Hero Factory: Brain Attack! game - http://www.roblox.com/LEGO-Hero-Factory-Brain-Attack-place?id=88419564.

14131602.name: Pirate Hook
14131602.description: Arrr! I be hooked on this weapon!

124126871.name: Newtrat's Tuskinator
124126871.description: Tuskies are your chums, spam them on your friends, watch them stick like glue, spewing wishes all the time.

4811755352.name: The 7th Annual Bloxy Award
4811755352.description: A prestigious prize granted to winners of the Bloxy Awards, our yearly ceremony honoring the best and brightest of Roblox!

163995460.name: NobleDragon's Noble Dragon
163995460.description: If well taken care of, your Noble Dragon will follow you around and shoot flames at anyone who dares to approach you! We recommend feeding your Noble Dragon only coffee and dreams (this keeps it in prime condition!) but it's a virtual pet. Pixels are pixels!

63721724.name: Bat Blade
63721724.description: Strike your opponents with blades as sharp as a vampire bat's teeth!

13841367.name: Ninja Guitar
13841367.description: Take time out from your ninja training to rock!

94233367.name: Ghost Blaster
94233367.description: This blaster will down your foes with just one hit!  But that's not all - your foe will come back as  your ghost minion and attack other players for 30 seconds.

37694889.name: Silver Dust
37694889.description: This necklace prevents Werewolves  from doing too much damage.  Works only in our special Halloween level -http://www.roblox.com/Halloween-CTF-Vampires-vs-Werewolves-item?id=18454366

168142869.name: Death Run 2 Shoes
168142869.description: Equip to put these shoes on and increase your walk speed to 24.  Click to double your walk speed and jump super high for the next 30 seconds.

4146860828.name: D-O
4146860828.description: An eager new ally of the Resistance’s greatest heroes.

261826683.name: Minions YTO Special
261826683.description: Get ready for a yellow takeover, courtesy of the Minions. Firepower of the paint variety - good for remodeling houses or ruining new outfits.

2845941219.name: Firstblade of the Federation
