2845941219.description: It’s so beautiful, do I hang it like art or take it into battle? With this, all of creation will be yours. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy! Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

2016188435.name: Adventurous Hiker Compass
2016188435.description: Point me in the direction of adventure! Part of the Adventurous Hiker package.

517827962.name: Mr. Whiskers
517827962.description: A faithful feline friend to the end. Toss his favorite skeleton fish and he'll fetch it back.  When not fetching; he follows you around the map like a loyal pet.

3739219006.name: Golden Football
3739219006.description: Celebrate NFL’s centennial season with a 24-karat pigskin, perfect for completing your winning ensemble.

2568200796.name: Turkey Mount
2568200796.description: Just like how the pilgrims used to ride turkeys at the first Thanksgiving. I saw it in a comic book.

130925426.name: Super Tone Cape
130925426.description: It's a bird, it's a plane, it's SUPER TONE!  Use this sweet cape to fly and shoot lasers from your eyes - just like the real Tone.

10884288.name: War Rocks
10884288.description: Has anyone ever read The Lottery by Shirley Jackson? It's hugely overrated.

928914739.name: Black Iron Katana
928914739.description: Slash and lunge at your foes with this amazing katana to do 12 to 16 points of damage. The power of the blackest iron surrounds this Katana.

98253651.name: Mahem's ROBLOX Tablet
98253651.description: Winner: Mahem. ROBLOX will be in touch to redeem this prize. Void if sold, traded, or deleted.

81847533.name: Ameriboard
81847533.description: Skateboarding for freedom since 1776!  Okay maybe not quite that long...

108148479.name: Shamrockin' Guitar
108148479.description: I've never heard a more rockin' version of Mollie Malone.  Get this exclusive gear when you redeem a $25 card from Walmart in the month of March.

146026928.name: ROBLOX Winter Games 2014 Gold Trophy
146026928.description:
Awarded to the top scoring levels for the highest achievement across
all the Winter Games, as indicated on the Winter Lodge Leaderboard.

1829110586.name: Ferocious Mr. Fox
1829110586.description: The swiftest of mounts, the most cunning of steeds.

306971659.name: Skeleton Slashers
306971659.description: Click to slash, dealing between 15 to 25 damage. Double click to dash forward and double-slash, using both arms. If you can hit your opponent with this attack, they take 30 points of damage!

17407931.name: The Midas Glove
17407931.description: As seen in Ovid, Metamorphoses XI.

569676258.name: Candy Cane Bow
569676258.description: Sweet, but deadly. Click and hold to charge, let go to release and fire an arrow in the direction of your cursor. Does between 15 minimum to 100 maximum damage depending on the charge.

62809243.name: Outrageous Board with a Nail in It
62809243.description: Did they? That outrageous board with a nail in it may have defeated us. But the humans won't stop there. They'll make bigger boards and bigger nails, and soon, they will make a board with a nail so big, it will destroy them all!

33382711.name: Staff of Gloomy Grip
33382711.description: One click and a gloomy hand does your bidding. Tip - Try grabbing something with the staff and then walking!

92142799.name: Phoenix
92142799.description: Equip the Phoenix and watch as it flies around you in a defensive circle, shooting at nearby enemies (25 damage per hit) for as long as five minutes. You can even have the Phoenix target specific enemies by clicking on them.

2605965785.name: Ice Blue Rolling Hoverboard
2605965785.description: Be blue cool when you’re rolling.  Control your direction using arrow keys or the 'W', 'A', 'S', and 'D' keys while leaving snow behind you. Hit Backspace to dismount.

18462637.name: Staff of the Winds
18462637.description: Try it for free in the ROBLOX Thanksgiving Turkey Hunt! Hold down the left mouse button to unleash a huge gust of wind that will blow away enemies and loose parts alike!

19703062.name: Christmas Tree Topper
19703062.description: Throw these at a Christmas tree to top it off!  My Christmas tree has a Viking helmet as a topper, but to each his own...

1016496274.name: Jungle Explorer Boomerang
1016496274.description: Give it a toss to send foes flying.  Part of the Jungle Explorer package.

26777410.name: Pwny
26777410.description: This magical pwny lets you rise high above the rest on a spiked platform.  Left click at anytime on your magical flight to drop the spiky platform (and yourself) onto enemies.

42200852.name: Igloo of Solitude
42200852.description: It's not quite a Fortress of Solitude, but, then again, you're not quite Superman, are you?

101106419.name: Farmer's Revenge
101106419.description: Protect your farmland by charging at your enemies and send them flying.

454733534.name: Fruity Pebbles Spoon
454733534.description: This is advertising. And probably the most interesting spoon you’ll ever come across. Why? Well do any other spoons teleport you? Case closed.

286526176.name: Adurite Katana
286526176.description: Harness the heat of your rage with this adurite katana.

10831489.name: Fencing Foil
10831489.description: En garde! This sword is very quick. It does high lunging damage but very low slashing damage.

738925737.name: Horde of Attack Chirps
738925737.description: Don't let their cute eyes fool you, they're deadly. Summon a horde of chirps to your side. Click on a foe to launch a chirp attack!

501939119.name: Save the Noobs Protest Sign
501939119.description:
Apologies that the sign is blocking your view, just move over there to the left a little. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

535104095.name: Neon Ninja's Katana
535104095.description: Click to slash, dealing roughly 13 damage and double click to lunge dealing around 18 damage. Part of the Neon Ninja package!

119101643.name: Cool Story Air Conditioner
119101643.description: Remember that time 4 air conditioners fell from the sky simultaneously. Cool story, bro.

51346471.name: Twin Kodachi
51346471.description: From the Asuna Samurais comes this twin Kodachi. With its lightness and speed, the Kodachi is deadly in the hands of any true Samurai warrior. Give them two and see them cut through their opponents as if they were made of paper.

15642486.name: Protest Sign: Save the Whales
15642486.description: Some people think nuking whales is wrong... And they're not going to take it any more!

161208517.name: Summer 2014 Skateboard
161208517.description: "My whole life has been the skate life. I don't really remember doing anything besides skateboarding."

1402292509.name: Year of the Dog Lantern
1402292509.description: Happy Lunar New Year! Celebrate with your own ghostly guard dog to protect you.

113299590.name: Orbital Piano Strike
113299590.description: Play a piano that summons other flaming pianos to smite your foes! The most ridiculous instrument on ROBLOX has arrived!

22787168.name: Iris Katana of Goldengrove Unleaving
22787168.description: "Nor mouth had / no nor mind expressed / what heart heard of / ghost guessed"

116693694.name: Amerilaser Blaster
116693694.description: Blast your foes all the way back to 1776.  Looks great in places with dynamic lighting enabled!

170903216.name: Pizza Delivery Vehicle
170903216.description: Cruise around ROBLOX in your sweet pizza delivery vehicle.  Click 'X' to turn on your headlights and 'H' to honk.

346687946.name: Redcliff Rogue Sword
346687946.description: Click to slash or double-click to lunge. Part of the Redcliff Rogue package!

1046322934.name: Megagavel
1046322934.description: You're out of order! You're out of order! Everyone is out of order! Click to send people flying out of your courtroom.

36913594.name: Pumpkinade Launcher
36913594.description: Launch maniacal pumpkin bombs at your friends for fun and profit!

53130867.name: JediTkacheff's DeathStar
53130867.description:
Crafted using futuristic techniques by JediTkacheff this death star is capable of moving and blistering speeds to attack its marked target. Watch out though, as the star is also capable of conjuring a shield around its wielder to protect him from incoming projectiles and do damage to any tresspassers and boost your health.

Press "x" for conjuring the shield!

100472084.name: Agent 99's Laser Goggles
100472084.description: Your mission can only be completed with the latest laser technology.  Aim lasers at people to do massive fiery damage.

248287898.name: Club Boates Disco Ball
248287898.description: Summon your very own club and dance anywhere!

186867671.name: Sir Lancelot’s Sword
186867671.description: Do centuries amounts of damage with this sword.  Exclusively fit for a Knight of the roundtable. Check out Night at the Museum: Secret of the Tomb in theaters December 19th!

64869947.name: Ninja Sticky Bomb
64869947.description: Sticks to your enemies like a ninja! Get this item when you redeem a ROBLOX card from W.H. Smith in May.

179369752.name: Halloween Skateboard
179369752.description: Because even Ghosts want to grind.

498752334.name: Paper Ninja Stars
498752334.description: Ever had a paper cut? It's like that, but a lot worse. Click to throw in the direction of your cursor; three fly, twirling toward their target. The further they move away from you, the more they spread apart. Upon striking an opponent, they stick and deal 15 damage each.

119917531.name: Tennis Racket
119917531.description: Cause a ruckus with this racket!

89390416.name: Arachnix Drone
89390416.description: Black Phantom's drone is all kinds of trouble. This little spider-like drone multiplies itself and attacks your enemies. Play the Lego® Hero Factory game on ROBLOX to win this prize!  http://www.roblox.com/LEGO-Hero-Factory-Breakout-place?id=32373412

313547345.name: Halloween Throwing Stars
313547345.description: Who says throwing stars have to look like stars?  Throw all three of these Halloween themed blades at once to do triple damage!

1060282245.name: Forest Bow and Arrow
1060282245.description: These bows, often given as gifts by forest elves, can be used by anyone regardless of skill with a bow. Click to shoot and leave a flurry of leaves in your arrow's wake.

164369961.name: Magic Beach Towel
164369961.description: Like a magic carpet, but you know, a beach towel!  Hop on your magic towel and fly all over ROBLOX!

718245473.name: TechnoWizard Staff
718245473.description: He who controls the wires controls the world. Click and hold to cast deadly lightning at your enemies! The longer you maintain the lightning on your enemies; the more damage it deals to them! Medium length range. Part of the TechnoWizard package.

527383094.name: Sir Scaresalot
527383094.description: A good knight always carries on until the job is done. Equip to spawn this loyal ghost knight by your side. He'll attack at your command.

106701619.name: Wizards of the Astral Isles: Frog Transformer
106701619.description: Transform those around you into frogs. They'll be forced to hop around and drop all of their weapons!

3798370428.name: Ren the Red Fox Ranger Bow

820013867.name: Bloxster PRL
820013867.description: Where speed meets elegance, the Bloxster is a most sophisticated ride on two wheels.

1536052210.name: Gem Egg Claymore
1536052210.description: Passed down through the eons, this mighty sword was wielded by the bravest warriors of Egg Hunts past.

28277195.name: Eight Bit Marvel
28277195.description: Who knew eight bits could do so much!

61459678.name: Ne'Kotikoz Phaser
61459678.description: The Ne'Kotikoz will ask you to move politely, then they'll pull out the Phasers.  Trust me, you don't want them to pull out the Phasers.

67747912.name: Heat Seeking Missile Launcher
67747912.description: Lock on to the enemy and fire for a one hit knock out.  4 second reload time.

120749494.name: Bald Eagle
120749494.description: America's proud symbol flies above you and protects you with the very latest Amerilaser defense... or offense depending on how you look at it.

250407413.name: Ezra’s Trusty Lightsaber
250407413.description: Scientists don’t get how Lightsabers work, but what is there to get? It’s a laser sword. You go fight other people with laser swords. Simple stuff!

85879435.name: EMP Shockmine
85879435.description: Shock the gear out of your opponents hands.

202039834.name: Puss in Boots' Sword
202039834.description: Puss’ devastating “kitty stare” is off the table, but how’s his sword as a stand-in? Watch The Adventures of Puss In Boots, only on Netflix Jan. 16

120749452.name: American Rockets 1776
120749452.description: These fireworks have been bringing light to destroy darkness since 1776.

180298414.name: Bat Burglar
180298414.description: Equip this item to summon your bat.  Click on a player with an equipped tool and your trained bat burglar will chase the player and attempt to take the item back to you. Your trained bat burglar can be hurt on the job, if killed during a heist, you will not receive the item he has taken.

27860496.name: Nova Wand
27860496.description: It's super!  Super Nova... get it? Supernova?  That's why they don't let me write the jokes.

2906731998.name: Video Star Pizza Launcher
2906731998.description: What's better than having your pizza delivered?  Having your favorite YouTuber launch it at you with a special prize.

148791414.name: Pi RAIG Table
148791414.description: It's like (╯°□°)╯︵ ┻━┻ but with more π.  Also more damage. Also more actual pies. Okay virtual pies.

11419319.name: Healing Potion
11419319.description: This is pretty much the best healing potion in any videogame ever. One use per spawn.

35366155.name: Hypnocannon
35366155.description: You're getting very sleepy!  And slow!  You're in control with the hypnocannon!

928807470.name: Blue Fidget Spinner
928807470.description: True blue, too cool. The fidget spinner will spin when you click on it and each time you click on it, the faster it will spin.

413199938.name: Bad Luck Sword
413199938.description: Bad luck for your enemies - good luck for you!  Strike at your foes with this bad luck sword and in addition to regular damage your foe has a 10% chance of being poisoned with one of four different poisons.

286527303.name: Midnight Motor Madness Scooter
286527303.description: It's a party on a bike...that delivers tacos! Ride around using 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D', or the arrow keys. Hit 'X' to toggle the headlight and 'H' to honk. Click with your mouse to grab a taco from the crate on the back of the vehicle and eat it.

40892405.name: Yamernade
40892405.description: I've always been more of a mashed potatoes girl myself.

531702150.name: Virtual Book – Harry Potter
531702150.description: Start your adventure today with Harry Potter!

22152211.name: Happy New Year Lantern
22152211.description: Celebrate the Year of the Tiger with a beautiful red lantern.

30392263.name: Decoy Deploy
30392263.description: Makes a copy of the best thing ever - you!

152233381.name: Sleepy Song Bird
152233381.description: What a sweet song.... zzzzz.  How can anyone stay awake when they hear this sweet music?  They can't!

172249239.name: Balloon Tank
172249239.description: This tank looks silly, but is capable of doing some serious damage.  To move the tank hold the W or S key while moving your mouse in the direction you would like it to follow. When you click, the tank fires balloons which are random colors. If a player is hit by a balloon, they are dealt 25 damage. There is a 1.5 second reload time.

99119240.name: Crimson Periastron Mu
99119240.description: This sword is meant to fight angry narwhals... in space.

928805891.name: Golden Rolling Hoverboard
928805891.description: Nothing says sophistication like solid gold. Control your direction using arrow keys or the 'W', 'A', 'S', and 'D' keys. Hit Backspace to dismount.

1402446243.name: Golden Dreams Convertible
1402446243.description: Some people dream in black in white... others dream in gold.

15973049.name: Protest Sign: We Want User GUIs Now!
15973049.description: User GUIs will revolutionize ROBLOX and we don't want to wait another single day before we can play with them. If you don't agree, we will beat you into submission with rational pro/con discussions, so you might as well give us what we want right now.

243790517.name: Homemade Jet pack
243790517.description: Harness the power of steam to send you soaring through the skies of ROBLOX.

25317304.name: Sheriff Steve's Six Shooter
25317304.description: Sheriff Steve's Six-Shooter makes catching outlaws a breeze!

183665698.name: Orbital Violin Strike
183665698.description: Play a violin that summons other flaming violins to smite your foes! The most ridiculous weapon on ROBLOX has arrived!  Any player you hit is dealt 15 damage per limb.

148791460.name: Pi Transmorpher
148791460.description: I'm about to bake a pi for Pi Month (3/14).  Surprise- you're the pie! Morph all your foes into pies for fun.

157205837.name: Steamgun
157205837.description: This powerful steamgun emits... you guessed it... steam!  Shoot a stream of steam at your foes to do damage.

445150567.name: Lincoln's Golden Rail Splitter
445150567.description: Split any brick into dozens of pieces!  May or may not actually split bricks.

1748602670.name: Millennium Falcon
1748602670.description: Explore the realms of Roblox with Han Solo’s ship! Be sure to watch Solo: A Star Wars Story, in theaters May 25!

1665509807.name: Prismaboard
1665509807.description: Shred through city streets on this purple prisma plank. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy! Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

122278316.name: Attack Honey Badger
122278316.description: Honey Badger don't care.  Your honey badger friend will attack the foes you click on.  Then he'll return to faithfully follow you around.

114552541.name: Fundroid Blaster
114552541.description: Part of the Fundroid package - a GameStop exclusive - http://www.roblox.com/Fundroid-item?id=114552623

718259118.name: Speedy Cleats
718259118.description: Nice to CLEAT you! Equip this gear to double your speed!

161219985.name: The United Staff of America
161219985.description: Eagles screech in the distance.  They see your foe and heed their patriotic calling - they attack all who oppose the owner of the United Staff of America. They swoop them up and drop them in the distance - doing 20 damage per drop.

236441643.name: Earth Protection Orb
236441643.description: Heal the world!  In ROBLOX - world heals you!  Well...it at least protects you!  This Earth orbits around you and shields you from nearby foes. Anyone who dares approach you will feel the burning wrath of core magma!

439988813.name: Attack Ocelot
439988813.description: "I've never seen an ocelot!" This ocelot companion follows you around and chases after enemies.

95951291.name: Skeleton King's Sword
95951291.description: This sword features three unique swings and a spin move (tap “W” twice and left-click), each of which has a 20% chance of cracking an enemy’s joints. As if that wasn’t enough, each attack has a 22% chance of being critical (2.25x damage). Normal attacks do 25 damage, landing critical attacks at about 56. Bone has never been so dangerous.

1145080014.name: Heedless Horse
1145080014.description:
Ride this fiery steed. Yeah, steed means horse. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

2014805757.name: Glorious Eagle Mount
2014805757.description: Fly like an eagle, with ultimate freedom.

19643249.name: Silver Snowflake
19643249.description: This festive holiday decoration is actually a razor-sharp steel throwing star. Perfectly camoflaged for ninja holiday parties.

64160547.name: Ghost Hoverboard
64160547.description: Finally- the future I was promised is here!  Hoverboards!  Because ghosts are too cool to skateboard.

999866081.name: Scrooge McDuck
999866081.description: The most adventurous, and richest, duck in the world! Scrooge McDuck is back and hungry for more treasure!

65545955.name: Dance Grenade
65545955.description: The roof, the roof, the roof is on fire!  The roof is on fire because you just set off this awesome dance grenade!

16987194.name: Cursed Mummy Friend
16987194.description: He's normal just like you and me. Except for that whole mummy curse thing. That's whack.

108875151.name: Golden Katana of Destiny
108875151.description: Do you fulfill the sword's golden destiny or does it help you fulfill yours?

101078524.name: The Overseer's Bow
101078524.description: Overseer bow - Powerful ranged weapon of the overseers that does 35 damage per hit and 100 damage upon headshot. Also has the ability to rapidly fire projectiles on all directions poisoning your enemies doing upto 70 damage to them over 4 seconds.

204095724.name: Monster Fierce Basher
204095724.description: This aweseome bashing stick has a ton of ways for you to bring the pain to your foes.  If your enemies touch the stick they will take 5-8 damage. If hit by a swing they can expect 10-15 damage. Double click to do 20-25 damage or click and hold to super charge your swing and do 25-40 points of damage.

2568114215.name: Blinged Gold Motorcycle
2568114215.description: Ride this bike your way. And with style.

126704033.name: Chupacabra
126704033.description: You've captured the mystical chupacabra and now he does your bidding.   He still disappears on occasion, but when you click, he will attack your foes.  If you click another character, the chupacabra will attack it until it dies.

66416579.name: Spec Zeta Biograft Energy Sword
66416579.description: After the tremendous success of the Epsilon sword, only one person was left who understood how to make energy swords.  This is largely due to the scientists testing the swords on one another in an effort to create the best product possible (and to keep all the profit for themselves).  The last scientist left standing created only 200 of these before he was spawn killed by a noob holding his own sword.

44115926.name: Magical Umbrella
44115926.description: Float away with this magical umbrella.  Click to do a twirling trick. Jump while moving to go farther. Click a lot to make it float away! (does not make the player fly)

149222485.name: My Big Fat Zombie Goldfish: The Seaquel
149222485.description: Prepare to be zombie-fied! Start reading MY BIG FAT ZOMBIE GOLDFISH: THE SEAQUEL now!

183355732.name: Deluxe Vine Staff
183355732.description: Call forth a circle of vines from the earth.  If your foes hit them they will do 20 damage.

22788134.name: Elven Blade of Glory
22788134.description: Rumored to bring glory to all who fight with it, the Elven Blade of Glory assures you a victory against even the toughest of opponents.

1645052196.name: Ancient Eagle Mount
1645052196.description: Fly like an eagle, to the sea or anywhere else.

398122724.name: Hawkeye’s Bow and Arrow
398122724.description: Can’t get within reach of your opponent? No problem! Use your bow and arrow to reach every single one of them from a distance.

108899214.name: Nerf Shoes
108899214.description: Wear these cool Nerf shoes around ROBLOX.  While you’re at it be sure to check out the Nerf Double Your Blasting Target Challenge here - http://www.roblox.com/NERF-Double-Your-Blasting-Target-Challenge-place?id=157382.

130113061.name: Hyperbike
130113061.description: Solar powered awesome motorbike.  Travel at hyperspeed and leave a trail of burning light behind you.

31314931.name: Epicsauce
31314931.description: Ultimate EPIC Juice Brand Epicsauce. Extremely hot.

264989911.name: Independence Day Fireworks 2015
264989911.description: Click to launch the firework from your hand. It'll spark then ignite with flames on the bottom as it flies up into the sky.

81155006.name: A More Elegant Blade
81155006.description: From a time twice as civilized...

91360081.name: Psychokinesis Glove
91360081.description: Move things with your mind...no problem. Okay you're actually moving it with the glove, but no one else has to know that.  Picks up near by players and rocks and hurls them to the ground.

122278207.name: Punk Wrist Cuff
122278207.description: This extreme wrist cuff instantly transforms you to a tough guy with a cool mohawk and sweet rock moves... mostly head banging.

96501417.name: Autumn Oak Staff - A Walmart Exclusive
96501417.description: Summon vines that will wrap your enemies in trouble!

161230469.name: Watermelon Launcher
161230469.description: Click to launch ripe summer watermelons at your foes!  If hit, your target will take 15 damage and have a screen covered in Watermelon splatters!

223800426.name: Korblox Lord of Death Sword
223800426.description: Part of the Lord of Death package.  This sword does 20 - 25 damage per hit. Hit the 'Q' key and hold to throw the sword out in front of you and spin it, dealing serious damage to anyone that runs in its path. If killed by this sword, your enemy turns into ghosts, and fly up into the sky.

698862470.name: Big Bug Net
698862470.description: Is someone BUGGING you? Well tell them to buzz off! Swing the net at your enemies, either stunning them in their place temporarily, or literally- catch them inside the net! Enemies will literally shrink and appear in the net for a short while unable to do anything!

97885572.name: Emergency Rations
97885572.description: Increases your max health by 100 points.

241542047.name: Golden Staff of Bling Squared
241542047.description: Part of the Golden Suit of Bling Squared package.

88143060.name: Troll Pet
88143060.description: Use to annoy your friends and enemies alike.

223132588.name: Track Builder Spiral Stack Up™
223132588.description: How will you stack the track? Get the Hot Wheels® Track Builder Spiral Stack Up™ starter set today!

204095612.name: Bejeweled Sword of Great Fury
204095612.description: Do you see red or blue?  This fierce sword lets you switch between Ruby and Sapphire attacks.  In Ruby mode you deal 40 damage per hit, but take 15 damage yourself. In Sapphire mode you do 15 damage per hit, but can strike at a great speed, and heal yourself with each hit you land.

121946387.name: Bombo's Survival Knife
121946387.description: There's only one way out- and you can bet Bombo's gonna find it!

639343572.name: Plunger Bow and Arrow
639343572.description: I shot a plunger into the air, it fell to earth I know not where. Fire plungers at your enemies- because they are nasty! Upon impact, they'll stick to your opponent for a short amount of time.

87361995.name: Chaos Master's Wing Slasher
87361995.description: Man may not fly in your presence.  Any person with wings will have them slashed by this sword and fall to their peril.  As for your enemies on the ground, they'll have a tough time escaping this swords speedy 24 damage hit.

146047188.name: Presidential Vampire Slaying Ax
146047188.description: It's what the founding father's would want you to slay vampires with.

264991177.name: American Monster Blade
264991177.description: "Chasin' this American Dream / We sweat for a nickel and a dime / Turn it into an empire" Click to slash and do 20 damage per hit.  The special does much more than that...

1320966824.name: Dragon Companion
1320966824.description: The smallest dragons often work as scouts or traveling companions throughout the misty forests of the far north. This friend will follow you faithfully though any adventure.

268533852.name: Magical Unicorn
268533852.description:
"Always, I wanna be with you / And make believe with you / And live in harmony" Fly your very own unicorn through the skies of ROBLOX.  An awesome rainbow trail marks where you've been. 
Use the 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D' or the arrow keys to control your magical friend.

1191143111.name: Battle Elk Mount
1191143111.description: This fearsome friend is bred for intense loyalty and unshakable courage in battle. He is also bred to love bread!

24814192.name: Egg Basket
24814192.description: Provides a handy in-game inventory with hints to help you successfully complete the ROBLOX 2012 Egg Hunt. Users get this item for free when they purchase Builders Club.

743691009.name: Blue LAZER Sword
743691009.description:
Just holding this makes you way more awesome. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

33867016.name: Hand Cannon
33867016.description: The Hand Cannon was recently discovered in a deep sea dive to recover artifacts from Blackbeard’s sunken pirate ship. It is rumored only Blackbeard himself was able to wield this mighty weapon.

549914420.name: Razor Sharp Looks
549914420.description: If looking good was a crime, you'd be deadly. Also the blades help.  Click to throw in the direction of your cursor. Blades will pop out of the sides of the fedora and spin toward its target.

1402452608.name: Tiny Elephant
1402452608.description: His mom thought it would be hilarious to name him Tiny.  She wasn't wrong.

987030948.name: Top Secret Briefcase
987030948.description: What's in here? Documents. Not pictures of cats. Don't be silly. Click to throw top secret cat pictures at your foes.

106701659.name: Wizards of the Astral Isles: Pegasus
106701659.description: Soar above ROBLOXIA on your very own Pegasus.

395205954.name: Korblox Ice Dragon
395205954.description: The Korblox have magically summoned the ice dragons of yore and tamed them for your transportation convenience!  Control using 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D', or the arrow keys.

48159648.name: Pirate Lieutenant's Cutlass
48159648.description: A mighty sword she be.  Only the mightiest of men might hope to wield her gracefully.

183441634.name: Mega Bloks ® Hot Wheels ™ Truck
183441634.description: Get ready for some smash & crash action with the Mega Bloks® Hot Wheels™ Baja Bone Shaker Monster Truck. Get it now!

110892267.name: Fallen Artemis Bow
110892267.description: No artifice, just fallen Artemis. Use this item to soar above the crowd and shoot arrows in 1 of 2 modes. The first mode allows for a concentrated strong shot and the other allows for rapid fire.

123234510.name: Instant Campfire
123234510.description: Pull up a log and roast a hot dog!

365642352.name: Cobalt Multiblaster
365642352.description: Rapid-fire five neon blue lasers at once!

67319425.name: The Merry Avenger
67319425.description: His vengeance is swift and just..... and merry!

315574690.name: Party Executive Briefcase
315574690.description: Part of the party executive package!

845518976.name: Scuba Gear Starfish
845518976.description: You meet the friendliest people in the ocean. Click to throw at your target to obscure their vision. Part of the Scuba Pro package.

16722267.name: Moneybag
16722267.description: Rich people like to carry these around and shake them, leaving a trail of money behind them.

2136443074.name: Cy the Cyborg - Gun
2136443074.description: In the future, man's best friend...is machine.

193771176.name: Rockin' Pink Guitar
193771176.description: Rock on! Use the keys 'Z', 'X', 'C', 'V', 'B', 'N', 'M', to play different chords. You can play sharp version of the notes by holding shift. You can alter the pitch as well with the keys 'G', 'H', 'J', 'K', 'L'.

501941714.name: Kernel Panic Katana (1x1x1x1's)
501941714.description:
Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out www.roblox.com/toys to learn more...

1215515248.name: Frozen Throwing Knives
1215515248.description: Sometimes in a tight situation you have to improvise. Click to launch a knife at your foes. Does up to 22.5 damage per hit.

746687364.name: Mega Mallet
746687364.description: Get ready to lower the BOOM! Click to swing at enemies; dealing anywhere from 20 to 30 damage. Double click to slam the mallet against the ground - dealing 80 damage to anybody hit.

110704033.name: Badblox Hatchling - Hatched Egg of Duty
110704033.description: Badblox Hatchling came out of the Egg of Duty from the 2013 Egg Hunt.

728207067.name: Bouquet of Pain Throwing Stars
728207067.description: The only thing more painful than spring allergies: flower shaped throwing stars.

277963405.name: Lt. Maverick Scout Jetpack
277963405.description: Part of the Lt. Maverick Scout package.

150927798.name: The Kingdom of Wrenly: The Lost Stone
150927798.description: Welcome to The Kingdom of Wrenly book series! Join Prince Lucas and Clara as they meet dragons, trolls, faries, and wizards on their search for the Queen's lost emerald.

2535472650.name: The Great Sword Justice
2535472650.description: “The moral arc of the universe is long, but it bends toward justice.” Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy! Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

28277486.name: Black Hole Bomb
28277486.description: Instead of blowing everything apart, it pulls everything together. The consequences are pretty.

1084980039.name: Hognob
1084980039.description: Like a dog, except a hog! This faithful companion is ready to join you in all your adventures no matter where (or when) they are!

454734258.name: Floating Thingumajig
454734258.description: A truly revolutionary device that follows you no matter where you or your imagination wanders.

317593132.name: Big Stick
317593132.description: "Speak softly and carry a big stick..." Bash your foes with this oversized wooden club, dealing massive damage! Click to swing, dealing 15 to 22 damage, 30 if you're lucky.

37347098.name: Witch Wand
37347098.description: She turned me into a newt, she did!

515688387.name: Nerf Zombie Horde Companion
515688387.description: This is advertising. Zombies, zombies, and zombies. OH MY!

186867645.name: Tablet of Akmenrah
186867645.description: Use the magic of the Pharaoh’s Tablet to power up your player.  Don’t miss Night at the Museum: Secret of the Tomb in theaters December 19th!

11885154.name: Rolling Pin
11885154.description: Your grandma uses this to make pies.  What will you use it for?

65469882.name: Fist of Schoolage - Level Up Exclusive
65469882.description: Angie uses the Fist of Schoolage to school noobs!

99797381.name: Sword of Fiery Justice
99797381.description: Use this sword for regular slash damage or send out fiery justice one flaming ball at a time.

2544539559.name: Inugami: Ninja Warrior
2544539559.description: Ninja dogs stay hidden in the barkness. This faithful friend follows your every step, remaining in your shadow, waiting for the right moment to strike...

233660801.name: Merely's Hover Surfboard
233660801.description: It's spring break, and the surf is up!  "But wait," you say, "I'm not near the ocean." With Merely's Hover Surfboard, no ocean, no problem!  Hover along on your delightful hover surfboard - wherever you are in the world! We know you have many choices when you hover, but when you want the best, make it a Merely! Don't seranok it until you've tried it!

10469910.name: Orc Blade
10469910.description: Rusty yet effective sword for primitive humanoids. Has only a basic slashing attack, but does increased damage.

47871597.name: Attrition Blade
47871597.description: Your enemies won't last long with this blade on your side.

391005275.name: Ticket Launcher
391005275.description: Make it rain tickets! Each ticket trips enemies and slows them down for 5 seconds.

62827106.name: Death's Trident: A Walmart Exclusive Item
62827106.description: Charge your enemies with a weapon that's sure to be a hit.  A deadly hit.

185422758.name: KRE-O Grimlock
185422758.description: Need a trusty dinosaur sidekick? Look no further! Get your KRE-O Transformers Grimlock today!

70032387.name: Catapult
70032387.description: Launching projectiles the old fashion way.

2163549594.name: Adurite Skateboard
2163549594.description: Only the rarest, strongest material can withstand your trashing.

336371164.name: Retro Shrink Ray
336371164.description: This shrink ray will make your foes smaller and smaller with each hit!

41856126.name: Santa's Big Bag O' Toys
41856126.description: "He's got a sleighfull, / that's not gonna stay-full / He's got stuff to drop at every stop on the way / Everybody's waitin' for the man with the bag, / 'Cause christmas is comin' again. "

305943571.name: Nerf Zombie Friend
305943571.description: This is advertising. Brains….brains.. This little guy would follow you anywhere. Anywhere that has brains that is…

34870758.name: Wormhole Tunneler
34870758.description: Is the speed of light too slow for you? With Wormhole Tunneler there is no galactic speed limit! Create two tunnels to travel between two places instantly. Beware though, as any Robloxian can use these inter-dimensional superhighways.

13477890.name: Pirate Juice
13477890.description: Taking a pirate's juice cup is the surest way to get a sword through yer belly!

119917487.name: Human Rocket
119917487.description: To the moon and back!  Send yourself (or any nearby ROBLOX player) into the sky and then parachute back down.

65969749.name: Deluxe Pumpkin Pie
65969749.description: Pumpkin pie to the face!  Take that noob!

98253626.name: Vilicus' ROBLOX Tablet
98253626.description: Winner: Vilicus. ROBLOX will be in touch to redeem this prize. Void if sold, traded, or deleted.

346687565.name: Blue Speedster
346687565.description: Drive this road-ready, raceable speedster with  'W', 'A', 'S', 'D', or the arrow keys.

382837862.name: Opened Basket of Musical Domination
382837862.description: Get Rex! Inside you find... Musica Rex Dominator.

16435306.name: Protest: More Gear Nao
16435306.description: What do we want? More Gear! When do we want it? NAO!

26014536.name: Red Rebels Paintball Gun
26014536.description: We're going to paint the town red!  Literally...

116055112.name: Ogre Friend
116055112.description: Friend or foe?  You be the judge!

46360870.name: Ice Axe
46360870.description: Defend the igloos at any price!

118281609.name: Squid Ink Bomb
118281609.description: Your enemies won't be able to see clearly!  Literally! This rapid firing squid throws ink balls at your foes and fills their screen up with ink splats.

2463674178.name: Baby Nessie Mount
2463674178.description: You’re a long way from your loch, friend.

1536053426.name: Hard Boiled Roadster
1536053426.description: Hop into this egg-shaped car and speed down the bunny trail!

439315202.name: Trophy of Participation 2016
439315202.description: This trophy stands as proof that this user earned the old school (think stone age) item that was available during a 2016 event.

1046323916.name: Motherboard Sword
1046323916.description: Send them crying for their mother(boards) faster than you can say nanoprocesser.

170897263.name: Mad Murderer Knife
170897263.description: Stab your enemies to instantly blox them. U mad bro? Yep.

304720496.name: Zombie Crossbow
304720496.description: Click to fire an arrow, dealing 15 damage each. There is a 20% chance of poisoning your enemy, which does a about 15 more damage over a 4 second period, while slowing you down while it takes its effect.

50937815.name: Atmoblaster 777
50937815.description: Send your enemies flying with an invisible blast of air!

139577956.name: Festive Roped
139577956.description: Your mom would probably prefer that you not rock around the Christmas tree on this thing.

67755192.name: Santa's Sleigh
67755192.description: Soar above the sky in Santa's magical flying sleigh.  Try not to drop too many presents accidentally!

283755431.name: Dueling Piano
283755431.description: One simple click will send this piano crashing down from the sky and onto your target.  They'll get crushed and be unable to move while you play them a little tune.  Is it a duel if only one of you has a piano? Only one way to find out.

55642223.name: 7-Eleven Slurpee
55642223.description: Get this 7-Eleven Slurpee for free when you redeem a 7-Eleven ROBLOX Card in the month of July!

45177979.name: Sledge Hammer
45177979.description: If I had a hammer / I'd hammer in the morning / I'd hammer in the evening / All over this land

58574416.name: Wild West Sarsaparilla
58574416.description: This here sarsaparilla will make you the fastest draw in the West!

98970218.name: simoon68's ROBLOX Tablet
98970218.description: Winner: simoon68. ROBLOX will be in touch to redeem this prize. Void if sold, traded, or deleted.

236401511.name: Flock of Attack Seagulls
236401511.description: Summoning this flock of attack seagulls will have your enemies running, running so far away, running all night and day.  Click on enemies for them to swoop down and bite at them! They do 5 damage per hit.

139574344.name: Frost Guard General's Sword
139574344.description: Part of the Frost Guard General package.

113328094.name: Lightblox Jar
113328094.description: Open the jar to light up the night!  This jar of bloxy firelight looks great in places with dynamic lighting.

82358339.name: Police Badge
82358339.description: It's a tough job but someone has to do it.

503957703.name: Deluxe Slime Ray
503957703.description: He slimed me! A rapid fire slime gun; can fire quickly with a short reload time. Shoot projectiles of slime at your opponents which do 8 damage upon striking them and obscure their screen in slime temporarily!

57902859.name: Ice Cream
57902859.description: I scream, you scream, we all scream for ice cream!

1856117810.name: Game Dev Mug
1856117810.description:
It’s good for water, coffee, tea, and telling everyone you’re living Game Dev Life. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

47871615.name: Guitarmy
47871615.description: Blow away your enemies with this heavy sound!  Also - cannonballs.

130112971.name: Trilaser Bow
130112971.description: Arrows are so last decade.  Charge and blast powerful lasers from  your bow.  No need for quivers... no need for arrows!

387285940.name: Bunny Moto
387285940.description: Gotta go fast like a bunny! Control using 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D', or arrow keys. Hit space to leap up (like a bunny) with this motorcycle.

172922089.name: Bronze Bloxxer
172922089.description: Bloxxing never looked so good. This item will be awarded to the top 25,000 competitors in the 2014 Clan Battle Arenas.

236440696.name: Burger Launcher
236440696.description: Fire deadly burgers and fries at your foes!  They'll take some serious burger damage (25 points per hit) and massive fry devastation (35 damage per hit)!

262406180.name: Magnificent Lion
262406180.description: You've befriended the king of beasts, and now you two will ride together. Hop on and control using 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D' or the arrow keys. Hit space to jump. Shift to charge; ctrl to dismount.

123234545.name: Camping Lantern
123234545.description: Reading in your tent....brought to you by lanterns.  Dynamically lit lanterns.

3130875522.name: Godzilla Companion
3130875522.description: No matter what you’re battling, the King of the Monsters is more than equal to the challenge. This exclusive item is from the film Godzilla: King of the Monsters - in theaters May 31, 2019.

743687369.name: Green LAZER Hammer
743687369.description:
Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out www.roblox.com/toys to learn more...

84419543.name: Nuclear Arms
84419543.description: Like nuclear arms? Well now you can have nuclear arms on your... arms.

225921724.name: Celtic Throwing Stars
225921724.description: Small enough to hide in a leprechaun's pocket, deadly enough to belong in an assassin's.

65469817.name: Thunder Pole - Level Up Exclusive
65469817.description: Lyle's weapon of choice!  Use it to cast epic spells!

48395736.name: Knight's Elder Blade
48395736.description: It is said that the Knights, once wielded blades that grew stronger as an enemy’s morale weakens. Time to test your knighthood!

34901961.name: Gravity Gun
34901961.description: Try out the new gravity gun and make the Spacetime fabric look like your grandma’s knitted sweaters. Aim this at an object to levitate it for a short amount of time.

33866846.name: Gravitational Radiation Hammer v0.01
33866846.description: Utilizing the latest in subspace/molecular deformation technology for mining on the planet Ysteb, the Gravity Hammer will expel objects surrounding its user in an outward vector. Warning: currently the Gravity Hammer does not work on objects that contain anchoritium.

90718618.name: Anti-Ballistics Force Field
90718618.description: This force field deflects most projectiles launched at you and sends them sailing back at your opponents. What’s more, the reflected projectiles do an additional 50 damage points.

40493590.name: Cherry Pie
40493590.description: Hand over the pie and no one gets hurt.

62803173.name: Jack O' Splosion
62803173.description: Oh someone left a jack o lantern for me.... how nice! Oh wait, why is it smoking?  Now that you mention it, his expression is a little menacing.... BOOM! Rut Roh.

164174293.name: Protest Sign: Explode the Fireworks
164174293.description: Blow them all up! Light up the night!

608818868.name: Eveningstar: Bringer of Dusk
608818868.description: Legend tells of a cursed mace appearing in conflicts from time immemorial. A terrible darkness radiates from it as whispers swarm your mind.

92628079.name: Orinthian Sword and Shield
92628079.description: Slash enemies with your futuristic sword or stop them dead in their tracks with a shield bash!  Activate the shield bash stun with a right click to stun enemies for 2 seconds.  When enemies are stunned, you can do extra damage!

1377984056.name: Bloxal the Barbarian's Blade
1377984056.description: Are you brave enough to dare to lift the blade of Bloxal? Part of the Bloxal the Barbarian package.

182273799.name: Rotten Pumpkin Toss
182273799.description: Click this item to drop this stinky pumpkin.  Anyone who comes near it is overpowered by it's horrifying stench and falls over - unable to move until the smell has disappeared.

178077177.name: Overseer's Steed
178077177.description: Ride your trusty steed into the sky using the WASD keys to soar over ROBLOX.

170896571.name: Red Hyperbike
170896571.description: Everyone knows red is always faster than blue.  Goes 10 faster than the original hyperbike.

156467926.name: Knights of the Splintered Skies: Sword
156467926.description: Strike at your foes and in addition to doing damage you will push them to the ground.

22158176.name: Pickaxe
22158176.description: Prospecting for gold has never been easier with handy pickaxe! Or breaking apart just about anything!

193705415.name: Snow Shredder's Board
193705415.description: Part of the Snow Shredder's Package.

34223662.name: ROBLOX Birthday Cake 2010
34223662.description: Celebrate our birthday with this delicious birthday cake gear!

1258015943.name: 2018 Noisemaker
1258015943.description: The louder your new year, the better your year will be. That's just science.

2290921705.name: Harvest Wizard's Staff
2290921705.description: Part of the Harvest Wizard package.

375832969.name: Hiro the Hero Dual Swords
375832969.description: Part of the Hiro the Hero package. A set of dual swords.Click to equip. Double click to dash on green fire while double slashing in front of you. Slashing does 14 to 18 damage; double slashing does 18 to 26 damage.

33683368.name: Bugle
33683368.description:
He was a famous trumpet man from out Chicago way / He had a boogie style that no one else could play / He was the top man at his craft, but then his number came up and he was gone with the draft / He's in the army now / He's blowin' reveille /
He's the boogie woogie bugle boy of company B

150363993.name: Spring Sunshine
150363993.description: You're just all sunshine and flowers!  Literally!  Bring the sun and have flowers grow everywhere you go.

639345143.name: Galactic Green Blaster
639345143.description: When they say eat your greens, they didn't mean lasers! Fire multi-colored laser beams of different shades of green at your enemies! Offers a medium range while also dealing roughly 20 damage per hit.

63253718.name: Bone Crusher - Mace and Shield
63253718.description: From crushing joints, to running faster to being stronger to spinning like a tornado, this one has got it all. Use "q" to bring out the shield to protect you from projectiles and tap "w" twice and left click to spin like a blistering hurricane!

73799243.name: Magma Dismantler
73799243.description: Red hot vengeance - straight from the Earth's core.

26419811.name: BANG!
26419811.description: Does no damage, but that's not really the point is it?

32355966.name: Winsome Wizard Wand
32355966.description: One blast from this wand will blow your enemies away!

233520257.name: Joyful Periastron Epsilon
233520257.description: The sword men use to hunt colorful eggs... in space.

69209924.name: R80 Launcher - A Walmart Exclusive!
69209924.description: Launch powerful explosives for fun and profit!

47262951.name: Bo Staff
47262951.description: Unleash the flaming fury within with this spinning bo staff.  The final blow has an extra firey kick!

58364871.name: ROBLOX Rally Award 2011
58364871.description: These went out to some of the best game developers on ROBLOX.  Awarded at the ROBLOX Rally 2011.

22920072.name: Rebel Incinitron 6530
22920072.description: Rebels are reckless.  You're thinking...should we have shot that?  And they're yelling "More Pew Pew, Less QQ!"

225921650.name: Orbital Flute Strike
225921650.description: Imagine for a moment, you are peacefully playing a beautiful melody on your flute, when suddenly you see a flaming missile.  You realize that you are controlling its direction with your sweet music.  Where do you send it? That choice is yours and yours alone.

334177905.name: Blobby
334177905.description: Fear the mighty blob! Just kidding, it is only Blobby – everyone’s favorite sentient, scooter riding, gelatinous ooze! Find both the Dennis Bat and Drac Bat somewhere on ROBLOX and get Blobby after the event closes on 01/19/2016!

36568418.name: Pumpkin Sword
36568418.description: Jack O’Lantern was nimble and also was quick, and Jack attacked his enemies with a wicked-looking stick. The dreaded Pumpkin Sword gives the wielder all the power of Jack’s famed Samurai Slash.

361950795.name: Golden Roped
361950795.description: Get yourself a gold plated roped - because you're worth it!

17237662.name: Bloxiade
17237662.description: As a Robloxian athlete, I know how important it is to stay hydrated.  I like to stay hydrated with Bloxiade.  I think it makes me run faster, and my coach does too!

89491407.name: Zombie Grip Bomb
89491407.description: Your enemies will try to scream, but terror will take the sound before they make it.  Toss this zombie bomb up to 100 studs away and drag your enemies six feet under.

64220952.name: Ghostfire Throwing Daggers
64220952.description: Spawn several daggers and throw them at different angles to do maximum damage!

69210321.name: Hades Staff of Darkness - A Gamestop Exclusive
69210321.description: Imagine a world where no one can see what's coming but you....

153025459.name: Egglite
153025459.description: This gear item is meant for use in the official ROBLOX 2014 Egg Hunt - which is only open for a few more hours. Egglite, egg bright, first egg that I see tonight! This awesome egglite helps you see in even the darkest of places.

209980247.name: Adventurous Assassin Crossbow
209980247.description: Part of the adventurous assassin package.

19703476.name: Yellow Snowball
19703476.description: Ewww...  say no to yellow snow.

63253701.name: Skelefriend
63253701.description: They see him swirlin', They hatin'

2620523875.name: Moose Mount
2620523875.description: This majestic moose will take you on festive adventures!

168140516.name: Breath of Fire
168140516.description: Swallow the flames and spit out fireballs at your foes!

1224414225.name: Gingerbread Companion
1224414225.description: This little helper is here to help spread holiday cheer far and wide! Just be wary of hungry foxes!

22787189.name: Crimson Double Threat
22787189.description: Double your threat, double your fun!

4771622762.name: Eggveloper Cannon 9002
4771622762.description: After working countless hours on the event, you can let your anger out by launching eggs in the faces of unsuspeggting players!

22152234.name: Clawknife
22152234.description: A sword with claws seems a little redundant to me, but whatever.

108875172.name: Graffiti Skateboard
108875172.description: Keep it fresh with this skateboard.

50938773.name: Laser Electrocutor Blade
50938773.description: The electric blade works like a normal sword most of the time.... but sometimes it sends out a deadly shock!

278009025.name: Interplanetary Fighter Sword
278009025.description: Part of the Interplanetary Fighter Package

1230024287.name: Instant Snowman
1230024287.description: There must of been some magic in that top hat you bought, for when you placed it on the ground that was where a snowman dropped! Drop to spawn a snowman friend!

17237675.name: Captain's Flintlock
17237675.description: This flintlock is slightly more accurate than the average pirate's flintlock.  It's gold plated so the captain knows if any of the other pirates try to switch flintlocks with him while he's sleeping.

136170437.name: Unfriendly Turkey Friend
136170437.description: Why would you be friends with someone who wants to eat you? I don't know either, but this turkey is your friend and will not stop following you. If you click another player, this unfriendly little guy will attack!GOBBLE GOBBLE GOBBLE

2845952487.name: Sungrace, the Bo Sword
2845952487.description:
By the grace of the sun I shall conquer all with my worthy sword! Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

999865627.name: Scrooge McDuck’s Sun Chaser Plane
999865627.description: The famed plane of Scrooge McDuck! It has seen countless adventures (and survived even more crashes at the hands of Launchpad).

119917556.name: Chalk Sword
119917556.description: Use this sword when you really want to leave a mark.

99797357.name: Holiday Ornament Staff
99797357.description: Send a giant holiday ornament hurling at your enemies to squish them.

738924664.name: Carrot Slingshot
738924664.description: Sling deadly carrots at your enemies!! Click to release the string and launch a carrot in the direction of your cursor. Roughly 10 damage is dealt to any enemies hit.

24294400.name: The Unstoppable
24294400.description: What happens when the Unstoppable object meets an unyielding force?

114687236.name: Double Damage Frog
114687236.description: Throw this double damage frog at your foes. If it hits them, his poison rubs off on them and they turn blue for twenty seconds!  Any damage you do to them during this time is doubly effective!

284135286.name: Robloxian Clone
284135286.description: Click to spawn a tiny version of yourself that follows you everywhere.  A tiny imitation of yourself! How cute!

172922026.name: Silver Bloxxer
172922026.description: You've bloxxed around the clock, and now, victory is yours!  This item will be awarded to the top 10,000 competitors in the 2014 Clan Battle Arenas.

2544539043.name: Ninja Star Launcher
2544539043.description: Your foes will just be seeing stars. They’ll never know what hit them.

23922939.name: Orange You Jealous XD
23922939.description: Awarded to the winners of the Skaters in Giant World building contest, March 2010. *It's a gear item but currently showing up as a hat. We're working to fix it. Thanks!*

87361662.name: Ice Breaker
87361662.description: First he makes it - then he breaks it!  Freeze your enemies, then destroy them while they're stuck in your icy trap.  Does an astounding 14 damage per hit.

11719016.name: Blow Dryer
11719016.description: Point and hold down the left mouse button to unleash a stream of hot air that will blow the competition away (quite literally).

152173304.name: Opened Pastel Basket of Danger
152173304.description: If danger comes, you will be ready. Inside you find... Springtime Swordpack.

346686979.name: Crossbling Bow
346686979.description: Click to fire arrows that do 18 damage per hit! Hit the 'Q' key to drop a hundred of gold/silver/and bronze coins from the sky, around you, dealing 15 damage each if someone touches them!

62803165.name: Trick or Treat Bag 2011
62803165.description: Click this gear and receive a trick or a treat.  Which will it be?  You don't know until it happens!

26421972.name: Zombie Staff
26421972.description: ZOMG - Zombies!!  This staff summons 5 zombies to do your bidding.

709400407.name: Sabertooth Attack Friend
709400407.description: The thing about sabertooths is they always get their 'point' across. Equip to spawn a sabertooth tiger by your side! He'll chase after your foes and bite them with his massive fangs, dealing quite some damage.

936704694.name: Hunk’s Energy Cannon
936704694.description: The bayard weapon of the Yellow Lion pilot, Hunk. What it lacks in speed it makes up for in power!

99254358.name: Are200's ROBLOX Tablet
99254358.description: Winner: Are200. ROBLOX will be in touch to redeem this prize. Void if sold, traded, or deleted.

27474371.name: NoobTube
27474371.description: Annoy your friends by shooting noobs at them!  Or just shoot some noobs and use them for target practice.  The choice is yours!

176087639.name: ROBLOX U Moped
176087639.description: The ROBLOX University campus is huge!  You'll need this moped to get around quickly.

257812862.name: Neon Bloxster 2XP
257812862.description: Ride all over ROBLOXIA. Hit 'H' to honk and turn your headlight on and off with the 'X' key.

845527166.name: Shark Warrior Trident
845527166.description: The sharpest weapon in all the seven seas. Click to attack for 20 damage. Part of the Shark Warrior package.

113299556.name: Ultraviolet Laser Oculus
113299556.description: Charge up your eye laser to do maximum laser firing damage to your enemies.  Always wanted an eye that could shoot lasers?  Today is your day!

359244394.name: Guitar of Rock Excellence
359244394.description: For those about to rock, we salute you. Use the keys: 'Z', 'X', 'C', 'V', 'B', 'N', and 'M'. to play different tunes. Hold shift while pressing to sharpen the notes.

410001793.name: Rainbow Hot Air Balloon
410001793.description: This is advertising. And the stars look very different today. Here I am floating round my Hot Air Balloon – far above the spoon (for my cereal).

2221409781.name: Q-Bot Companion
2221409781.description: Find your robot companion here at Roblox! Be sure to watch Netflix’s new movie Next Gen on Friday, September 7.

2906732820.name: Community Pizza Launcher
2906732820.description: Unload some party during this awesome community event to earn the prizes!

132789698.name: Hallo-Cycle
132789698.description: Hey! You are on fire!  Use this cycle to speed through ROBLOX's gigantic Halloween level.

64372659.name: Fiery Dragon Axe - a Target exclusive item!
64372659.description: This dragon axe will have your enemies begging for mercy.  Get this item when you redeem a ROBLOX Card from Target after October 24th.

341109697.name: DarkAge Shuriken
341109697.description: Click to throw two of these powerful weapons swirling towards your foes.  Anyone hit is dealt 22 damage per shuriken.

65969704.name: Turkey's Vengeance Sword
65969704.description: Did you think turkeys were just going to sit there and take it while you ate them? No way - they're striking back...with a sword!

302030998.name: Vampire Hunter's Crossbow
302030998.description: Part of the Vampire Hunter package.  A crossbow with a deadly axe attached. Click to fire arrows at your enemies, dealing 18 damage per hit with a half a second fire rate.

159199218.name: Laser-saw
159199218.description: Chain saws are so yesterday on Earth.  The future is now with this laser saw.  Tired of just sawing through your enemies with lasers? Double click to activate the special laser shooting attack.

32858699.name: Faux Firebrand
32858699.description: The magical weapon of the Brothers Ignis, a 1000-strong force of battlehardened shocktroops.

287424705.name: Overseer Crossbow
287424705.description: Click and hold to rapidly fire arrows at your foes. Hit the 'Q' key to activate the Overseer's Menacing Arrow. Once fired, a massively sized Overseer Eye will magically replace the arrow and explode into hundreds of tiny eyes, which will shoot in all directions!

160198008.name: Dynamically Lit Bow and Arrow
160198008.description: Light up the night with this dynamic bow and arrow set.  One hit does 22 damage, but charge the bow and you'll quadruple the damage.

2620521684.name: Fireball Spell
2620521684.description: Turn your enemies into a crispy crater!

154727201.name: Exploding Lab Table
154727201.description: You're a mad scientist.  You want to blow things up.  What could look more innocent than an exploding lab table?  Drop your portable lab anywhere and 10 seconds later watch everything explode!

2620523077.name: Inflatable Saxophone
2620523077.description: Play some airy tunes with this sax.

365631067.name: Nickelodeon Slime Blaster
365631067.description: Shoot slime at friends and foes with this awesome Slime Launcher. Catch the Kids’ Choice Awards on Nickelodeon, Saturday, March 12th at 8pm/7c!

329022047.name: Alvin
329022047.description: The cavalier leader of the band Alvin and the Chipmunks. Be sure to find him before he ends up continuing on his “Road Chip”. Be sure to catch Alvin and the Chipmunks: The Road Chip in theaters December 18!

264289990.name: Green All Terrain Vehicle
264289990.description: Part of the All Terrain Driver Package!

2569012480.name: Maaus, the Battle Lion
2569012480.description: Ride into battle with strength and courage.

106064447.name: Love Hurts Ray Gun
106064447.description: Love is like a ray gun - it'll burn you if you're not paying attention.

29100347.name: Father's Day Card 2010
29100347.description: Father, dad, papa, vater, padre or pere.  Call him whatever you like, but make sure that he knows you appreciate him today!

33382537.name: Slingshot
33382537.description: It's a sure shot everytime!  Well only if you've got great aim....

71037076.name: Arabian Knight Scimitar
71037076.description: "Son of infamy! Every bone in your body shall be broken if you continue to defy me!"

549915884.name: Disguise-to-Go Watch
549915884.description: It's TIME to disappear! Click to change into a random appearance, wearing random hats and clothing for a little while and confuse others!

31314966.name: US Military Top Secret Experimental Jetpack
31314966.description: "WHO GOT GREEN PAINT ON THIS THING!!! THIS IS GOING TO COST THE TAXPAYERS SEVEN BILLION DOLLARS!!!!"

472607575.name: Horde of Attack Crabs
472607575.description: Summon five tiny crabs which will run after enemies and pinch them with their claws dealing damage! They'll chase anybody nearby and you click on.

892001727.name: 4th of July 2017 Fireworks
892001727.description: Light the sky this 4th of July!

174418144.name: CJJ’s Guide to Making Money
174418144.description: Can Charlie Joe make some extra cash doing as little work as possible? Find out in Charlie Joe Jackson’s Guide to Making Money. Start reading now!

270562881.name: Panda’s Cellphone
270562881.description: Trying to fit in with humans isn’t easy when you’re a bear. But having a phone helps. You must be pretty cool if Panda gave it to you!

27902398.name: TBC Skateboard
27902398.description: Turbo Builders Club members don't mess around. For shock and awe, you can't beat the black and orange.

65082275.name: Z Ray Gun
65082275.description: Hit an opponent twice and he'll go to sleep.

343587237.name: Personal Fighter Jets
343587237.description: Equip and click to spawn three personal fighter jets that fly around you. When there is an enemy within a 75 stud radius of you, they fire rockets at them!

2230348478.name: Captain Underpants Book 6
2230348478.description: When George and Harold’s latest prank makes a direct hit on school brainiac Melvin Sneedly, he decides to get even!

84418938.name: RoVacuum 2012
84418938.description: Cleaning up ROBLOXia, parts and noobs alike.

880448457.name: Beast Scythe
880448457.description:
It's red and has a skull on top, so it's scarier than the average scythe. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

2845820064.name: The Purfect Edge
2845820064.description:
The purrfect accessory to your adventure arsenal. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out roblox.com/toys to learn more...

2906731343.name: Admin Pizza Launcher
2906731343.description: Admins! Join the party during our community event to give a special prize!

37821473.name: ROBLOX GameStop Card
37821473.description: To celebrate the release of ROBLOX Cards at GameStop we're selling a limited edition ROBLOX Card.  In game, it transforms into 1 of several different ROBLOX games. For more information about ROBLOX Cards check out http://blog.roblox.com/

69499437.name: Azure Periastron Alpha
69499437.description: Only when two stars are at their closest point, can the material for this sword be collected, so they are extremely rare, and depending on which stars are orbiting one another they are different colors.  One thing is sure, they spell doom for anyone who comes near. First in a series!

96092647.name: Korblox Skeleton Wraith
96092647.description: He was alive when they put him in the box!  Now he's your official Korblox guardian pet.  The Korblox Skeleton Wraith came out of the Gift of the Korbloxian on October 26th, 2012

29532111.name: USA Vuvuzela
29532111.description: I saw the England-USA game at the Happy Pig in Copenhagen. Man were those guys upset.

226206253.name: Flower Feet
226206253.description: Flowers will follow wherever you walk. The magic of spring is inside your feet! Well, in these shoes at least...

221266538.name: The Daring Archer's Bow & Arrow
221266538.description: This bow does damage based on the distance of your strike for a minimum of 15 damage and a maximum of 55. Part of the Daring Archer package.

435116454.name: Golden Nunchucks
435116454.description: Click to swing at your foes to deal 18 to 26 damage per hit. With each hit there is a 10% chance you'll turn your foe into solid gold.

97161262.name: Booster Gloves
97161262.description: Oh you wanted some jet propelled gloves that let you glide through a level leaving only trails of smoke in your wake?  Yeah we've got those.

365674685.name: Sword of the Epicblueness
365674685.description: Click to slash, dealing 16 to 22 damage. Hit the 'Q' key, to shoot blue flames out in all directions, which will knock back your enemies and deal 25 additional damage! This special has a 10 second cool down. The Epicblueness is the stuff of vampires and will restore 25% of your health.

936703828.name: Lance’s Energy Blaster
936703828.description: The bayard weapon of the fun loving Blue Lion pilot, Lance. Be careful with this, hot shot! (It packs a punch).

19111869.name: Hanukiah
19111869.description: The Hanukkah menorah (Hebrew: מנורה menorah) (also Hebrew: חַנֻכִּיָּה‎ hanukiah, or chanukkiyah, pl. hanukiyot/chanukkiyot, or Yiddish: חנוכּה לאמפּ khanike lomp, lit.: Hanukkah lamp) is, strictly speaking, a nine-branched candelabrum lit during the eight-day holiday of Hanukkah, as opposed to the seven-branched menorah used in the ancient Temple or as a symbol. The ninth holder, called the shamash ("helper or servant"), is for a candle used to light all other candles.

158069180.name: Dual Venomshanks
158069180.description: Great for lunging and slashing, but its real damage comes with its special ability.  Hit 'E', 'Q', 'Z', or 'X' to create acid rain that will fall on anyone in a 50 stud radius.

146047220.name: Quill of the President
146047220.description: Use this to write out your presidential decree!

936703279.name: Blade of Marmora
936703279.description: The weapon of an secret group of resistance fighters committed to opposing the tyranny of the Galra Empire. Wield it with honor!

1001541309.name: Dog Man 3 Virtual Book
1001541309.description: Dog Man is back! This time he is up against a cute kitten clone and his conniving creator, Petey!

193769809.name: Boombox Gear 3.0
193769809.description: Click to play some hot jams.  Put in any sound id to play it in game!

332748371.name: Festive Dueling Piano
332748371.description: One simple click will send this festive holiday piano crashing down from the sky and onto your target.  They'll get crushed and be unable to move while you play them a little holiday tune.

160189871.name: Ninja Claws
160189871.description: These powerful attack claws allow you to slash at your foes in grand melee style!  Double click to slash both your claws at your foe and potentially push them to the ground.

159913543.name: Toothless
159913543.description: Get Toothless, Hiccup’s best friend and the only known Night Fury, from DreamWork’s Dragons: Race to the Edge.

29939404.name: Hot Dog
29939404.description: Challenge your friends to an awesome hot dog eating contest.  Regardless of who wins, it's going to be a fun time!

23532796.name: Lava XD
23532796.description: This skateboard was awarded to builders who scorched the Urban Skate Jungle building contest in March 2010.

120749408.name: Patriotic Sparkler
120749408.description: You'll light up the night with this dynamically lit sparkler!

25158998.name: ROBLOX Frisbee
25158998.description: Whether you play Ultimate or old school - this is the frisbee for you!

99797327.name: Hanukkah Menorah
99797327.description: Celebrating the festival of lights in style!

1363023036.name: RoboDog
1363023036.description: All the fun of a dog without ever having to worry about remembering to feed it. And if it keeps barking at the neighbors you can just turn it off

1119906090.name: Coco - Dante Companion
1119906090.description: Miguel’s faithful companion! This loyal friend will follow you anywhere – wherever your adventure may take you!
